quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,"Qhaaf: (edde faxem Yalli yaaxige). Yalli nabna-leeh sharaf-le qhuraanal xiibite"
  50,2,"Wonna hinnay keenik meesiise (takkaawise) keenih yemeetem qajjibsiteeniih (cakkumsiteeniih), koros itteh ah-qajiibik (cakkumuk) taniimi"
  50,3,Rabneeh burta tikki inna waqdi aduurennoo? Toh xer madaara (woh takkem hinna) itte koros
  50,4,"Yalli keenil gacisak iyyeh; nummah nanu neexegeh baaxo keenik daggossaah ken xagoorak takmem, ni-garil daccarsime kitab yan, kay addal tanim korsaanamak. (lawcal macfuuz kinnuk)"
  50,5,"Tonna hinnay a-koros Qhuraan kee Nabii dirabbosseh keenih yemeete waqdi, edde luk usun tobollokime (yengeggele) caagidih addat yanin qhuraan kee Nabiik iyyaanamak"
  50,6,"Keenik iró yan qaraanâ fan mawagitaanaa? kaa elle xisneeh kaa elle bilqisne inna, usuk foxooxa aalle waak"
  50,7,"Ķaadu baaxo fidisneeh, xiikooluh tan qaleelá teetil hayneeh, cooxuk ummaan qaynatay mabla kak meqe (ableh meqe) teetil nuysubuke"
  50,8,"Amah kah abnem mayballaay kassiisi, ummaan naqsuy yallal yaduurih yanih"
  50,9,"Kaadu qaraanak barkat-le lee oobisneeh, teetit masnoonaa (basaatin) kee amboy taggirqimeeh orbisimta teetit nuysubuke"
  50,10,"Kaadu xer tamiiray, exefuh yan mixexu-le, edde nuysubuke"
  50,11,"Woh naqoosâ quusih (maaqoh) nuysubuke kaadu rabte baaxo teetit nuynuwwee, mawuq wonna rabteenik lakal.nuwwuk awqetton sin magooqak qhiyaamah ayró"
  50,12,"Qhureyshi korosuk naharal nuuc maraay, rassi deqsita qeelih maraa kee samuud deqsita mari sinni farmoytit dirabbosseh"
  50,13,"Kaadu wonnah qaad deqsita maraay, firqawnaa kee luut tooboko (kay mara kinnuk) sinni farmoytit dirabbosseh"
  50,14,"Kaadu wonnah garbô maraa (Nabii shuqeybi mara kinnuk) kee tubbaq mari, inkih sinni farmoytit dirabboyseeh, Yi-digaala keenih taguudeh"
  50,15,"Naharsi ginot taannee? Aleey ma-taaninninok, nammay haytoh ken ginnaah kah sugen innah ken gacisnaamak mannal taannaah? Wonna hinnay usun qusba ginok agay waagat yanin"
  50,16,"Diggah seehadaytu ginneeh, kay nafsi kaa edde walalisam naaxigeh, kaadu nanu canti-ramadak (filli- ramadak) kaal xaynoh"
  50,17,"Namma malaykatti seehadayti taama yaktube waqdi, migdaa kee gural kaak daffeyak"
  50,18,Inki qangara maqida seehadayti dacrisey (namma malaykattu kinnuk) wohuh massoyseeni kay garil yanih akke waytek
  50,19,"Rabi qeero temeeteh nummal, toh kak kudak sugteemi immay catu mali"
  50,20,"Kaadu baantá fuxsinteh (ugut baanta kinnuk), too ayró koros digaalah edde xagnisinte ayró"
  50,21,"Kaadu ummaan nafsi yamaateh, warraysee kee sumaaqité teetî luk anuk malaykak"
  50,22,"Yalli xiibitak iyyeh; nıummah seehadaytow tahak garcit sugteeh, ku-lubbit suge alifu kok kalleeh, ku-mabla asaaku maqar-leeh gibdih"
  50,23,Kaadu kay wakliiti iyyah (malaykatti) ah yi-garil taniimiy massowte kay taamak
  50,24,Ummaan korostih cirdeyna (qinaadi-li) jahannamat qambisa iyya yalli
  50,25,"Isil yan cakki ciné, caddok tatur-li, agay waaga-li isi diinit"
  50,26,"Kaay Yallâ lih gersi yalla haa, gibdi digaalat kaa qambisa. (jahannam girah digaala kinnuk)"
  50,27,"Kay wakliiti (xibbanti) iyyah (sheetantu kinnuk), ni-Rabbow anu kaa ma-makkoysinniyo, kinnih immay usuk xer makoh addat suge tirtô gitak"
  50,28,"Yalli iyyeh; yi-garil a-saaku sitta ma-keemaarisina (ma-daawisina), nummah anu meesissó siinih tatruseh addunyalak"
  50,29,"Yi- garil maxcó ma-korsinta (ma- tadbiddilima), kaadu anu naqoosa yadlumi (tantise) hinniyo"
  50,30,"Kassis a-farmoytaw, kibbintee jahannamak inna ayroy (qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk), edde luk is ossantina maaytan itta"
  50,31,"Kaadu jannat xayyoysima ayró Yallak meesita marah, usuk keenik axxeere kal"
  50,32,"Keenik iyyaanah ah-elle xagnisimak sugteenimi Yallak meesita maraw, ummaan numuy toobitey (Yallal gaceh) Yallih amri dacriseh"
  50,33,"Ablekal racmaan kinni Rabbik meesiteeh, Yallal yuduure sorkocô baxa luk yemeete mara kinni. (Qhiyaamah ayró)"
  50,34,"Keenik iyyaanah; Jannat cula nagaynan luk, toh-waar ayrók"
  50,35,"Tama moominiin Jannat addal faxxa haytam-le, kaadu Ni-garil keenih neceemik bagul niqmatak ossantina lon"
  50,36,"Qhureyshi korosuk duma sinaamak makina hora bayisneeh, usun qandeh keenik gibiduk, tokkel baaxooxat mekki iyyeenihik, eleelitan rike maay geen yallih digaala keenit temeete waqdi? (magennon)"
  50,37,"Diggah, tohut kassit yan raaqisa sorkocobbaxa-le numuh, hinnay usuk hangi edde-luk sorkocobbaxi kaak aracal anuk ayti kah yeceeh ankacse numuh"
  50,38,"Yalli xiibitak iyyeh; nummah qaranwaa kee baaxooy, ken nammayih fanat tanim lica ayróh addat ginneeh, hebeltô taqbi nee maxaginna wohul"
  50,39,"Nabiyow usun iyyaanamal isbiraay ku- Rabbi Faylisak salat-ab, ayró tawqek naharataay (subci salat), ayro kortak naharat (qasri salat)"
  50,40,"Kaadu barak-tut salat kaah abaay, fardi salaatitteh lakal sunnâ salat abaay, Yalla cus. (uzkur)"
  50,41,Kaadu xayikkeek israafil deqsita malaykatti seeca ayró ankacis nabiyow
  50,42,"Toh nammay haytô baantah xongoló nummah edde yaabben ayró kinniih, too ayro is mawqah ayróy magooqak edde yawqeeni kinni"
  50,43,Diggah yalli ginó taynuwweeh qiddam (rabissam) Neé kaadu madaara Nee fan takke iyye
  50,44,"Baaxó keenil qanxixxa ayró, usun magooqak sissikuk yawqen, toh nel xabcin kobxisiyya (gaaboysiyya) cisab booxal"
  50,45,"A-koros ittaamat ixxigah nanu nayse, kaadu nabiyow atu ken dirkisé hinnito islaąamaninnol, kinnih immay yi-digaalak meesita mara Qhuraanat kassis"
  51,1,Yalli xiibiteh burtá fixiixisiyyah fixiixisa caacayal
  51,2,Kaadu kaxxam qilsi lee yakkuqe qambuurul xiibite
  51,3,Kaadu baddi bagul caalih gexa dawaanikil xiibite
  51,4,Kaadu Yallih amri ginô fanal keefiyta (kurta) malaykal xiibite
  51,5,"Cagalah ta seehaday elle xagnisinteenim, ugut kee cisaabak akkelem asmat-le numma"
  51,6,"Kaadu diggah, abten taamoomik cisab kee galto asmatah akkele"
  51,7,Yalli qaraanay qaxmeqe gino lel xiibite
  51,8,Diggah isin korosey Qhuraan kee Nabii caagidik sitta wayta maxcoh addat taniinimil xiibite
  51,9,Qhuraan kee Nabiil yaamineenimik daggaawime num daggawsimah
  51,10,Dirableelá abbarsinteh
  51,11,Usun koroosannuu kee toogimaaney ken tunxuqet aylahite mara amô xexxaarah
  51,12,"Usun cisab kee galtoh ayró mawaqdiiy, iyyaanaah esseran anqasah"
  51,13,Woh galtoh ayróy usun giral cararsimaana digaalah
  51,14,Tammoysa sin digaala! Ah teetik edde Qataatakak faxak sugteeni addunyal Keenik iyyan anqasah
  51,15,Diggah yallak meesita mari jannootaa kee daroorih addal yanin
  51,16,"Ken Rabbi niqmootak keenih yeceem raabitak beetan, diggah usun wohuk duma meqe marah sugen addunyal sinni meqe taamal"
  51,17,Tama mari barak xiinaanam keenik daguk sugte salat abak
  51,18,Kaadu maaci bar usun dambi cabti esserak sugen sinni Rabbil
  51,19,Kaadu ken maalut essera num kee wacarriyih esserewaa num maglab le
  51,20,Kaadu baaxol baxxaqqa le astootiy Yallih inkittinaanee kee qamal geyto tascasse tan Yallih inkittinaanel asmat le marah
  51,21,Kaadu sin nafsih ginot Yallih qamal geyto tascasse astooti tanik matablaanaa ?kas elle geytoonuh
  51,22,Kaadu qaraanal sin rizqhii (quusi) kee elle xagnisinteenim tan galtoo kee digaalak
  51,23,"Qaran kee baaxô Rabbi isi nafsil xiibite, nıummah Usuk sin elle xagnisem numma kinniimil, tohul maagaywaagitina sinni yaabat kah agay waagite (shakkite) waytan innah"
  51,24,Nabiyow Nabii Ibraahim qibinay konnabimê xaagi koo gufee
  51,25,"Kay qari kaal culen waqdi, nagaynan kol yanay kaak iyyen, nagaynan siinil yanay isin igmon maraay nanu sin manaaxiga keenik iyye"
  51,26,"Tokkel isi buxah marâ fanah gacca iyyeeh, gabul le beqra yusguudeeh solal hayyaheeh baahe"
  51,27,"Tokkel Kaa keenil xayyoyseeh, matakmaanaa keenik iyye"
  51,28,"Edde luk meesih diriggi keenik iyye maaqo akme waanam keenik yuble waqdi. Ma meesitin kaak iyyeeniih, ixxiga le awki kaah yaabaku waamal kaa aytikumusen (berrekisen)"
  51,29,"Tokkel Kay barrá woh toobe waqdi qawitak temeeteeh, fooca isik tootokeeh, anu idaltô maxalayto kinniyok mannal xalaa itte"
  51,30,"Malayka: tonnah ku Rabbi iyye teetik itteh, diggaluk usuk naggaaray ixxiga li"
  51,31,"Nabii Ibraahim malaykak: sin caagid macaay ta rubsume maraw iyye"
  51,32,Diggah nanu umeyniitih yan marâ fanah rubsumne iyyen
  51,33,Xeetiy alayte kallak yani keenil qambisnuh
  51,34,Asta le xeetiy ku Rabbih xaqul umaanet caddok tatre marah massoysime kinni
  51,35,Tonna luk yalla nummayse marak tet addal (Nabii luut meelah magaala kinnuk) sugtem neyyeeqeh
  51,36,Tokkel tet addal muslimiin buxaaxik inki buxak sá buxa magennino. (woh Nabii luut buxa kinnuk)
  51,37,"Kaadu tet addal ken finqa tascassee asta cabne, qansaru le digaalak meesita marah. (moominiin kinnuk)"
  51,38,"Kaadu Nabii Muusâ maaqentat moominiinih yallih dudda tascassee asta tan, firqawnâ fanah baxxaqqa le sumaq kee astooti luk kaa rubne waqdi"
  51,39,"Edde luk firqawni iimaanat derre cabe isi qandel duquurutak, kaadu firqawni Muusak:usuk baab abeyna akkiiy, hinnay cabuli akki iyye"
  51,40,"Edde luk firqawnaa kee kay qande nibbixeeh digaalleeh, badat ken qidne, usuk Assacokkilem baahe numuh anuk koroositeenimih sabbatah"
  51,41,"Kaadu qaad deqsita marat yekke finqat elle kaskassoowa marah asta tan, ken finqah maxalaytuh yan caacayay kayri sinni keenit rubne waqdi"
  51,42,"Ama caacay elle amma iyyeemik hebeltohim (ulim) macaba, ruminnah kaa hayya heeh cabah akke waytek"
  51,43,"Kaadu samuud deqsita marat yekke finqat elle kaskassoowa marah asta tan, sin finqah: yimixxige uddurû fanah hataká keenik iyyen waqdi"
  51,44,"Kaadu usun sinni Rabbih amrih cinat caddok tatreeniih, ken finqissa kakkaqô keenit radde usun intih abaluk"
  51,45,Edde luk ugtaanaah kudaanam maduudinnon edde yanin digaalah sabbatah. kaadu sinni nafsi cata mara makkinnon
  51,46,"Kaadu keenik duma Nabii Nuuc mara finqisneh, diggah usun Yallih amrik yewqe marah sugen"
  51,47,"Nanu qaran ninni maqaraay ninni qandet xisne, diggah nanu deraafek farakka kaa haam duuda marah anuk"
  51,48,"Kaadu baaxo fidisneeh, nanu maxxu meqe fidseynitte kinninoo"
  51,49,"Kaadu ummaan iimik sissin namma qaynat ginne, kassita mara takkeenî gidah Yallih qamal geyto"
  51,50,"Toysa sinaamey Yallih digaalak kay Racmatâ fanah kuda kaa kee kay farmoyta nummassaanamal, anu diggaluk siinih kaa le kabuk baxxaqqa le meesiise (takkaawise) kinniyok"
  51,51,"Kaadu Yalla lih aka yallay taqbudeeni mahaysina, diggah anu siinih Yalla le kabuk baxxaqqa le meesiise (takkaawise) kinniyok"
  51,52,"Qhoreyshi isi Nabii Mucammadak Aale baab abeyna hinnay cabuli kaak axcuk kaa kah dirabbosse innaah, keenik duma suge maral farmoytiitik hebeltô farmoyti mamatto, kaa dirabboysak baab abeyna hinnay cabuli kaak iyyeenih akke waytek"
  51,53,"Naharsi maraa kee wadirsi mari farmoyta dirabboysaanamal sitta maay farriimen inkih woh iyyen waqdi, aleey, wonna hinnay usun caddok tatre mara koroosannul"
  51,54,"Toysa derre keenit cab Nabiyow, atu yassacakkeenih qeemitan num hinnito, Koo edde rubne diini gudduysê kalah"
  51,55,Kaadu kassis diggah kassis yalla nummaysa marah tu-xiqahak
  51,56,"Kaadu jinnii kee seehada tuh maginniyyo, yoo yaqbudeenî gidih akke waytek"
  51,57,"Rizqhi (quusi) keenik mafaxaay, yoo yaskameenim keenik mafaxa"
  51,58,"Diggah Yalli usuk rizqhi yacayi, dudda-li kaxxa maqar-li"
  51,59,"Diggah tama korosuy isi nafsi Nabii Mucammad dirabbossaamat tudlume, keenik naharat sugte ken kataysis (koros kinnuk) digaalâ geyte maglabih innah yan maglab lon digaalak, usun tokkel yi digaalat qataatake woonay (assexeere woonay) is keenih amaatelem raq malik"
  51,60,"Koroosite marah finqi yan, ken ayróy kah xagnisimeenit. (woh Qhiyaamah ayró)"
  52,1,Yalli tuur deqsitta qalel xiibite. (woh Yalli Nabii Muusâ luk elle yaabe qale kinnuk)
  52,2,Kaadu kitaabay yunkuttubel xiibite
  52,3,Woh Qhuraanay fiddiime waraakitih addal yani kinni
  52,4,Kaadu Qaraanal yan Qariy beytil maqmuvr deqsitay malayka Yalla elle taqbudel xiibite
  52,5,Kaadu fayya heen Qaraanal (addunyâ Qaran kinnuk) xiibite
  52,6,Kaadu leek kiben badal xiibite
  52,7,Diggah Nabiyow ku Rabbih digaala korosul oobeleemil
  52,8,Hebeltoh (uli) iimiy tet waassa matan obta waqdi
  52,9,Woh qaran amooxiyyah yamooxeeh kaxxa angoyyih yangayye ayro (Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk)
  52,10,Kaadu qaleelá isi aracak kattaah gexoh gexxa ayro (Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk). qubultinnah
  52,11,Too ayro farmoytit luk temeetem dirabboyse marah baatii kee finqi yan
  52,12,Woo mari usun deedalat giirisaah digra mara
  52,13,Tama mari gutqoh gutqumoonu waan ayró jahannam girâ fanah
  52,14,Ah teeti giray dirbboysak sugteeni keenik iyyan
  52,15,Tokkel ta tablen digaala baaba innaa hinnak isin ablewaytaanaa
  52,16,"Isin gira culaay, tet niqna tammoysa, teetil tasbiroonu (coolaysittoonu) hinnay asbire waytoonu, siinil inki gide, cagalah isin elle galtimettoonum addunyal abak sugten uma taama"
  52,17,Diggah Yallak meesita mari jannootaa kee niqmatitteh addal yanin
  52,18,Ken Rabbi keenih yeceemit ruffu axcuk (tassa axcuk) kaadu ken Rabbi ken reebiseeh naggoyseh jaciim deqsitta girah digaalak
  52,19,"Akumaay, aquba rufto luk addunyal abak sugten meqe taamah galtoh"
  52,20,"Usun rooruh yan qaraakiiyih amol cusuulah anuk itta wagitak, kaadu ken rihmisneh (alkumusneh) curral qeyni deqsita agabul"
  52,21,"Kaadu Yallal yeemene maraa kee ken xayloy iimaanal ken katatte, ken xaylo ken eleelisneh, kaadu ken taamah galtok tu keenik madaggoysinnino, ummaan num abba heemih yabbixsime"
  52,22,Kaadu niqmatittek caxa mixuu kee cadok faxxa haanam keenih osisneh
  52,23,"Jannat addal kamri kaaqon sittal tabaatabsan, kaat kas magexaay, uma maxcoo kee dambit ken maqida"
  52,24,"Kaadu keenit meekitah keenih taamituh massoysen urri, usun sibat dansime luulih inna lon qaxah"
  52,25,Kaadu jannatti marak mariiy marâ fanah yafkune addunyal abak sugen taama sitta esserak
  52,26,Diggah nanu duma addunyal ninni marih addal Yallih digaalak meesita marah sugne iyyan
  52,27,"Tokkel Yalli nee guneeh neh yemqeh tirri neeheemil, kaadu jahannam girah huvurih digaalak nee naggoyseh"
  52,28,"Diggah nanu duma dubuk Yalla aqbudak sugne, diggah usuk meqe Rabbiiy, xuwaw li kinni"
  52,29,"Toysa Nabiyow fan kak rubsumte mara ta Qhuraanal kassis, atu ku Rabbi koh abe niqmatal ginnili hinnitooy, cabuli hinnitok"
  52,30,Hinnak ta koros qadarabey raba kah qamballa kok ittaa Nabiyow
  52,31,"Yi raba qambaala keenik ixxic:diggah anu sin innaah sin finqa qambaala marat anik"
  52,32,"Hinnak ta koros ahal ken kas ken amrise innaa, hinnak usun umaanet caddok tatre maraay"
  52,33,"Hinnak Nabii Mucammad Acade Qhuraan isih ginnaasiteeh bicsite iyyaanaa? Aleey, tonna hinna usun nummayse waana ikkal"
  52,34,Toysa kaa (Qhuraan kinnuk) ceela yab baahoonay nummat yaaba mara yekkeenik
  52,35,"Hinnak ta koros tu ken gine kal ginniimeeni innaa, hinnak usun sinni nafsi sinnih gine maraay Yalli ken gine kalah"
  52,36,"Hinnak usun qaranwaa kee baaxó gineeni innaa? Aleey, tonna hinna usun Yallih digaala asmite waanaah, Yallih inkittinaane nummayse waana ikkal"
  52,37,"Hinnak ku Rabbih kadnooni ken garil tani innaa, hinnak usun maysó-le maray sinam dirkisaay"
  52,38,Hinnak qaran elle yawqen daragay (magaaray) malaykâ yab kee wacyi elle ankacsaana loonu innaa? Toysa keenik ankacise num baxxaqqa-le sumaq baahay
  52,39,"Hinnak Yalli say xayló leeh, isin lab xaylo litoonuv? isin dirab kee ererih kah ittan innah"
  52,40,Hinnak Nabiyow diini gudduysiyyal cawal ken (koros kinnuk) essertannaa?edde luk usun woo magoyta elle tingiddibeh tiqilsee maraay
  52,41,Hinnak usun qellittaamih ixxigay usun sinaamah kak yaktubeeniih warsaana maay lon
  52,42,"Hinnak Nabiyow usun uma mala koh malsaanam faxaanaa? Tokkel koroosite mari, ken uma mala keenil taduure"
  52,43,Hinnak Yallak kalah qibaada cakkisita Yallay yaqbudeeni loonu innaa? usun agleh kaat hayya haanamak Yalli saytunnooweh
  52,44,"Kaadu ta koros qaran kitiifoonuh keenil oobah yableenimil digaalah, ittak bagul tan qamburre axcuk yenen"
  52,45,Toysa ken cab Nabiyow ken ayróy (woh Qhiyaamah ayró) edde finqitoonu waanat ongoorowwu iyyaanam fanah
  52,46,"Too ayró ken uma mala Yallih digaalak tu keenih ma xiqtaay, Yallih digaalak ken cattam matan"
  52,47,"Kaadu diggah isi nafsi koroosannut yudlume mari, Qhiyaamah ayroh digaalak naharat digaala lon addunyal, kaadu kinnih immay keenik maggo mari woh mayaaxiga"
  52,48,"Kaadu Nabiyow ku Rabbih meklal isbir, diggah atu Ni dacayrih gubat tantooh koo nablehik, kaadu saytunnos ku Rabbi faylisak salaatah solta waqdi"
  52,49,"Kaadu barak tut ku Rabbi saytunnoysaay cutuk derre caba waqdi salat (subci salaatih wakti kinnuk), kaah ab"
  53,1,Yalli cutuktal xiibite korah qellita waqdi
  53,2,Sin kataysa (Nabii kinnuk) cakki gitak hoxeweeh awqe weemil
  53,3,Kaadu nafsi fayxih yaabe waamal
  53,4,"Qhuraan kee cadiis rikeek tanim hinna, Yalli isi farmoyta Nabii Mucammadal 4zsaieńýķo oobise wacyi akke waytek"
  53,5,Gibdi cayla-li (jibriil kinnuk) Qhuraan kaa barse
  53,6,"Usuk (jibriil kinnuk) meqe weeloo kee qande li, edde luk Yalli kaa edde gineh yan weelot massowu iyye"
  53,7,Usuk ayró mawqa le kabuk fayya iyya aracal anuk
  53,8,"Tohuk lakal jibriil Nabii Mucammadal csato xayyooweeh, hangoggu (Qongoggu) kaal iyyeh nabam kaal xayyoowe"
  53,9,"Tokkel gassê namma exxah gideh kaak gacca iyye xaynah, hinnay wohuk kaat xayyooweh"
  53,10,"Edde luk Yalli isi naqasu Nabii Mucammadal åzsaińíķo wacyi oobise, woh jibriil gitak oobise wacyi kinni"
  53,11,Nabii Mucammad ĝas sorkocobbaxi madirabboysinna kay inti tublem
  53,12,"Ta korosey Nabii Mucammad Aale dirabbossaanaah, kaa giddiytaanaa isi Rabbih Aayootak yableh yaniimil"
  53,13,"Nummah Yalli xiibiteh, Nabii Mucammad dzakýķo jibriil malaykatti weeloy Yalli kaa edde ginet anuk nammay haytoh adda kaa yubleemil"
  53,14,Idyâ kusray malcin haytô Qaraanal tanih garil
  53,15,Tet garil orbeynâ Jannat deqsita jannat yan
  53,16,Kusra Yallih noorik tet buultah tanim tet buulta waqdi kaa yubleh
  53,17,"Nabii Muccammad ġzsafeýo mabla madaggaawinnaay, caddok matatrinna woo waqdi"
  53,18,Nummah Yalli xiibiteh Nabii Mucammad åzsaińýķo israa kee miqraaj bar isi Rabbih astootik kaxxa astooti yubleemil
  53,19,Neh warisay ta korosey laat kee Quzza deqsita namma numtinwellu
  53,20,Kaadu manaatay kalah sidoc haak taqbudeeni
  53,21,"Isin lab xaylo sinnih teexegeenih haysittaanaah, Yallah sinnih faxewaytan say xayló teexegeeniih haytaanaa"
  53,22,Toysa toh dulmi mekla kinni
  53,23,"Korosey tama yallittey isin taqbudeeni tu hinna, cagalah migooqay sin kee sin abbobti yallitteh muggaqsitte akke waytek, Yalli hebeltô sumaq kah moobisinna isin tet taqbudeenimih, ta koros dareemuu kee ken nafsi kicnim akke waytek kataataāaanam malon, nummah Yallih Nabiih arrabat ken Rabbik tirto keenih temeeteh"
  53,24,Hinnak seehadayti faxinnaanim maay le? (mali)
  53,25,Toysa Yalli le akeeraa kee addunyah amri
  53,26,"Kaadu Qaranwal malaykak maggo malaykay shafaaqatta (cató) kak tuxiqe sinni tan, Yalli idini keenih yeceek lakal akke waytek isih kah faxaah, kicna marah"
  53,27,Digga luk akeeral aamine waa mari malayka say marih migaaqal muggaaqisa
  53,28,"Usun iyyaanamak hebeltoh ixxigah loonum malon, akkalaksa katayaanam malon, digga luk akkal cakkik tu maxiqaay, cakkķi aracat magaca inkinnah"
  53,29,Toysa Nabiyow Ni kassitik (Qhuraanak) waaliyeh derre cabeeh addunya manok sah tu-faxewaa marat derre cab
  53,30,"Toh keenik ixxigak gufti, diggah nabiyow ku Rabbi usuk isi gitak makkoote marat sinaamak ixxigah yaysi kinni, kaadu usuk tirri iyye marat sinaamak ixxigah aysuk raaqa"
  53,31,"Qaranwal tanim kee baaxol tanim inkih Yalli le, umam abe mara giral galatuh (digaaluh) kaadu meqem abe mara jannatal galatuh"
  53,32,"Usun kaxxa dambittee kee umaaneenak yaxxeere mara qunxa dambitte akke waytek, diggah Nabiyow ku Rabbik dambi cabti farakka le kaal gace marah, usuk ixxigah sin caalootat siinik yaysi, sin abba aadam baaxok gine waqdi, kaadu isin sin inaanih bagut qellitak sugten waqdi, toysa sinni nafsi ma saytunnoysina tet faylissaanamal, usuk ixxigah yaysi kinni isi naqoosak isik meesita marat"
  53,33,Tokkel Yoh warisey Nabiyow iimaan kee Yallih taaqatat derre cabe num
  53,34,"Kaadu isi maaluk dagom baxa yeceeh, tohuk lakal cillaaleh mattaccoo yeyseede num"
  53,35,"Qellitteemih ixxiga kay xaqul maay tan usuk intih abaluk, kay gabat tanim tamurruqu waytaamah, edde luk usuk woh intih maay yable? (mayabla)"
  53,36,Hinnak Nabii Muusal oobe tawraat kitaabal tanim kaah mawarsinnoonuu
  53,37,Kaadu Nabii Ibraahimiy Yalli kaa elle amrisem duuduseeh gudduyseh kitoobah addal tanim kaah mawarsinnoonuu
  53,38,Dambi le nafsi aka nafsih dambi mayakkuqaay kaa kah makataataana
  53,39,Kaadu seehadayti taamiteemik kalihim aalle waam galtok
  53,40,"Kaadu diggah, kay taama sarrah ambulluyele akeeral"
  53,41,Tohuk lakal usuk galtimele dudda le galtoh abba hee taamal
  53,42,"Kaadu diggah, Nabiyow ginô gacim ku Rabbit yaadee Qhiyaamah ayro"
  53,43,"Kaadu diggah, Yalli usuk isih faxa mara yaysuuleeh isih faxa mara weeqisah"
  53,44,"Kaadu diggah, Yalli usuk Qidaah yaynuwweeh"
  53,45,"Kaadu diggah, Yalli usuk kulliimik namma Qaynat gine labim kee sayiimih anuk"
  53,46,"Daacoyti tiffa, maxaxat caxitta waqdi"
  53,47,"Kaadu diggah, aka ginoh ken ginaah ken gacsam Yallal tan rabeeniik lakal Qhiyaamah ayró"
  53,48,"Kaadu diggah, Yalli usuk isih faxa mara maalut gaddalisaah, ken edde leedisah"
  53,49,"Kaadu diggah, Yalli usuk shiqra deqsita cutuktih Rabbi. (woh qarabak marak teyni aqbudak suge cutukta)"
  53,50,"Kaadu diggah, Yalli usuk bayseh naharsi Qaad (usun Nabii Huud meela kinnuk)"
  53,51,Kaadu Yalli Nabii Saalic maray Samuud deqsita bayseeh num keenik macabinna
  53,52,"Kaadu Yalli Nabii Nuuc mara Qaad kee Samuuduk naharat finqise, diggah usun dulmii kee caddok taturuh lafit luk sugen keenik lakal yemeete marak"
  53,53,Kaadu Yalli Nabii Luut marih magaalooli Nabii Luut maral deerik afah korse
  53,54,Edde luk tet buultem tet buulteh xeet digaalak. (woh Qaraanak keenil oobe xeeti kinnuk)
  53,55,"Toysa seehadaytow anni niqmatitteey, isi Rabbik edde agay waa gittam. (geyyi wayittam)"
  53,56,A meesiise usuk Nabii Mucammaday 4zsafeájķo kaak naharsi ambiyay sinni mara meesiisak temeetek numuk teyna kinni
  53,57,Qhiyaamay xayyoowa deqsitta xayyowteh
  53,58,Too waqdi Yallak sa is edde tamaate wakti taaxigem matanaay tet gutuqtam matan
  53,59,Ta korosey Qajjibsittaanam (cakkumsuttaanam) ta Qhuraanaa
  53,60,"Kaadu anqasah kaal tasuuleeniih, usuk sin akak meesiisaamih conxoh maweqtaanaa"
  53,61,Isin deedalat gabxitak kaat derre cabtan
  53,62,"Toysa Yallah kummaataay, qibaada dubuk kaah caglisa"
  54,1,"Qhiyaama xayyowteeh, alsá faqitteeh, namma ikkel gacte"
  54,2,"Kaadu koros Nabii numma tascasse asta table waqdi iimaanat derre cabtaah, ah aggiriqee waa baaba iyyan"
  54,3,"Kaadu Nabii dirabboyseeniih, sinni kalbi fayxi kataaten, ummaan amri umaané takkay maqaané takkay le maral dabqa Qhiyaamah ayró"
  54,4,Kaadu nummah ta korosuh keenik duma sinni farmoytit dirabboyse marat tekkeemih xaagittek sahii kee waasó edde tanim keenih temeeteh
  54,5,"Ama keenih yemeete Qhuraanat kaxxa cikmatay dudda leeh gufti taafee edde tan.tokkel meesisso maca xiqtaa, Yallat derre cabeeh, farmoytit dirabboyse marah"
  54,6,"Toysa Nabiyow derre keenit cab, keenih qambal israafiil deqsita malaykatti seeca ayró baantat waagaleeh hagga leemih fan. (cisab booxá kinnuk)"
  54,7,Ken intiita rammit luk magooqak yawqen fixiixe qanaytih innah gacak fixix gibdah
  54,8,"Usun sissikuk seeceynâ fanah gexaanaah, koroositeh yan mari tah gibdi ayró iyya"
  54,9,"Dirabbosseh nabiyow ku meelak naharat Nabii Nuuc meela, usun dirabboyseenim ni naqsu Nuucu kaadu cabuli kaak iyyeeniih kaa sahteeniih kaa xiiriyeenih"
  54,10,"Edde luk isi Rabbi kallaceh: Nabii Nuuc, diggah anu kak yeysen num kinniyok yoo cat axcuk"
  54,11,"Edde luk dooqa kaak oggolleeh, qaran afoofi keenil fakneh maggo leey tanfxxuket"
  54,12,"Kaadu baaxó tanfuxxuke daroorih keenil qanxisneeh, qaran kee baaxô lee tongooroweh ken finqay nummah Yalli keenil mekleh yanih"
  54,13,Kaadu kaa nukkuqeh lucwaa kee bisaamirit xakben doynikit
  54,14,"Is ni dacayrit gexxa, toh kah abnem Nabii Nuucuh qokoluuy, koroosite marah digaalá takku"
  54,15,Kaadu nummah Yalli xiibiteh Nabii Nuuc kee kay marih maaqentat Yallih dudda tascassee astay kas elle geyaanah tet cabneemil nuucul ciggiila marah. Tohul kassita maray qakkaloowah iyya maay yan
  54,16,Toysa mannak tenee yi digaalaa kee Yi meesisso koroosite marah
  54,17,"Kaadu nummah, Qhuraan kassiisih xabbacosnehik, tohul kaskassoowaah qakkaloowa mari maay yan"
  54,18,"Qaad deqsita mari sinni Nabii Huud dirabboyseeh, wohul ken digaallehik, mannak tenee yi digaalaa kee yi meesisso"
  54,19,"Diggah, nanu keenil rubneh kaxxa caacayay kaxxa xabca le baytii kee umaané edde amurruqe wayta ayrót"
  54,20,"Usuk sinam laaracak hadiffi haah gomboh ken qida, usun laqiibak tewqe tamiirah (nakilih) inna luk raaqan"
  54,21,Toysa mannak tenee yi digaalaa kee yi meesisso
  54,22,"Kaadu nummah, Qhuraan kassiisih xabbacosnehik, tohul kaskassoowaah qakkaloowa mari maay yan"
  54,23,"Samuud deqsita mari sinni Nabii Saalic dirabboyseeniih, wohul farmoytit inkih dirabboyse mara yekken"
  54,24,"Tokkel nek numuk teynah yan inki seehadaytu kataynaa iyyen? Diggah, nanu toysa makoo (maxqawit) kee cabut nan"
  54,25,"Nek fanaak wacyi kaal oobaa? aleey, takkem hinna usuk dirabli kaxxiina li iyyen"
  54,26,Beera digaala keenil obta waqdi aaxige lon addunyaa kee akeeral dirabli kaxxiina li kinni mara. (saalic kinnik ken kinnim)
  54,27,"Diggah, nanu usun esseren Alá xaxxaqak tet ayyaaqennooh keenih ruubenno mokkoroh, toysa digaala keenil obtam qambaalaay, ken adal isbir"
  54,28,"Kaadu Nabii Saalicow ku marah keenih waris diggah, lee ken kee Alâ fanal kurrumtaah, mariiy ayro keenik yaaqubeeh, kulli arakil le num geytimam"
  54,29,"Tokkel Sinni kataysah seeceenih Alá qidimih, edde luk usuk alá xabbaheeh qideh"
  54,30,Wohul anu ken digaalehik Yi digaalaa kee Yi meesisso mannak teneeh
  54,31,"Diggah Nanu jibriil keenil rubneeh, inki adda keenit xongoleeh inkih rabeenih, edde luk usun gaso li dagiiree kee bocoy buluulunteh inna yekken"
  54,32,"Kaadu nummah, Qhuraan kassiisih xabbacosnehik, tohul kaskassoowaah qakkaloowa mari maay yan"
  54,33,"Nabii Luut mari sinni Nabii luut meesissoosa dirabboyseeniih, wohul farmoytit inkih dirabboyse mara yekken"
  54,34,"Diggah, Nanu xeet keenil rubne digaalah, Nabii Luut buxah mari (kaa kataate mara kinnuk) koh raaquh, nanu ken naggosneh woo digaalak maaci bar"
  54,35,"Ama asallam Ni xaquk yan niqmata, Tonnal galatna nee faatite mara"
  54,36,"kaadu nummah Nabii Luut Ni digaalay gibdil ken meesiiseeh, woo meesissoosat shakkiteeniih kaa dirabboyseenih"
  54,37,"Kaadu nummah Kay qibina kaa essereenih umaane edde faxoonuh, edde luk intiita ken waysisneeh, Yi digaalaa kee Yi meesisso tamannak tammoysa keenik inne"
  54,38,Kaadu nummah dabaqta digaalay salalta maaca keenil maacisse
  54,39,Yalli yi digaalaa kee meesisso tammoysa keenik iyye
  54,40,"Kaadu nummah, Qhuraan kassiisih xabbacosnehik, tohul kaskassoowaah qakkaloowa mari maay yan"
  54,41,Kaadu nummah firqawni marah ni meesissoosa temeeteh
  54,42,"Ni astooti inkih dirabboyseeniih, maysoliiy, duddalih yanih digaalah ken digaalle"
  54,43,"Qhureyshey sin koros maay tayse, woo korosuy siinik duma sugtey finqisnek, hinnak yallih digaalak amaan (saay) maay liton ambiyal obte kitoobah addal"
  54,44,Hinnak makki koros nanu buttay sitta geytey mayso le kinnino ittaa
  54,45,Makki korosih butta buksumeleeh bukah derre cabe le
  54,46,"Wonna hinnay xagni keenik Qhiyaamah ayró, Kaadu Qhiyaamah ayró gibdiih, qeero le. (makeeko-le)"
  54,47,"Diggah umeynit addunyal cakkik badit kee hoxat yaniiniih, akeeral habug itta girah addal yanin"
  54,48,"Girah addal ken foocitteh hirrigsimoonuwaan ayró, saqhar deqsitta girah digaalay gibdi tammoysa keenik iyyan"
  54,49,Diggah nanu ummaanim le caddol mekelleh ginne
  54,50,"Kaadu nanu tu abnam fannek ni amri kalah tu hinna, inki qangara akke waytek, woh tik iyyaanamih qangara kinni, wohim edde takke, sissikaaneh inti ramaccah innah"
  54,51,"Kaadu nummah siinik duma warrayte ummattak koroosannuh sin innah tan koros bayisneh, Toysa keenit tekke digaalat kas kassoowaah, kassita mari maay yan"
  54,52,Kaadu ummaanimiy usun abba heeni kitoobah addal tan kutbeh. (malayka tuktubeh tan kitooba kinnuk)
  54,53,Ummaan iimik qunxaah nabaamay tikki itta lowcal macfuuzul kutbeh tan
  54,54,Diggah Yallak meesita mari jannootaa kee weeqaytitteh addal yan Qhiyaamah ayró
  54,55,"Usun nummâ madabay elle daffeyaanay satta elle iyyaanal yanin, woh dudda leeh kaxxa reeda le Yallih xaqu kinni"
  55,1,Yallay fulte Racmatta le
  55,2,isi naqoosak isih faxe mara Qhuraan barse
  55,3,Usuk seehadaytu gine
  55,4,isih faxam baxxaqqa hayuh yab kaa barse
  55,5,Ayróo kee alsá sittal ciggiilak yimixxige cisaabay diggi iyyal gexxa
  55,6,"Kaadu cutuk kee coox isi Rabbi taaxigeeh, kaah kummatta. (sujuud kaah abta)"
  55,7,Kaadu qaran baaxóh amol fayya heeh baaxól qadliy isi naqoosa kah amrisa hee
  55,8,"Miidaanat caddok tatre waytaanaah, tu kah miidaanissen mara gane waytaanâ gideh"
  55,9,"Kaadu miidaan qadlil (massal) soolisaay, miidaan madaggoysina (madaacisina) sinaamak"
  55,10,Kaadu Yalli baaxó ginóh tet fidise
  55,11,Teetil caxâ mixuu kee curra addak kak tawqe faan le tamiira (nakili) tan
  55,12,Kaadu amboy qagura lee kee suruy meqe coox teetil yan
  55,13,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,14,Yalli seehadaytu (aadam) gineh kafnaanah kanniy itta kallay alayseenih inna lek
  55,15,Kaadu jinni girah uray hadiidigak (bliis) gine
  55,16,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,17,"Yalli usuk ayró kak tawqe namma kabih Rabbiiy, ayró kak korta namma kabih Rabbi cagay kee gilalah"
  55,18,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,19,"Yalli namma baday tii kak coboy lee kee, tii kak qasbo le yesgelleeh sittat yangoorowen"
  55,20,Ken nammayih fanat reebuy sittat kak tatre waana yan
  55,21,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,22,Ken nammayak luul kee marjaan yawqe Yallih duddal
  55,23,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,24,Kaadu Yalli qaleelah inna le kaxxa dawaanikiy badal gexa le sinam tu xiqih
  55,25,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,26,Ginók baaxô bagul ennittam inkih baytaah
  55,27,Ku Rabbiy nabna leeh massakaxxa le raaqa
  55,28,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,29,"Qaranwaa kee baaxól tanim faxxa haytam kaa esserta, kulli ayro usuk abaamat yan. (fayyaheek, rammaheek, yuynuwweek, qidek)"
  55,30,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,31,Sin cisaabâ fanah afkunenno abba hayteenimil sin galatnuh a qilsi namma buxay. (seehadaa kee jinni kinnuk)
  55,32,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,33,"Jinnii kee seehada buttay, Yallih amrik tawqeenim duddeenik, qaranwâ deraafee kee baaxô deraafek eweqa. Tawqeenim ma duddan kaxxa maqaraay, (kuwwataay) Yallih fayxi edde tanih akke waytek"
  55,34,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,35,"Toysa seehadaa kee ginnow girak uraa kee diyaayisen nacaas Siinil rubsumele (siinil Qulelon), tokkel wohuk sitta ma cattaana"
  55,36,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,37,"Qaran qanxixaah qisih admisen qasa faleh (adintá) inna le qoborta yakke waqdi, (qhħiyaamah ayró kinnuk)"
  55,38,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,39,"Too ayró aben dambik seehadah umeynit messerimaay, jinni umeynit messerima"
  55,40,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,41,"Woo ayró umeynit sinni astootil tamixxigimeeh, malayka amok gonboobaa kee ibak dadoobal (xibiiqal) xabba ken haytaah, girat ken qambissa"
  55,42,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,43,Tah jahannam giray umeynit addunyal dirabboysak sugte kinni Keenik iyyaanah
  55,44,Tet fan kee niqna kak caddok taturte leeh fanat meekitan digaalah
  55,45,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,46,"Sinni Rabbih foocih soolok meesite mari, namma jannat le"
  55,47,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,48,Caxâ mixuu kee mexexu le luud le namma jannata
  55,49,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,50,Ama namma jannatih addal gexxa namma dara tan
  55,51,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,52,Ken nammayih addal ummaan caxâ mixuk namma qaynat yan
  55,53,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,54,"Yallih foocih soolok meesite mari ama namma jannatal ruffu iyyan, fidooday adda kak gibdi cariirik kibuk tanil cusuulah anuk namma jannatih mexexih mafaala keenil xayih"
  55,55,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,56,"Woo fidoodal wagitto isi baqoltit yayseede agabi yan, ken baqoltik duma seehada keenil morbinnaay, jinni keenil morbinna fidoh"
  55,57,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,58,Ta agabi qaxah wirya yaaqhuut kee marjaan innah
  55,59,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,60,Addunyal maqaané abe marih galto akeeral jannatak sa macaay
  55,61,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,62,Edde yabne namma jannatâ kalah namma jannat yan
  55,63,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,64,Ama namma jannat inxixih cuuginih
  55,65,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,66,Ken nammayih addal namma daray nabam darittay aggiriqqe wayta tan
  55,67,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,68,"Ama namma jannatih addal caxâ mixuu kee tamiiraay (nakilaay), rummaan yan"
  55,69,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,70,Woo jannootah addal cal meqe agabuy kaxxam qaxmeqe yan
  55,71,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,72,"Woo jannootah addal curral qayniy wagitto isi baqoltit tayseedey, luuluk tan qarwah addal tani elle tan"
  55,73,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,74,"Ken baqoltik duma seehada keenil morbinnaay, jinni keenil morbinna fidoh"
  55,75,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,76,Anxax makaddid (barkumaamii) kee qaxmeqe fiddiimil cusuulah anuk
  55,77,Toysa seehadaa kee jinnik sin Rabbi siinih yecee niqmatittek dirabbossaanam ma niqmataay
  55,78,"Ku Rabbih migaq saytuniih, kay kayri maggoh, usuk dudda le nabna leeh, kaal yeemene marah mattaccoo leeh, konnaba le"
  56,1,Qhiyaama solta waqdi
  56,2,Woo ayró tet ugut dirabboysa nafsi mayan
  56,3,"Is Yallih qaduwwi girá culaamal ramma haytaah, Yallih kacnoytit jannat culaamal fayya hayta"
  56,4,"Baaxó rukkuumiyyah, rukkumta waqdi angoyyi gibdah"
  56,5,"Kaadu Qaaleela buluulumiyyah, bululsumta waqdi"
  56,6,Edde bullaaqey hawal fixiixisinte takke
  56,7,Kaadu a ginoy sidiica gexoh tanin akeeral
  56,8,"Edde luk migdi mara, migdi mari ma maraay ? usun akeeral meqe arac le mara"
  56,9,"Kaadu guri mara, guri mari ma maraay? Usun akeeral uma arac le mara"
  56,10,"Addunyal maqaane yaakume mari, usun akeeral niqmat yaakume mara kinnon"
  56,11,"Woo mari, Yalli isil xayyoyseh yan mara kinnon"
  56,12,Usun naqiim deqsitta jannootah addal yanin
  56,13,Nabii Mucammad Ĵa ummatak naharsi maraa kee keenik naharal warrayte ummatittek maggo mari tet cula
  56,14,Kaadu Nabii Mucammad Aade ummatak ellecabô marak dagom tet culta
  56,15,Dahabat haxxisen (bilisen) qaraakiyih amol yanin
  56,16,Usun cusuulah anuk sitta fan afkanuk tet amol yanin
  56,17,"Idoolitewaah, rabewaa urruy waara keenit meekita keenih taamitoonuh (ken kidmatah)"
  56,18,"Kobboyyaayii kee, ibriikaay, kaaquunuy gocoy darak kibuk yani luk"
  56,19,"Kay maqubut amó keenik ma berrissaay, kas keenik edde ma gexa"
  56,20,Kaadu waara urri keenit meekisa caxâ mixuk faxaanam dooritan
  56,21,Kaadu haadâ cadok faxxa haanam lon
  56,22,Kaadu curral qayni deqsita agabuy
  56,23,Taagisen luulih inna le lon
  56,24,Amah usun addunyal abak sugen meqe taamah galto kinni
  56,25,Jannat addal uma yab kee dambi edde yanim ma yaabban
  56,26,Mariiy marah keenik aba salaąamaqleh maxco akke waytek
  56,27,"Kaadu migdi mara, migdi mari ma maraay? usun kaxxa arac kee kaxxa galto le mara akeeral"
  56,28,Usun keenaani sinni kusuurul yanin
  56,29,Kaadu muuz cooxuy xaylo kak exefih tani lon
  56,30,Kaadu kate wayta iraawol yanin
  56,31,"Kaadu qulluntaah, gexxa leey, aggiriqqe wayta lon"
  56,32,Kaadu maggo caxâ mixuy ambaxewaay
  56,33,"Aggiriqqe sinniih, waaso sinni lon"
  56,34,Kaadu fidooday fayya le lon qaraakiy bagul
  56,35,Diggah nanu tayse ginoh ken (jannatti agabu kinnuk) ginne
  56,36,Edde luk bikir leela ken abne
  56,37,Usun sinni baqolti kicna agabuy fooduh (waday kinnuk) yani ken abne
  56,38,Ama agabu migdi marah ginne
  56,39,Ama niqmoota lem naharsi marak butta
  56,40,Kaadu ellecabô marak (migdi mara kinnuk) butta
  56,41,"Kaadu guri mara, guri mari ma maraay?usun galtoo kee caalat kak uma mara akeeral"
  56,42,Niqin huuriy jahannam girak yanii kee kaxxa niqna le leeh addat yanin
  56,43,Kaadu diyyit inna le qiirih (qeerih) iraawoy (silaaloy)
  56,44,"Xabca sinniih, mabla kak amqe waytah addat yanin"
  56,45,"Woh ken kah geytem diggah, usun wohuk duma addunyal Yallih niqmatat batrite marah sugen"
  56,46,Kaadu kaxxa dambih (koroosannu kinnuk) bagul sugen yatoobeenim niyaate kalah
  56,47,"Kaadu rabneeh, burta nekkeeh, lafoofiy ruma tekke nakke waqdi, diggah nanu ugtennoo? axcuk sugen rabi lakal ugut yaniimih angaddiyyah"
  56,48,"Hinnak nee kee nek naharsi abbobti ugutennoo rabneeh, burta nekkeek geeral"
  56,49,"Nabiyow Keenik ixxic :diggah naharsi maraay, ellecabô mari Aadam xaylok"
  56,50,Kobxisime le timixxige ayroh (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) uddurul
  56,51,Wohuk lakal isin diggaluk ahoxa leelah dirab leelay
  56,52,Nummaak akmetton cooxuk zaqhqhuum deqsitta caxak
  56,53,Edde luk teetik bagitte kibetton qulul gibdah
  56,54,Edde luk tet bagul niqna kak caddok taturte leey bakar kalewayta aaqubetton
  56,55,"Tokkel isin bakar gibdah maggom tet aaqubetton, kaxxam bakaareh yan gaalay bakar kak kate waah maaqabah"
  56,56,"Ama digaalay ken geyte ken qibnaytiinó kinni, galtoh ayró (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk)"
  56,57,Seehaday suge waytik nanu sin ginnek Qhiyaamah ayróh madaara manummassaanaa
  56,58,Yoh warisay sin agabih maxaxat caxxan daacoyta
  56,59,"Siini innaa seehadaytuh kaa gintam, hinnak neey kaa gintam"
  56,60,"Nanu sin fanal raba mekelleeh, nanu yaffare mara hinnino"
  56,61,"sin weeloola korisnaah, aaxige waytan ginoh sin ginnam Qhiyaamah ayró"
  56,62,Nummah Yalli suge waytik naharsi ginoh sin ginem teexegeenih. Edde luk Yalli isi duddal nammey haytoh adda sin gacisuwaam makassittaanaa akorosey
  56,63,Yoh warisay tabqureenih taniinimik dariyyuy baaxol qiddaana
  56,64,"Isin kaa taysubukeeni innaa, hinnak neey kaa taysubukem baaxok"
  56,65,"Fanne nee tekkek a yooboke darqi ruma kaa abak neneeh, sin darqil obtem qajjibsita mara akkuk tenen"
  56,66,Diggah nanu kasaaritneh
  56,67,Tonna hinnay nanu rizqhik baxaysinneh axcuk tenen
  56,68,Yoh warisay a leey taaqubeenih iyya
  56,69,"Isin tet oobisseeni innaa qamburrek baaxol, hinnay neey tet oobissem"
  56,70,"Fanne nee tekkek Qasboh carakak tan lee tet abak nenek, Yalla mafaatittaanaa Coboyuk siinih oobiseemil"
  56,71,Yoh warisay a giray damaluk qiddaanah iyya
  56,72,"Tet caxá, Isin ginteeni innaa hinnak neey tet gintem"
  56,73,Nanu jahannam girah kassis kee guurô marih tuxxiq tet (addunya gira kinnuk) abne
  56,74,Toysa Nabiyow ku Rabbiy nabay dudda leh migooqaa kee weeloola saytunnos
  56,75,Yalli xiibiteh cutuuka kak korta aroocal ayrô kormak
  56,76,"Ama cutuuka kak korta aroocal abna xiiba, aaxaginnitoonuy is naba xiiba kinni kas le marah"
  56,77,"Diggah, ta Qhuraan Nabii Mucammadal 4zsafeńýķo oobisne, Qhuraanay nabay maqaane maggo kinni"
  56,78,Usuk daccarsime kitaabih addal yan Yallih garil (lowcal macfuuz kinnuk)
  56,79,"Qhuraan gabah xagtam matan Yalli satunnoyse malayka akke waytek, hinnay Yallat agleyta haanam kee janaabaa kee wadô sinnak saytunnoowe mara akke waytek"
  56,80,A Qhuraanak oobiyyi ginô Rabbi le kabuk yekke
  56,81,A korosey A Qhuraanaa isin dirabbossaanam
  56,82,Kaadu Yalli siinih yeceeh yan rizqhih (quusih) faatitiyyaa diggaluk isin dirabbossaanaah tangaddeenim
  56,83,Siinik numuk teyni rooci garoyra yaafe waqdi gacissaanam maay duddan kay xagarah
  56,84,Isin woo waqdi kay fan wagitak
  56,85,Nanu siinik kaal xayuk raqna able waytaanakkal
  56,86,Tokkel Isin abtan taamal cisab kak abe waanaah wohul galtime waa mara tekkeenik
  56,87,Isin nummat yaaba mara tekkeenik Rooci xagarah gacissaanam maay duddan (woh ma-duddan)
  56,88,A rabe num Yallal xayyoysime marih num yekkek
  56,89,"Toysa farakka le racmataay, ruffu edde iyyam kee naqiim deqsita jannat le akeeral"
  56,90,Rabe num migdi marih num yekkek
  56,91,Migdi marih num tekkeemih nagaynan lito Kaak iyyaanah
  56,92,Kaadu a-rabe num dirab leelah hoxa leelah num yekkek
  56,93,Toysa qibnaytiinoh niqna kak caddok taturte lee le
  56,94,Kaadu jaciim degqsitta girâ culim le galtoh tet digaala tammoysak
  56,95,"Diggah Nabiyow ama kol gabbaqne yab, nummay asmat le kinniih agay waaga mali"
  56,96,Toysa Nabiyow ku Rabbiy nabay dudda leh migooqaa kee weeloola saytunnos
  57,1,"Yalla saytunnosseh qaranwah addaay, baaxoh addal tanim, Usuk (Yalli) maysoliy naggaarah yani"
  57,2,"Yalli qaranwaa kee baaxô mulki-le (reeda-le), usuk yaynuwweeh qidah kaadu Usuk ummaanimil qamal geyto-li (xiqto li)"
  57,3,"Yalli Usuk naharsittuy naharat tu- kak aneewayta kaadu ellecaboytay wadirit tu-kak raaqe wayta, iró raaqaah kaak iró raqtam matan, qellitaah kaak xayuk raqtam matanaay, mablooli kaa matabla, kaadu Usuk ummaanim yaaxigi"
  57,4,"Yalla kinni gintem qaranwaa kee baaxó licá ayroh addat, wohuk lakat fayya iyyeeh, isi celta massoynah qarshi amol massooweh (kay nabna celta massoynah). baaxot cullu ittaamaay (ambooy, roobuuy.....) teetik bukku ittam Yalli Yaaxigeh. kaadu qaraanak obbu ittaamaay kaâ fanah eweqqi ittam yaaxigeh (malaykaa kee kay naqoosah taamak) Kaadu Usuk isi ixxigal siinî luk yan elle aninnaanih rikel, kaadu Yalli isin abba haytaanam yabali"
  57,5,"Qaranwaa kee baaxô mulki-le (reeda-le), ginô caagiida inkih Yallâ fanah gacta"
  57,6,"Yalli bar laqot culsaah, laqó barat culsa, kaadu Usuk isi naqoosah alilwah addat tanim yaaxigi"
  57,7,"Yallaa kee kay farmoyta nummaysa, kaadu acuya amol sin kak hee maalu (ciggiile mara sin kak abe maalu). Siinik Yalla nummayseeh isi maalu Yallih sabbatah yecee marii, kaxxa galto- le"
  57,8,"Maca malkittaanaa Yalli inkittu kinnim kah nummayse waytaanam! Yallih farmoyti siinih seecak sinni Rabbi nummassaanâ gidih, wohul Yalli nummah digga-le xagna siinik bee Yalla nummaysa mara tekkeenik"
  57,9,"Yalla kinni isi naqsu Nabii Mucammadal ġa Qhuraan aayootay baxxaqqa itta oobissam, wohul koroosanni diteetak iimaan noorî fanah sin yayyaaqe gidah. Kaadu diggah Yalli xuwaw li nacrur li"
  57,10,"Maca sin waassa maalu Yallih gitah taceenimik, Yalli qaranwaa kee baaxô nagra luk, siinik makki fakiyyak naharat maalu yeceeh korosut qeb abba hee mari galtol ma-massoowa, woo mari Yallih garil darajatah nabah, makki fakiyyak lakat Yallih gitah maalu yeceeh korosut qeb abe marak, kaadu Yalli ama namma mara inkih jannatah xagnise, kaadu Yalli isin abba haytaanamak adda yaaxigiiy teetil sin galatele"
  57,11,"Yalla meqe amaakisiyyah (gacsa) amaakissam (taceem) miyyaay? (kay taaqatah maalu yaceenimil galto kaak qaagitak), Yalli wohul galto kaah xirribisuh (yaymagguh) kaadu usuk meqe galto-le (jannat kinnuk)"
  57,12,"Lab moominiin kee say moominiinik ken noori ken foocittee kee ken migdittel gexah table ayró, asaaku sin aytikuma (berraka) jannatittey guba weeqaytitte kak gexxâ culimi tet addal waarak keenik iyyan, woo galto is kaxxa affaafa (limayiyya)"
  57,13,"Lab munaafiqhiin kee say munaafiqhiin moominiinik nee qambaala itta ayró sin noorik tu hirgitnamkeh, siinik wadirih addunyâ fanah gacaay noori wokkel gurrusa keenik itta moominiin angasah, tokkel moominiin kee munaafiqhiin fanal reebuy afá le xissiime, teetik adda-le gammiy moominiin kak tanik Racmattá tan (jannat kinnuk) kaadu teetik iró-le gammiy munaafiqhiin kak tanik digaalá tan. (girâ digaala kinnuk)"
  57,14,"Munaafiqhiin moominiinih sectah siinî luk masuginninoo addunyal axcuk. Yeey iyyan, kinnih immay isin sinni nafsi nifaaqhat (bagi kufrit) finqisseeniih, Nabii kee moominiinih finga qambalten kaadu rabi lakal ugut yaniimil shakkitteeniih, deedal qaagit sin duquuruseh Yallih amri (raba kinnuk) siinil amma iyyam fanah, kaadu sheetan Yallal taamineenimik sin duquuruseh"
  57,15,"A saaku munaafiqhiiney fidá siinik moggolintaay, koroosite marak moggolinta. Orbeyna siinik inkih girá, is siinih taguude keenik iyya Yalli. Kaadu is maxxu qax uma gacsimeynaay"
  57,16,"Yallaa kee kay farmoyta nummayseh yan marah wakti maxayyoowinnaa ken sorkocôbbaxitte Yallih cusim (kassit) kee qhuraanak obteemit allagowtuh.kaadu keenik duma kitab kah yontocowwime maray edde luk wakti edde yexxeereeh sorkocobbaxitte kak kafteh inna (yahuud kee nasaara kinnuk) akke wayoonay, keenik maggo mari Yallih taaqatak yewqeh"
  57,17,"Diggah yalla kinnim ixiga, baaxó is qabaarah kafteeh rabteek lakal taynuwweem! Nummah ni dudda tascassee astooti siinih baxxaqisneh elle kaskassoowa mara takkeeninkeh"
  57,18,"Diggah sinni maaluk sadaqhat tacee labhaa kee sadaqhat tacee sayyó, usun Yallih fooca edde faxak meqe gacsa (amaaki) yeceenik, Yalli Keenih xirribisaah, wohuk bagul usun meqe galtó lon (jannat kinnuk)"
  57,19,"Kaadu Yallaa kee kay farmoytit nummayse mari, woo mari usun nummaysiyyi kak duude mara ambiya elle temeeteemil. Kaadu Yallih diinih sabbatah koros gaadut rabe mari, usun sinni Rabbih xaqul sinni galtoo kee sinni noori lon qhiyaamah ayró, koroositeeh nastooti dirabboyse marah tu gactek, woo mari jaciim deqsitta girah mara"
  57,20,"Sinaamey! Cagalah addunyâ mano digir kee doklaay, bilqaa kee sin fanih hiddootu, kaadu maaluu kee xaylô massamagga kinnim ixiga, Teetik ceelallo roobut tooboke buqre edde temqe buqraabay tohuk lakal is kaftaah walqinuk tet tableeh, sarra rumay buluule yakkeh inna kinni. kaadu akeeral korosuh gibdi digaalá tan, kaadu yalla nımmayse marah dambi cabtii kee Yallih kacni yan. Kaadu addunyâ mano is tu hinna duquurusiyyi duyye (afeyna) baxa akke waytek"
  57,21,"Kee sinaamey sin Rabbik dambi-cabtii kee jannatay garbi (bagbaggi) kak qaran kee baaxô gide yakke fan qalala. Usuk Yallaa kee Kay farmoytit nımmayse marah massoysimeh yan jannata, woh Yallih muxxoo kee cinday isi naqoosak isih faxe marah tet yacee kinni, Yalli kaxxa muxxo li kinni"
  57,22,"Kee sinaamey hekeltô musiibáy (umaané) baaxô bagul takkey sin xagta matan, kaadu biyookaay qululuk sin nafsi xagta musiibá matan, tet ginnaamak naharal kitaabal (lawcal macfuuz kinnuk) tanih akke waytek, Toh diggah Yallal xabcinih"
  57,23,"Sinaamey tamah siinih kah warisnem, siinik taturteemih rookite (aczune) waytoonuuy, Yalli siinih yeceemih wallite waytoonu. Yalli makicna ummaan kaxxa mariinolih hideyna (hobbiyyo-li)"
  57,24,"Usun gabâ gibda le maray sinam gabâ gibdaa kee cinnaanel (cillaalel) amrisa. limaan kee Yallih taaqatat derre cabe mari, sinni nafsik sá wohut Yallak kalaąaanam malon. Toysa diggah Yalli usuk isi ginok gadda li, fayla li"
  57,25,"Nummah ninni farmoytit baxxaqqa-le astootiy sumaq keenih takkel ken rubne, kaadu kitab kee miidaan keenil oobisne sinam sittin fanal qadlil taamittamkeh. Kaadu birtay gibdi maqarleeh, sinaamah maggo tuxxiq edde yani oobisne, Yalli isee kee isi farmoytit kaa able kalah qokla maray isih dumaak aaxaguk suge sinam yaybulleenkeh. Diggah Yalli qande li mayso li"
  57,26,"Kaadu nummah Nabii Nuuc kee Nabii Ibraahim ken mara fan ken rubne, kaadu nubuwwannuu kee kitab ken nammayih samadah neceeh neexege.ken nammayih samadak tirri ittem taniih, maggo mari keenik Yallih taaqatak yewqeh"
  57,27,"tohuk lakal Ni farmoytit ken raatittel katasne (Nabii Nuuc kee Nabii Ibraahim raatitte kinnuk), kaadu maryam baxa Nabii Qiisa keenil katasneeh, injiil kitab kaah necee. Kaadu kaa kataate marih sorkocôbbaxittet xuwaw kee nacror hayne, Kaadu Rahbaaniyya (Gs rihim kee addunyak yaggiriqqeenimi qibaadah) tet bicsiteenih ikkal nanu tet fardi keenil maabinnino, usun woh kah abeenim Yallih kacnih guran akke waytek, tokkel usun nummâ dacayrih tet madacrisinnon, edde luk keenik yeemene marah le galto neceeh, maggo mari keenik Yallih amrik yewqeh"
  57,28,"Kee yallal yeemene maraw Yallak meesitaay Kay farmoytal eemena! Usuk isi racmattak namma maglab siinih aceele, (afto) kaadu nooriy elle gexxaana siinih heeleeh, dambi siinih cabele, Yalli dambi cabti li, xuwaw li kinni"
  57,29,"Yalli tamah inkih siinih kah yeceem, kitab le mari (yahuud kee nasaara kinnuk) Yallih muxxok tul dudda aalle waanam sinnik yaaxigeenî gida. Diggah muxxo inkih Yallih gabat taniih isih faxa marah tet yacee isi naqoosak. Yalli isi ginoh kaxxa muxxo li kinni"
  58,1,"Nummah Yalli isi baqlih caagidil Koo giddiyta barráh maxcó yoobbeh, kaadu is tet yibbixe gibdaabinak Yallal weqsitta, Yalli sin nammayih xawàh gacam gacsiyya yaabbeh, diggah Yalli ummaan maxco yaabbi, ummaanim yabali kinni"
  58,2,"Siinik sinni agabu sinnil carammoysa mari usun (agabu kinnuk) niinaanih xiiron nel yakkoonay axcuk, ken agbi nummah ken inaani hinna, Ken inaani ken xalte inaanî kalah usun Ken inaani hinnon, Kaadu diggah usun (labha kinnuk) maxcók uma maxcóo kee diraabat yaaban, diggah Yalli kaal gaca marah qafu abe, dambi cabe kinni"
  58,3,"Kaadu sinni agabu sinnil carammoysa mari ni inaanih xiiron nel yakkoonay axcuk, tohih lakal iyyeenimit gaceenik, naqasu currusaanam keenil tan (baqolti kinnuk) barráa kee baqala fidoh sittal orobtak naharal, toh Yallih meklay Yalli elle kas kassowtaanâ gideh siinil madqe. Kaadu Yalli, isin abba haytaanamak adda yaaxigi kinni"
  58,4,"Tokkel Currusam gee wee num namma alsay sitta kataatah soom kaal yan, sittal orbaanak naharal fidoh, toh duude wee num toysa lactam tu dagoytih maskama kaal tan. Toh siinih kah baxxaqisnem, Yallaa kee kay farmoyta nummassaanaah Yallih madqal taamittaanâmkeh iyyaanama, Kaadu toh Yallih caddoodaa kee kay amrittek edde matatrina, kaadu koros qansarissa digaalá le"
  58,5,"Diggah Yallaa kee Ķay farmoytih amri yakeelefeeh cina mari, bursumeenih keenik naharal suge mari kah bursume innah, kaadu nummah baxxaqqa le astootiy Yallih farmoytih numma tascassee oobisne, Kaadu koros ken tayqunxeeh xixxibissa digaalá le"
  58,6,"Nabiyow! keenih cus Yalli inkih ken ugusuwa ayróy (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk), usun taamoomik abba heenim keenih warsa, Yalli ken taamoomi loowol arac xagseh usun tet habbaaleenih anuk, Yalli usuk ummaanim yabali kinniih, kaak qellittam matan"
  58,7,"Yalli qaranwal tanim kee baaxól tanim inkih yaaxigem Maaxaginnitoo? diggah sidiica numuy garayta matan yalli keenik ferey haytuh yani kaa akke waytek, kaadu koona numuy garayta matan usuk lecey haytuh keenik yani kaa akke waytek, kaadu tama loowok daguk hinnay wohuk manguk magaryan Yalli isi ixxigal keenî luk yani kaa akke waytek, usun faxe ikkeliiy yanoonay.tohuk lakal usun umaanee kee maqaanek abba heenim Qhiyaamah ayró keenih warsele,diggah Yalli usuk ummaanim yaaxigi kinni"
  58,8,"Matablannaa Nabiyow! Yalli garayak waase marâ (yahuud kinnuk) fanah tohih lakal kak waasimeenimit yaduureeniih, dambiiy, caddok-tatur kee yallih farmoytih amrih cinal garayan, kaadu usun kol yamaaten waqdi Yalli koh abewe salaamaqle koh aban, kaadu sinni nafsih addal, nummah Mucammad Nabii akkinnay, nanu kaak innaamal Yalli nee digaalak manannaa iyyan? Jahannam deqsitta girá culaanaah digaalah ken xiqtah, is manxu uma gacsimeynay fan kak yaduureeni kinni"
  58,9,"Yallaa kee kay farmoytal yeemene maraw! Garay abtan waqdi dambiiy, caddok tatur kee Yallih farmoytih amrih cinal magarayinay, maqaanee kee Yallak meesil garaya, kaadu Yallak meesita, kaadu isin Yallay cisab kee galtoh fan kak gactoonu waytaanay garil kak maagowtoonu waytaanak meesita"
  58,10,"Cagalah umaane edde tan garay sheytan kabuk yan, Yallal yeemeneh yan mari rookitamkeh, tama garay tu keenik makala, Yallih idini akke waytek, kaadu moominiin dibuk Yallal kelitay"
  58,11,"Yallaa kee kay farmoytal yeemene maraw!daffeynaani farakka hayisa siinik iyyeenik, toysa daffeyna farakka hayisa, Yalli isi jannat farakka siinih heelek, kaadu uguta siinik iyyeenik uguta, Yalli siinik yeemeneh yan mara fayya haa, kaadu qilmi kah yontocowwime mara fayya le darajatittel fayya haa, Yalli isin abba haytaanamak adda yaaxigi, tu kaak maqellitta"
  58,12,"Yallaa kee kay farmoytal yeemene maraw! Yallih farmoyta garassaanam faxxan waqdi, toysa sadaqhat uysukuma sin garayak naharat, woh abtaanam maqaaneh siinih tayseeh, sorkocobbaxi saytunaaneh siinih aysuk raqtak, tokkel taceenim gee wayteenik, toysa diggah Yalli dambi cabti li, xuwaw li kinni"
  58,13,"Moominiiney isin tuddagnak meesitteenii! Yallih farmoyta garassaanak naharat Sadqhatitte taysukumeenimik? Toh abe wayteeniih siinil tigibdee tet tekkek Yalli dambi siinih cabehik, toysa salat soolisaay, zaka acuyaay, Yallaa kee kay farmoytih amri oggola, kaadu Yalli abba haytaanamak adda yaaxigi kinni"
  58,14,"Matablannaa!Munaafiqhiinih yan maray Yalli yinqibe yahuud awlitte? Moominiiney usun siinik mayaniinaay, keenik (yahuud kinnuk) mayanin, kaadu Yallal diraabah xiibitan usun aaxaguk"
  58,15,"Yalli Qhiyaamah ayro gibdi digaala keenih massoyse, diggah usun abak sugeenim manxu Qaxumaa"
  58,16,"Usun sinni xiibaabi goobuh haysiteeniih, sinni nafsii kee sinam Yallih gitak waaseeniih, ken bursussaah tayqunxee digaalá lon akeeral"
  58,17,"Ken maaluu kee ken xalay Yallih digaalak tu keenih maxiqta, woo mari usun girâ mara usun tet addal waaran"
  58,18,"Yalli inkih ken ugusu waa ayro (Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk), Kaah xiibitaanah siinih kah xiibitan innah, diggah usun ken tanfiqeemik tû bagul yaniinim akkaluk, oobbiya! Diggah usun dirableela kinnoonum"
  58,19,"Sheetan keenil reedeeh (ken koboreeh) Yallih cusiyya ken hawweeniseh, woo mari sheetan cizbi, oobbiya! Diggah, sheetan cizbi usun kasaarite mara"
  58,20,"Diggah, Yallaa kee Yallih farmoytih amri yakeelefeeh cina mari, woo mari yuqunxuyeeh xixxibite marih loowot yanin"
  58,21,"Yalli lawcal macfuuzul madqeeh mekleh, diggah Yoo kee Yi farmoytit aysenno iyyaanam, diggah Yalli Qande li, Mayso li"
  58,22,"Nabiyow Yallaa kee ellecaboh ayró nummayse maray yallaa kee kay farmoyta cine mara yakcine mageyta, ken abbobti yakken way, hinnay ken xaylo yakken way, hinnay ken tooboko yakken way, hinnay ken kedó yakken way, Yalli woo marih sorkocobbaxittet iimaan arciseeh, isi xaquk isi catot ken maqarroyseh, kaadu jannootay guba weeqaytitte kak gexxa ken culsa usun teetil waarak, Yalli ken meqe taamoomi keenik raabiteeh, keenih abe mattaccoo kaak raabiteenih (jannatal), woo mari Yallih cizbi, oobbiya! Digga luk Yallih cizbi, usun yisillime mara"
  59,1,"Qaranwaa kee baaxô bagul tanim Yalla saytunnosseh, kaadu usuk (Yalla kinnuk) Maysoli naggaara"
  59,2,"Yalla kinni kitab marak koroosite mara (yahuuduk bani-nadiir kinnuk) naharsi koboxul le dabooqak dabboh teyyeeqem, Moominiiney isin usun sinni kalqootak xixxibaane luk yawqoonuwaanam makkalitton, kaadu usun sinni kalqoota Yallih digaalá sinnek waaselem yekkelen. Tokkel Yalli digaalá usun kak akkaluk sugeween kabuk keenit baahe, kaadu ken sorkocobbaxittet conxo qide, usun sinni qarwa sinni gabaa kee yeemeneh yan marih gabat baysaanaah yaggilen, toysa sorkocobbaxi inti le maraw isin amahal kaskassoowa mara tika"
  59,3,"Yalli Dabbó keenil mekle wannay addunyal ken digaalak yen qidim kee seewat, kaadu usun akeeral girâ digaala lon"
  59,4,"Toh keenit kah tekkem diggah usun Yallaa kee kay farmoytih amri yekeelefeeniih, cineenimi, kaadu Yallih amri yekeelefeeh cine marah Yalli gibdi digaala le"
  59,5,"Moominiiney tamiirak (nakilak), tirgiqeenim hinnay laqiibah soolak teetik cabteenim, toh Yallih fayxiiy kay amrik tekke, kaadu wohut isi amrik yewqeh yan mara xixxibisankeh abe"
  59,6,"Yalli isi farmoytal Boylak (xannabak) qeb maliinoh keenik waassa heemit (yahuuduk bani- naziir), faaris kee gaala edde ma xoxbisinniton (ma ayradditon), kinnih immay Yalli isi farmoytit isih faxe marih amol haa isi qaduwwik, kaadu Yalli ummaan iimil dudda li kinni"
  59,7,"Yalli isi farmoytal boylak (xannabak) qeb maliinoh magaaloolî marak waaseeh gacsem, toysa Yallaa kee Yallih farmoytih iimi, Kaadu Yallih farmoytal ramadah xayih yan maraay, qayxiixaay, tumaleelaa kee gexsô (musaafirtu) maray sakyi kak yiggiriqqeh iimi, Yalli tama mekla kah abem cagalah maali siinik gaddaloolâ fanal tabantabe waankeh iyyaanama, Kaadu isin Yallih farmoyti siinih baahem beetaay elle taamita, kaadu usuk sin kak waaseemik waasima, Kaadu Yallak meesita, diggah Yalli usuk gibdi digaalá lek"
  59,8,"Tonnaah tama xannabat cakki lem muhaajiriin (makkak madiinâ fanah guurume mara) tudagoytiitih yan maray, le dabooqaa kee le maaluk makki koros teyyeeqe usun Yallak rizqhii (quusii) kee kacanu gurrusak, kaadu usun Yallih diinii kee kay farmoyta qokolak yewqe mara, woo mari usun nummat yaaba maray numma yacee kinni"
  59,9,"Madiinal dabqa haysite maray muhaajiriin deqsita yamaatek naharat iimaan luk sugeh yan mari, ken fanah yeerreeh yemeete mara kicnoonuh, kaadu usun sinni sorkocobbaxittet kuuxewaynan ma geyan muhaajiriinih xannabak keenih tontocowweemih, kaadu usun sinni nafsik ken muxxusaanah tuddagnaa kee ceya keenit taniway, Kaadu Isi nafsi baaker edde yan cillaalek (cinnaané) waase mari, toysa woo mari usun yisillimeeh yoffoofe (limayeenih) mara"
  59,10,"Kaadu keenik (moominiin kinnuk) lakat yemeete mari iyyah :ni Rabbow nee kee ni toobokoh yan maray iimaan nek yookomeh dambi cabaay, ni sorkocobbaxittet yeemene marah baguumaane kee kuuxe waynan mahaysin, ni Rabbow atu diggah allaaqal-li (nacrurli), xuwawli"
  59,11,"Nabiyow matablannaa! Munaafiqhiinih yan maray kitab marak ken toobokóy koroosittek: Mucammad kee kaâ luk yan mari sin buxaaxik sin yeyyeeqe kaa tekkek diggaluk nanu siinî luk awqennooh, sin saduh inkinnah num moggolla, kaadu qeebi siinit abeenik diggah nanu sin qokolenno iyyaanam, Yalli diggah usun dirableelá kinnoonumul sumaaqitah"
  59,12,"Sinni buxaaxik yeyyeqsimeenik (yahuud kinnuk) munaafiqhiin keenî luk matawqa, kaadu qeb keenit yekkek, ken ma qoklan (ma catan). Kaadu ken qokleenik diggaluk bukah derre cabelon, tohuk wadir Yalli ken macataay ken maqokla"
  59,13,"Moominiiney, munaafiqhiin siinik abta meesi, ken sorkocobbaxittet gibiduk raqta usun Yallak aban meesik, toh kah kinnim diggah usun Yallih nabnaa kee kaal yaamineenim aaxige waa mara yekkeenimih sabbata"
  59,14,"Yahuud tikki ittaamaak qeb siinit mabta moominiiney gasoosá maroh edde tan magaaloolih addak siinit abta tet akke waytek, hinnay gidoorâ derrek siinit abta tet akke waytek, Ken umaane ken fanal gibdih, inkih ittaluk yaniinim keenik takkaleeh ken sorkocobbaxitte fixiixih tan, toh kah kinnim diggah usun kas- kassoowa mara hinnon"
  59,15,"Ama marih (yahuud kinnuk) ceelallo keenik naharat xayi uddur suge marih (makki koros kinnuk) ceelallo usun tammoyseenih sinni umaaneh galto addunyal, kaadu qansaru le digaalá lon akeeral"
  59,16,"A munaafiqhiinih abinih ceelallo sheetan ceelallo kinni, seehadaytuk koroosit iyye waqdi, tokkel woo seehadayti koroosite waqdi diggaluk anu kok bari kinniyooh, diggah anu Yallay ginô Rabbi kinnik meesita iyye"
  59,17,"Tokkel Ken nammayih ellecabo (sheetan kee korostay kay amri oggole kinnuk), diggah usun girá culaanama teetil waarak, toh teeti daalimiinih yan marih galto"
  59,18,"Yallaa kee kay farmoyta nummayse maraw! yallak meesita, usuk sin kah amrisem abtaanaah usuk sin kak waaseemik waasimtaanamal, kaadu kulli nafsí beerah (Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk) taamak tatrusem wagitay, Kaadu Yallak meesita, diggah Yalli isin abba haytaanamak adda yaaxigi kinnik"
  59,19,"Kaadu Yallaa kee kay farmoyta nummayse maraw Yalla hawweeneeh, Yalli le nafsi hawweenise marih inna makkina, woo mari usun Yallih amrik yewqe mara kinni"
  59,20,"Girâ maraa kee jannatti mara Mamassowta, jannatti mari usun yisillimeeh yessemeqqe mara (limaye mara)"
  59,21,"A Qhuraan qalel oobisinninoy, Yallak meesih rammitah, baqitah tet abaluk ten, kaadu too ceelalloola sinaamah tet naagureeh baxxaqisna cubbusa mara yakkeenî gidah"
  59,22,"Usuk Yallay nummah qibaada cakkisitay kaak sa nıīmmey haytô Yalli kak aneewaa kinni, qellittam kee tambulleem yaaxigi, Yalli usuk fulte Racmattaay, Gunê Racmatta le Rabbi kinni"
  59,23,"Usuk Yallay kaak sa nummah qibaadá cakkisita yalli kak aneewaa kinni, usuk amoytay ginó inkih yamlike, kulli boolak saytunnooweh, kulli qaybik nagaynan le, Isi ambiyaa kee isi farmoytit Nummaysé (mugqjizal) usuk isi ginoh taamoomi dacrise (loynise) kinni, Maysoliy kak ayse waana kinni, Dirkisey naqoosa inkih kah Rammitta kinni, Kaxxiina liy kaxxiina cakkisita kinni, yalli agleh kaat hayya haytaamak saytunnooweh"
  59,24,"Usuk Yallay qibaada cakkisita, usuk gineynay gino inkih gine kinni, usuk ginó Qimbisé kinni, isi gino isih elle faxe innal weeloyse kinni, saytun Rabbiy meqe migooqay tayse le kinni, qaranwal tanim kee baaxól tanim inkih kaa saytunnossa, Usuk reedal mayso li, isi ginoh abaamal naggaara"
  60,1,"Yallaa kee kay farmoytaL yeemene maraw! Yi naqboytit kee sin naqboytiitih yan mara kacnoytiitih mahaysitina, sin kee ken fanat yan kacanih sabbatah, Nabii kee muslimiin xaagu ken guddussaanamal. Nummah usun cakkik (diinii kee Qhuraanak) siinih temeeteemil koroosite marah anuk, moominiiney usun Yallih farmoyta makkak yayyaaqeeniih sin makkak yayyaaqeenihik mannal ken takcineenii? isin Yallay sin Rabbi kinnil teemeneenimî sabbatah, Moomininey isin Yi gitih gicloo kee Yi kacnih guranah yewqe mara tekkeenik, toysa Yi naqboytit kee sin naqboytiitih yan mara kacnoytiitih mahaysitina, Nabii kee muslimiin xaagu ken guddussaanamal, anu isin qellisseenim kee tuybulleenim Inkih anu aaxaguk, kaadu siinik toh abe num nummah massa le gitak makkooteh"
  60,2,"Usun siinik yeyseenik, naqboytit siinik akke lon, kaadu sinni gaboobi qidimih siinil ruubeloonuuh, sinni arrob umaanee kee xaafuh siinil ruubelon, kaadu ken innah koroositinnitoonuy faxak yenen"
  60,3,"Inkinnah sin Ramad siinih xiqam maliiy sin xaylo siinih xiqtam mali, Qhiyaamah ayró Yalli sin fan baxse le, kaadu Yalli abbá haytaanam Yabali kinni"
  60,4,"Nummah moominiiney isin Nabii Ibraahim kee moominiinik kaâ lih yen marat meqe katayyu luk tenen ken kataytaanamal, usun sinni maray koroositek: diggah nanu sin kee isin Yallâ kalah uqbuddu haytaanamak bari kinninooh, isin koroosannuk elle taniinim nengeddeeh, nee kee sin fanat qadaawat kee naqbi umman yanim tumbulleh, Yallal dubuk eemenni haytaanam fanah, kinnih immay Nabii Ibraahim isi abbak iyye maxcó kay katayyut ma culta, diggah dambi cabti koh essereyyooh, Yallak tu koh maxiqa kaak iyye waqdih maxco kinni, Ni Rabbow kol kelitneeh, koo fanah nuduure (toobah) kaadu ni Rabbow Qhiyaamah ayró gacim Koo fanah yakke"
  60,5,"Ni Rabbow! koroosite marih mokkoro (aqayyaare) nee maabin ken gabat nee digaaltaah ni diinik nee korsaanamal, kaadu ni Rabbow dambi neh cab, diggah Atu maysoliy kak ayse waana kinnito, isi ginoh abtaamal naggaar kinnitok"
  60,6,"Nummah moominiiney inni nafsil siinih xiibita immay, isin Nabii Ibraahim kee moominiinik kaâ luk yen maral meqe katayyu luk tenen ken kataytaanamal, addunyaa kee akeeral Yallak galtó qaagita marah, iimaan kee ambiyâ katayyut derre cabe numuh tugactek, diggah Yalli isi naqoosak gaddali, kulli caalatal faylali kinni"
  60,7,"Moominiiney yalli sin fan kee makki korosuk sin xaynak isin qaduwwi kak tekken marî fanat kacanu heele usun islaam diinit culaanamal, Yalli usuk ummaan iimih duddali, Yalli isi naqoosah dambi cabti li xuwaw li kinni"
  60,8,"Moominiiney yalli diini taagah qeebi siinit abeweeh, sin dabooqak sin ayyaaqewe marah meqem abtaanaah qadaalat keenih abtaanamak sin ma waasa, diggah Yalli qadaalat le mara kicnih"
  60,9,"Cagalah Yalli kacanuk sin kak waasam, diini taagah qeb siinit abeeh sin dabooqak sin yeyyeeqeeh, sin mayyaaqal sitta qokole (cate) mara qokoltaanaah takcineenimi, ken (koros kinnuk) qoklaah ken yikcine mari, toysa too mari usun sinni nafsi koroosannut yudlume mara kinni"
  60,10,"Yallaa kee kay farmoytal yeemene maraw! Teemene sayyó guuroh anuk (koros baaxook Muslimiin baaxó fan) siinil temeetek, toysa ken mokkora (iqiyyira) iimaan numma keenik taaxigeenimkeh, Yalli ken iimaanih numma nagay yaaxigek. tokkel Teemene sayyó kinnim keenik teexegeenik, toysa ken baqoltiy korosuh tanî fanah ken magacsina. Teemene sayyó digibih koros ken abittam ma xiqtaay calaali hinna, kaadu koros teemene sayyo digibih abittam ma xiqtaay keenih calaali hinna, kaadu teemene sayyóh baqoltiy korosuh raqteh yarasak (mahrik) keenih yeceenî sugeenim maaluk keenih acuya, kaadu ken galtoota (mahri kinnuk) keenih taceeniih ken digbissaanam dambi siinil mali, kaadu moominiiney siinik koroosite agabih gennaaqó maloowitinaay, isin siinik koroositeh yan agabul yarasak (maharik) teceenim maaluk korosul esserita, kaadu koros ken agabuy yuslumel yeceenih sugen yaras esserittay moominiinil, Tama aayatal edde yabne mekla is Yallih meklay usuk sin fanal mekla elle abe inna kinnik ma cinina, Yalli yaaxigi kaak qellittam matan, usuk isi abtol naggaara"
  60,11,"Kaadu sin agabuk tuy diinik korraqte koros fan eleelitteeh, woo koros keenil maharik teceenim siinih aceewaytek, tohih lakal ken gaaddeeniih, xannaba orbisseenik, agbi kak gexe marah acuya xannabak usun yeceenih innah tanim maharik, kaadu Yallay isin elle teemeneenih taniinik meesita"
  60,12,"Kee a Nabiyow! Teemene sayyo kol temeetek xagana koh culak, Yallat agleytah tu heewaanamal, kaadu garqó abe waanaah, dalwa abe waanaah, sinni xaylo qide waanamal, kaadu bicsiten almummaa (ererii) kee diraabah ken baqolti xalewayte xaylo keenih orbise waanamal, kaadu ken kah amrissi hayte maqaanel ku amri cine waanamal, toysa xagna keenih culaay Yalla dambi cabti keenih esser, diggah Yalli dambi cabti li, xuwawli kinni"
  60,13,"Yallaa kee kay farmoytal Yeemeneh yan maraw! Yalli yinqibeeh kah ceere mara (koros kinnuk) Makcininaay qokoluh ken ma haysitina, nummah usun akeerâ galtók yobboodeenihik, korosuk magooqal yan mari Yallih Racmatak kah yobboode innah akeerak"
  61,1,"Qaranwal tanim kee baaxô bagul tanim inkih Yalla saytunnosseh, usuk (Yalla kinnuk) maysoliiy abaamal naggaar kinni"
  61,2,Yallaa kee kay farmoyta nummayse maraw! Xaganay duuduse waytoonu waytaanaa kee hinnay abinat asse waytoonu waytan maxco macah ittaanaa
  61,3,Tama taamay abe waytoonu waytaana Yallih garil naqabuh tembeh
  61,4,Diggah Yalli massowwu iyyeh isi gital qeebi abah yan mara kicna. Usun xisoosay exefut (xakabut) tanih innah anuk
  61,5,"Nabiyow isi mara Ķassis Nabii Muusa isi marak iyye waqdi: yi maraw ada macah yoo abtaanaa nummah anu Yallih farmoytay siinî fanah rubsume kinniyom yok taaxigeenihik? Tokkel usun cakkik makķooten waqdi, Yalli ken sorkocobbaxitte makkoyseh tirtok, Yalli kay taaqatak yewqe mara tirri mahaa"
  61,6,"Kaadu Nabiyow! Isi marah, Nabii Qiisa maryam baxi: israa- iil xayloy diggah anu Yallih farmoytay siinî fanah rubsumey, yok naharal yemeete tawraat kitaabal temeetem nummaysak, kaadu yallih farmoytay yok lakal yamaatey migaq kak Acmad kinnil Mucammad {zsak sin aytikumusak (berrekisak) emeete iyye waqdi keenih cus, tokkel Nabii Mucammad zsa baxxaqqa le astooti keenih luk yemeete waqdi, tah baabay baxxaqqa le atu neh luk temeetem kaak iyyen"
  61,7,"(Yallal dirab ginnaasiteh yan numuk dulmih iyyi gacaa, usuk islaamaninnâ fanah seecimak? num kaak ma gaca ), kaadu Yalli koroosannut isi nafsi yudlume mara tirri mahaa"
  61,8,"Yallih noori (Kay diini kinnuk) sinni afittet bargusaanam (badisaanam) faxan, Yalli isi noori (kay diini kinnuk) duuduséh koros tanqibe way"
  61,9,"Usuk Yallay isi farmoyta (Nabii Mucammad ġz;akíķkinnuk) ruube tirtoo (Qhuraan kinnuk) kee nummâ diinil (Islaam diini kinnuk) ummaan diinik iro kaa raaqisamkeh, Yallat agleyta haa mari yanqibe way"
  61,10,Kee Yalla nımmmayse maraw! qansarissa digaalak sin naggossa Tellemmo (kabxa) Siinih maay ascassoo
  61,11,"Yallaa kee kay farmoytal taamineeniih, Yallih gital tangicilleenimi sinni maaluu kee sinni nafsih, toh kayrih siinih aysuk raqta isin woh yaaxige mara tekkeenik"
  61,12,"Moominiiney toh abteenik, Yalli sin dambitte siinih cabeleeh, jannootay guba weeqaytitte kak gexxa sin culse le, kaadu meqe dabooqay Qadni deqsitta jannootal tanil dabqih sin heele, toh kaxxa asallam kee affaafa (limayiyya)"
  61,13,"Kaadu moominiiney akittoy kicintoonu liton, toh Yallak catoo kee makki fakimiy xayi kinni, kaadu Nabiyow tama muxxol moominiin aytikumus (berrakis)"
  61,14,"Yallaa kee kay farmoytal yeemeneh yan maraw! yallih diini cata mara tika, Nabii Qiisa Maryam baxi cawaariyyiinik (Yalli Qiisah doore wakliytitte kinnuk) kah iyye innah: Yallih diinih sinam seecaah yallih diini qoklaamah iyye yoo cataa? iyye waqdi, cawaariyyuun deqsita mari kaal gacisak :Yallih diini cattam nee iyyen, tokkel Israa-iil xaylok horta teemeneeh, horta keenik koroositteh, tokkel keenik yeemeneh yan mara ken naqboytiitil ken catneeh, usun mayso le marah maacisen sinni naqboytiitil"
  62,1,"Qaranwal tanim kee baaxô bagul tanim inkih Yalla saytunnossah, Usuk amoytay ginó inkih yamlike kinni, usuk kulli boolak saytunih, usuk isi reedal mayso li, isi abtol naggaara"
  62,2,"Yalla kinni toogimah yan marâ fanah farmoytay (Nabii Mucammad frae kinnuk) keenik yaniy Yallih Qhuraanih aayoota keenil yakriye keenih rubtem, kaadu koroosannuu kee dambittek ken saytunnoysaah, Qhuraan kee Sunna (cadiis kinnuk) ken barsa, usun kaak (Nabii kinnuk) naharal cakkik baxxaqqa le makoh addat sugen"
  62,3,"Kaadu keenik aka maray ken matre weey uxih amaate weeh kaa ruube (qarab yakkoonu, gersi mara yakkoonu), Yalli maysoli, naggaara"
  62,4,"Woo Nabiih ruubiyyi, Yallih muxxooy kay acway isi naqoosak, isih faxa marah tet yacee. Kaadu Yalli kaxxa muxxoli, maggo acwali"
  62,5,"Tawraatal taamitaanamal dirkisimeeh tohuk lakal elle taamite wee marih ceelallo, dananay elle tanim kak aaxige waa kitooba yakkuqeh ceelallo kinni, manxu qax umaa Yallih astootiy Nabii Mucammad ĵzsaseńíķ numma tascasse dirabboysah yan marak ceelallo, kaadu Yalli daalimiinih yan mara tirri mahaa"
  62,6,"Ixxic nabyow: kee yahuudute maraw sinaamak addaak Yallih kacnoytit sinni tekkeleenik, toysa raba qaagitaay faxa, numma yacee mara tekkeenik"
  62,7,"Kaadu usun inkinnah kaa (raba) maqaagitaanaay, mafaxan ken gaba umaanek tuysukumeemih sabbatah, kaadu Yalli daalimiinih yan mara yaaxigi kinni"
  62,8,"Nabiyow Keenik ixxic: diggah woo rabay isin kak kuddaana diggah usuk siinit angoorowe le, tohuk lakal qelittaah tambulleem yaaxigî fanah gacsimetton, tokkel yalli abak suggu itteenim siinih warseleeh, sin elle galtele"
  62,9,"Yallaa Kee kay farmoyta nummayse maraw! Adan aba num jumqatti ayro jumqattâ Salaatah adan aba waqdi, toysa isin Yallih kassitî fanah (kutbaa kee salat kinnuk) gexaay tellemmó caba, toh abtaanam kayrih siinih aysuk raqta sinni nafsih meqem yaaxige mara tekkeenik"
  62,10,"Tokkel jumqatta salaatak gaba kaltan waqdi, toysa baaxól fixiixaay, Yallih rizqhi guransita, kaadu Yalla maggom cusa (kasa), yasillimeeh yaffoofe (limaye) mara takkeeni gideh"
  62,11,"Kaadu muslimiinik tu tellemmo ablee kee hinnay addunyâ doklaa kee tet bilhada able yekken waqdi, Nabiyow teetî fanah sissikuk kok fixiixeeniih soolak koo caben. Nabiyow! keenik ixxic: Yallih garil tanim doklaa kee tellemmok (kabxa kinnuk) kayrih aysuk siinih raqta, Yalli usuk rizqhi acuyyu haa marak inkih yaysi kinnik isin rizqhi kaal esserita"
  63,1,"Nabiyow Munaafiqhiin kol tamaate waqdi, sinni arrabat diggah, atu yallih farmoyta kinnitoomuh sumaaqitnah itte, diggah Yalli atu kay farmoyta kinnitom yaaxigeh kaadu Yalli sumaaqitah diggah, munaafiqhiin dirableela kinniimil"
  63,2,"Munaafiqhiin sinni xiibaabi gob kee reebuh haysitteeh, Yallih gitak sinni nafsii kee sinam waasseh, diggah usun abak sugeenim manxu qaxuma taamaay"
  63,3,"Toh kah kinnim usun arrabal yeemeneeniih, tohuk lakal sorkocobbaxal koroositeenih, edde Yalli ken sorkocobbaxitte iimaanak alfeh koroositeenimih sabbatah, toysa usun maqaane keenik edde tanim mayaaxigaanaay edde maradan"
  63,4,"Kaadu tama munaafiqhiin table waqdi ken xagarih maqaane kot meqeeh, tassakooteh, kaadu usun yaaben ken tekkek, ken yab ankacissah, ken lubbitte iimaan kee kassi boolak gexxaamah hununuh gidaaral kelsime guruumudih innah gacak, usun conxô gibdah ummaan xongoló sinnil raddem yakkalen, Nabiyow! Usun nummah ku qaduwwik atu keenik daccarsim (cibbarsim). Yalli isi racmatak ken yayxaarayik usun tirtô gitak mannal makkootaanaa"
  63,5,"Yallih farmoyti dambi cabti Yallal siinih esserâ gideh ama keenik iyyan waqdi (munaafiqhiin kinnuk), sinni moyyaayi anqasah esgeyyi haan, Kaadu nabiyow usun kaxxamariinitak ken kah sectaamat derre cabah ken table"
  63,6,"Nabiyow! tama munaafiqhiinih dambi cabti essertam kee hinnay keenih essere waytam keenil inki gide, diggah Yalli dambi inkinnah keenih macaba, diggah yalli isi taaqatak yewqe mara cakki gital tirri mahaa"
  63,7,"Munaafiqhiin kinni: Yallih farmoytih xaqul yan marah (muhaajiriin kinnuk) masruf maaciinaay maskamina ittem usun fixixxi iyyaanam fanah, qaranwaa kee baaxô kadnooniiy quusik ken addal enni ittam dubuk Yalli le, kinnih immay munaafiqhiin woh mataaxigaay edde maradda"
  63,8,"Ta munaafiqhiin: nanu madiinâ fanah nuduurek, mayso le mari (munaafiqhiin kinnuk) gacaah xixxibaane le mara (moominiin kinnuk) teetik ayyaaqele itte. Yalli keenil gacisak: mayso lem Yallaa kee kay farmoytaay, moominiini, kinnih immay munaafiqhiin woh mataaxiga"
  63,9,"Kee yeemene maraw! sin maaluu kee sin xaylo yallih cusiyyaa kee kay qibaadak Sin agxise waytay, kaadu toh abe mari, toysa too mari usun baxaysite (kasaarite) mara"
  63,10,"Kaadu moominiiney siinih neceemik tu kayri gital acuya, siinik numuk teynal rabi yamaatek naharal, tokkel usuk rabi kaah yamaate waqdi nadaamitak:Yi Rabbow dago wakti rabak yoo wadirrossaamal, tokkel inni maaluk sadaqhat attacayyuk eneeh meqe marih num akkuk en iyya"
  63,11,"Kaadu Yalli nafsi mawadirroysa rabi kaah yamaate waqdi, kaadu Yalli maqaanee kee umaanek abba haytaanamak adda yaaxigi kinniih sin elle galtele"
  64,1,"Yalla qaranwal tanim kee baaxô bagul tanim inkih kaa saytunnossa, usuk dudda le reeda leeh, qax meqe fayla le, usuk ummaan iimil dudda li kinni"
  64,2,"Usuk Yallay sin gine kinni, korostay yallih inkittinaane yangadde siinik yaniih, moomintuy kaa nummaysay kay diinil taamita siinik yanih, Yalli isin abba haytaanam yabali kinniih tu kaak ma qellittaay sin elle galte le"
  64,3,"Yalli qaranwaa kee baaxó cakkil gineeh sin tayse weelot weeloyseeh usuk sin weeloola qaxa yeymeeqe, Qhiyaamah ayró siinik madaara kaâ fanah takke"
  64,4,"Yalli yaaxigeh qaranwaa kee baaxóh addat tanim, kaadu yaaxigeh qellissaanam kee taybulleenim, kaadu Yalli alilwah addat tanim yaaxigi kinni"
  64,5,"Ta korosey Siinik duma Koroositê suge marih (Qaad kee Samuuduuy.....) xaagi Siinih mamattoo? Tokkel usun sinni koroosannuu kee sinni uma taamah digaalá tammoyseenih, kaadu usun akeeral ken qansarissa digaalá lon"
  64,6,"Tama digaaláy addunyal keenit tekke keenit kah tekkem, ken farmoytiitiy Yalli keenih ruube baxxaqqooqi le astooti keenih luk amaatuk sugteeh, usun tokkel woh assacakkuk: nee seehada tirri haytaa? Iyyeeniih, koroositeeniih, iimaanat derre caben, Yalli usuk ken iimaanak gaddaliteh. Yalli isi ginók gaddali numuh ma ceyta, usuk isi abtol fayla li kinni"
  64,7,"Koroosite mari rabak lakal inkinnah magooqak ugsume waanaah awqe waanam yekkeleeniih warsiten, Nabiyow! Keenik ixxic: yeey inni Rabbil xiibita immay isin sinni magooqak ugsumettoonuuh awqetton, tohuk lakal isin addunyal taamoomik abteenim siinih warselon, Yalli sin magooqak sin ugsaah sin taamal sin galtam kaal xabcinih"
  64,8,"Toysa Yallaa kee kay farmoytaa kee Nooriy (Qhuraan kinnuk) oobisne nummaysa, Yalli abba haytaanamak adda yaaxagi kinni"
  64,9,"Maagoynah ayroy Yalli sin kee gino inkih edde gaaboysa kassita, toh baxaysitiyyi edde yambullee ayróy mariiy marak edde muxxuta kinni, kaadu Yalla nummayseeh, meqem abite num, Yalli kay dambitte kaak duugaah, jannootay guba weeqaytitte kak gexxa kaa culsa, umman tet addal waarak, too jannootal aban waariyyi kaxxa affaafaay kaxxa asallaame (limayiyya) kinni"
  64,10,"Kaadu koroositeeh, Ni astooti dirabboyse mari, woo mari girâ mara tet addal waarak, is manxu umá gacsimeyna"
  64,11,"Umaane inki num maxagta Yallih meklaay kay idini akke waytek, kaadu woh Yallak is xagtem nummayse num, Yalli kay sorkocobbaxa tirri haa wohul yisbireemih taagah, Yalli ummaanim yaaxigi kinni"
  64,12,"Kaadu Sinaamey Yallih amri oggolaay, Kay farmoytih amri oggola, ama oggolut derre cabteenik, toysa cagalah Ni farmoytal tanim baxxaqqa le gudduysiyya kinni"
  64,13,"Yalli inkittu kaak sa qibaada cakkisita Yalli mayan, tokkel moominiin dibuk sinni caagiidah Yallal kelittay"
  64,14,"Yallaa Kee kay farmoyta nummayseh yan maraw! diggah sin agabuu kee sin xaylok tuk teyna sin qaduwwik keenik cibbarsima, kaadu usun baaheenimik qafu keenih abteeniih ken elle kataate wayteeniih, keenih cabteeniih ken tustureenik, toysa diggah Yalli dambi cabti li xuwaw li kinni"
  64,15,"Cagalah sin maaluu kee sin xaylo siinih aqayyaare (mokkoro), Yalli kaxxa galto le (kay oggol doorite marah)"
  64,16,"Toysa moominiiney Yallak meesita duddu haytaanamal, kaadu yallaa kee kay farmoyta sin kah sectam oobbiyaay, ken amri oggola, kaadu Yalli siinih yecee maaluk sadaqhat acuya sin nafsih taysehik, isi nafsih cillaalek dacrise mari, toysa too mari usun yisillime (limaye) mara"
  64,17,"Isin Sinni maalu yallah meqe gacsah (likaacih) teceenik, Yalli sin maalu siinih xirrib xirribuh siinih heeleeh dambi siinih cabele, Yalli tu yetteccee marah kaxxa faatoli xiqli kinni"
  64,18,"Yalli qellitti ittam kee umbullu ittam inkih yaaxigi kinni, usuk isi reedal maysoli, isi abtol naggaara"
  65,1,"Nabiyow! Koo kee moominiin sinni Agabu cabtaanam faxxan waqdi, toysa ken qiddâ fanah afkanuk miyangalit anee kalah taahirih anuk ken cabaay, qidda loowaay dacrisa, kaadu yallay sin Rabbi kinnik meesita, isin qidda tamurruqeh gide ken (caben agabu kinnuk) dabooqak ken mayyaaqina, kaadu usun sinnih awqe woonay baxxaqqa itta umaanéy qax uma abeenih akke waytek, too edde yabnem Yallih madqooqiy yalli isi naqoosah madqe kinni. kaadu Yallih madqooqit caddok tatre num toysa nummah usuk isi nafsi yudlume numu. barra cabe numow Yalli Tohuk lakal atu cubewayta caagid abaway mataaxigak"
  65,2,"Tokkel usun (agabu kinnuk) qiddà keenik edde tamurruqe waktit xayyooweenik, toysa isin gennaaqoh ken gacsita sharqi elle xiqsiisa innal meqe gexsitih keenî luk gexsitak, hinnay keenik baxsimaay ken cakkķki keenih duudusa sharqi elle xiqsiisa innal, kaadu ken cabteenik hinnay ken gacsitteenik siinik qadaalat leeh diini kak tassakooten namma num sumaaqisaay, sumaaqita maraw! Isin sumaq gudduysaay yallah kaa aba, too Yalli sin kah amriseh yanim kassiisaanaah elle kaskassowtam yallaa kee ellecaboh ayro nummayse mara kinni, Yallak meesitaah Yalli kaa kah amrisem abaah, usuk kaa kak waaseemik waasima num Yalli kulli ceyak mawqa kaah aba"
  65,3,"Kaadu Yalli rizqhi usuk kak akkale waa kabuk kaah yacee, kaadu Yallal kelte num toysa usuk kaa xiqah, Diggah Yalli isi amri duudusa Rabbi kinni, nummah Yalli ummaan iimih yimixxige udduruy is kak tatre wayta teeti hee"
  65,4,"Sin agabuy cabbiimey miyangali kak yiggiriqqeey miyangalik yobboode, isin ken qiddat agaywaagitteenik ken qidda sidiica alsa kinni, kaadu qunxa sayyóy miyangali baahe waytâ qiddà tonna, agabuk Bagut lagbî qiddah wakti, usun bagut lon xalay oobisaanama edde taadem. Yallak meesitah yan numuh, Yalli kay caagid addunyaay akeeral kaah xabbacoysah"
  65,5,"Woo cabtii kee qiddak edde yabneh nanim, Yallih madqay Yalli siinil oobise kinni, Yallak meesitah yan numuh Yalli kay dambi kaah duugaah kay galto kaah yaynabeh"
  65,6,"Sin agabuk cabbiime agabu Sinnih dabqah elle aninnaan ikkel dabqah ken hayisa, usun qiddat yaniinih gide isin elle duddan innal, kaadu dabqaa kee masruf keenil ceyissoonuh ada ken maabinaay ken mabiyaakina, kaadu usun bagut le agabu yekkeenik, toysa masruf keenih aba bagut lon xalay oobissi haanam fanah, tokkel usun woo xaylo siinih qarseenik (yeyseexxeenik), toysa ken cawal keenih acuya, kaadu mariiy mara siinik maqaane edde taniimih amrisay ittâ luk malisak, kaadu isin itta wayteeniih itta geytaanam siinil tigibdeek toysa gersittoy inâ kalah tani kaah qarissay (taysaxxay)"
  65,7,"Gaddalih yan numuy maali farakka le isi barray cabee kee isi baxa duddak leh gidel yasrafay, kaadu tumaliy le rizqhi ceya elle baahe, Yalli rizqhik kaah yeceeh gidel yasrafay, Yalli hebeltô nafsil duude waam mahanna rizqhik kaah yeceeh gide kaal haa kaa akke waytek, Yalli ceyaa kee gibdâ lakal maali farakkaa kee gaddaliino heele"
  65,8,"Makina magaalah maraay, isi Rabbih amrii kee kay farmoytiitih amrî cinal caddok taturtem. Edde luk gibdi fokkaaqoh ken fokkaqne, kaadu gibdi digaalay qaxumah ken digaalle"
  65,9,"tokkel usun sinni uma taamah ellecaboh digaalá tammoyseenih, kaadu ken koroosannuu kee ken uma taamah ellecabo finqaa kee kasaara tekke"
  65,10,"Yalli gibdi digaala keenih massoyse (makkiseh), toysa Yalla nummaysech, kasle maraw Yallak meesita.nummah Yalli Qhuraanay sin edde kassiisa siinil oobisek"
  65,11,"Yalli isi farmoytay Yallih aayootay baxxaqqaley cakkii kee deedal ittak baxissa siinil yakriye siinih ruube, Yallaa kee kay farmoytal yeemeneeh meqe taamoomi abbaasita mara diteetak diifû fanah yayyaaqenkeh, Yallal yeemeneeh meqe taama abbaasite mara jannootay guba weeqaytitte kak gexxa ken culsa, usun umman tet addal waarak, nummah Yalli jannatal rizqhi keenih yeymeeqeeh farakka keenih elle hee"
  65,12,"Yalla kinni dubuk malcina qaran ginteeh, baaxók kay innah yan malciin gintem, Yallih wacyii kee kay amriiy kay mekla ken fanal obta, sinaamey diggah Yalli usuk ummaan iimih duddali kinnim taaxigeenimkeh, kaadu diggah Yallih ixxiga ummaan iimit maroh tanim taaxigeenimkeh"
  66,1,"Nabiyow! Yalli koh calalloysem isi nafsil macah carammossaa, isi agabih leedaa kee kacanu gurrusak? Yalli dambi cabti li xuwaw li kinni"
  66,2,"Nummah Yalli moominiiney sinni xiibaabik edde calallowtaanam siinih madqeh, kaffaara teetik taceenimil, Yalli sin awlaytuy sin qoklay sin caagiida gabat le kinni, usuk siinih meqem yaaxigi, isi abtol naggaara"
  66,3,"Cusey! Nabii isi agbuk baalî luk walalah tutuccu iyye waqdi, edde luk is tama yab warisseeh, Yalli woh kaa yuybullee waqdi, tu kak tet yiysixxigeeh, tu teetik kak cabeh edde luk woo xaagu teetih warse waqdi a xaagu iyyi koh warsee kaak itte? Yallay isi naqoosa qellissem yaaxigih yaniy, adda yaaxigiy tu kak qellite wayta yoh warse teetik iyye"
  66,4,"Sin nammay (Qaa-ishaa kee Cafsa kinnuk) Yallâ fanah gacten sin tekkek nummah sin sorkocobbaxitte Yallih farmoyti faxe waamâ fanah qeegteh, kaadu sin nammay usuk faxe waamal itta kaal (Nabii kinnuk), catteenik, diggah Yalli usuk kay awlaytuy kaa cata kinni, kaadu Jibriil kee moominiinik meqe mari kay awlaay kaa catah, wohuk lakal inkih tan malayka kay awlaay kay cateyniiti"
  66,5,"Diggah Kay Rabbi usuk (Nabii kinnuk) sin cabe kaa tekkek siinik yayseh yan agabu kaah ciggiilisam abele, Yallaa kee kay farmoytih amrih rammitaah kay famoyta nummaysah yan agabu kaah abele, Yalli ken kah amrisem oggola agabuy taaqatak Yalli kicnim abaah dambik kaal gaca kaah abele, Yallah maggo qibaada abaah sooma agabuy tu kak agabuuy tu kak baxuw kinni kaah abele"
  66,6,"Yallaa kee kay farmoyta nummayse maraw! sinni nafsii kee sinni mara giray sinam kee xeet edde ursan bocoh kak tanik reebisa, tet amol dacayrih (xagroh) malaykay nacrur sinniy cayla le tan, usun Yalli ken kah amrisem macinaanaay usun kah amrisimeenim abaanaah yagdubeenih"
  66,7,"Kee koroosite maraw! Ta saaku malkittaanam maallinaay ma gurrusina, cagalah isin elle galtimtaanam addunyal abak sugteenim kinnik keenik iyyan"
  66,8,"Yallaa kee kay farmoyta nummayse maraw! Abten dambik Yallâ fanah saytun madaarah uduura, sin Rabbi sin uma taamoomih dambi siinik duugelek, kaadu jannootay guba weeqaytitte kak gexxa sin culselek, Yalli Nabii kee kaâ lih yeemene mara edde ayqunxeewaah wacarriysewaay, Noori keenik foocittee kee migdittel gexay, usun ni Rabbow ni noori neh duudusaay ni dambi neh cab edde iyyan ayro, diggah atu ummaan iimil dudda li kinnitok"
  66,9,"Kee tá Nabiyow! Koros kee munaafiqhiinil ingicillaay, caagid keenil iygibdiy, keenik orbeyná jahannam girak, toh manxu umá gacsimeynaay"
  66,10,"Yalli koroosite marah Nabii Nuuc barraa kee Nabii Luut barrâ ceelallo yoogore. Too namma barra Ni naqoosak meqe namma naqsih gubat sugteeh, ken nammay diinil ganeenih, tokkel too nīqmma naqasi Yallih digaalak tu keenih ma xiqinna, kaadu ken nammayak: (namma barra kinnuk) gira cula girá, cula marâ lih keenik iyyen"
  66,11,"Kaadu Yalli moominiiniy Yallah qibaada caglisseh caalatal ceelallo yoogoreeh baxxaqise Firqawni barrâ caalatal, yi Rabbow! Ku xaqul jannat addal qari yoh xisaay, firqawnaa kee kay uma taamak yoo naggos, kaadu daalimiinih yan marih umaanek yoo naggos itte waqdi"
  66,12,"Kaadu Yalli yeemeneh yan marâå ceelallo yoogoreeh baxxaqise, Maryam Qimraan baxay isi sammo dalwak dacrissê caalatal, tokkel Yalli Jibriil amriseh diriqik moyya kak culta aracak fuffu teetik ixxic kaak iyyeeh, woo fuftó tet maxax (maganat) toofeeh wonna luk is Nabii Qiisal tussukuqqeeh, is isi Rabbî qangor kee kay kitooba nummassech, Yalla oggola maray qibaada kaah caglisak tiyak teyna tekke"
  67,1,"Yallay addunyaa kee akeerâ reeda gabat le nabaah kay kayri kay ginoh amol yemeggeh, kaadu usuk ummaanimil qamal geyto li kinni"
  67,2,"Usuk rabaa kee manó gine rabbi kinni sinaamey sin yaqiyyiruh, taamâ maqaanéh siinik yayse num yamixxiguh, kaadu usuk mayso li tu kaak mataysaay, dambi cabti li kinni, kaal yuduure marah"
  67,3,"Usuk Yallay malcina qaran sittak amol inkigide akkuk gine kinni. wagta numow Yallih ginót hebelto fulaa kee sissinaané matablak, tokkel qaraanâ fanah wagitto gacam gacisey, usuk tama nabna luk baquu kee qanxixu kaat maay tablee"
  67,4,"Tohuk lakal Kaadu wagitto qaraanâ fanah namma adda gacam gacisey, wagta numow kunti qunxaane luk bura luk kol aduurelek, Yallih ginot hebelto cooca able kalah, is wagittok taqabba itteh"
  67,5,"Yalli nummah, xiibitak addunyâ qaran ifta cutuukat bilisneeh, sheytoonâ geedano tet abne, kaadu akeeral girâ digaalá keenih massosne axcuk"
  67,6,"Kaadu isi Rabbil koroosite mari jahannam digaalá le, kaadu is manxu uma gacsimeynaay"
  67,7,"Usun teetit qambisiman waqdi, teetiy faciyyi gibdah muxxak kaxxa xongoló yaabben"
  67,8,"Jahannam korosuh abte naqbih gibdah taggiggiriqqeem xayossu hayte, sinaamak horta tet addal qambisiminnaan waqdi tet loynissa malayka addunyal ta digaalak sin meesiisa farmoyti siinih mamattoo axcuk ken esserta"
  67,9,"Yeey, nummah meesiise nel yemeeteh iyyan, tokkel kaa dirabbosneeh, Yalli hebeltoh iimiy oobise mali inne, isin tu hinniton kaxxa fingqat yan mara akke wayteenik"
  67,10,"Kaadu usun woh aalamuk: nummah nanu nek iyyaanam cakki maabbah aabbinninoy, hinnay tu raaqisa kas le mara akkķinninoy, urta giráh mara akkuk manannino iyyen"
  67,11,"Tokkel usun sinni dambi (koroosannu kinnuk) yeelemeeniih, tokkel urta girah marah finqaa kee Yallih Racmatak yaxxeereenim tanay"
  67,12,"Diggah, ablekal sinni Rabbik meesita mari, dambi cabtii kee kaxxa galató le"
  67,13,"Sinni maxcó qellissoonu, hinnay taybulloonu, Yalli sin alilwat tanim yaaxigi kinni"
  67,14,"Gino gineh yan Rabbi mannal aaxige waa qellissaanam kee taybulleenim? Usuk xuwawli, adda yaaxigi kinnik"
  67,15,"Kaa kinni baaxó siinih madabah sahhalossemik tet deraafel gexaay kay rizqhi akuma, kaadu ugut kaâ fanah yakke Qhiyaamah ayro"
  67,16,Korosey isin sinni teemeneenii qaraanal yan Rabbi Baaxó siinil xuumusaamak is gibdi angoyyih tangayye waqdi
  67,17,Hinnak isin sinni teemeneenii qaraanal yan Rabbi arraaqi le caacay siinil ruubaamak? toysa korosey isin yi meesisso le inna aaxigetton digaalá tablen waqdi
  67,18,"Yalli xiibiteh nummah, keenik naharsi mari sinni farmoytit dirabboyseemil, tokkel ken essecekkehik yi assacokki manna keenil teellee? Ken bayisne wagqdi"
  67,19,"Kaadu mayablaanaa keenik amól tan haadá galwá fakta waqdii kee xambaqta waqdi takkem? raddaamak tet tabbixeeh dacrissam matan Racmaan kinni Rabbi akke waytek, diggah usuk ummaanim yabali kinni"
  67,20,"Hinnak korosey tah iyyaay tah ni mara kak ittaanaah sin cattam? yalli sin digaalam faxek, Racmaan kinni Rabbi akke waytek, koroosite mari tû bagul mayan sheetan keenit abah yan duquurisiyya akke waytek"
  67,21,"Hinnak ah iyyaay, Yalli isi rizqhi siinik yibbixek siinih taceem? Wonna hinnay koroosite mari Nummaak caddok tatur kee cakkik giltaanamih bagul yeedeen"
  67,22,Tokkel Foocah radak gexa num yayse innaa tirtóh hinnay massowwu iyyeh massa le gitat gexa num yaysee
  67,23,"Nabiyow!Keenik ixxic :Yalla kinni suge waytik sin gintem, kaadu aytiy edde taabbeenii kee intiitay edde tableeniiy, sorkocobbaxittéy edde kaskassowtaana siinih gintem, korosey Yallih niqmatak faatittaanam siinik dagoh"
  67,24,"Ixxic Nabiyow:Yalla kinni baaxô bagul sin ginteeh sin fixiixissem, kaadu kaâ fanah gaaboysimetton cisab kee galtoh"
  67,25,"Kaadu koros: axagni maa waqadiiy isin numma yacee mara tekkeenik itta"
  67,26,"Nabiyow:cagalah, Qhiyaama edde solta waktih ixxiga Yallih garil tan, kaadu cagalah anu baxxaqqa le meesiise kinniyo keenik ixxic"
  67,27,"Koros digaalá xayyowtem table waqdi, koroosite marak foocitte taameh, tah teetiy esseritak assaxeeruk sugteeni keenik iyyan"
  67,28,"Ixxic Nabiyow korosuk:yoh warisa! Yalli yoo kee yollih yan mara qidek hinnay neh xuwaaweh nee udurruse yekkek, koros iyyi cateleeh qansarissa digaalák"
  67,29,"Ixxic Nabiyow: usuk Racmaan kinni Rabbi nanu kaa nummasneeh kaal kelitne, tokkel xayuk aaxigetton digaalá obtuwayta waqdi cakki gitak baxxaqqa le hoxat tanim sin kinnik nee kinnim"
  67,30,"Ixxic Nabiyow: yoh warisay! sin lee baaxot fuuqunteh maacissek, iyyi siinih baaheleeh daritta leey gexxa? (num mabaaha Yallak sá)"
  68,1,Nuun- (edde faxem Yalli yaaxige) Yalli Qhalam kee yaktube mari uktubbu haamal xiibite
  68,2,Atu Nabiyow ku Rabbi koh yecee niqmatih sabbatah cabuli akke waytaamal xiibite
  68,3,Kaadu diggah atu galtoy aggiriqqe sinni litoomul xiibite
  68,4,Kaadu diggah atu naba caalat maqaaneh bagul tantoomul xiibite
  68,5,"Xayi waktit Nabiyow atu ablettooh, usun (koros kinnuk) ablelon"
  68,6,Siinik cabulem kinni num abletton koo kinnik ken kinnim
  68,7,"Diggah ku Rabbi usuk ixxigah yayse Rabbi kinni kay gitak makkooteh yan marat, kaadu usuk ixxigah yayse Rabbi kinni kay gital tirri iyyeeh kaal diggi iyye marat"
  68,8,Toysa isi diinil diggi xicaay moggolin koo kee Qhuraan dirabboyse mara
  68,9,"Kaadu Nabiyow atu usun faxe waanamak tu cabtaamal keenih xabbacowtek, usun kaadu koh xabbacoowaanam faxan"
  68,10,Kaadu ummaan numwy xiiba maggoy bayoytah yanih yab moggolin
  68,11,Cami maggo numwy sittal hayah sinam fanal gexaah yangagayyeh yab moggolin
  68,12,"Cinnaaneynay kayri celli haytam gibdi waasoh waasay caddok taturlih yaniy, dambi maggoh yab moggolin"
  68,13,"Koroosanni maggah Sorkocobbaxi kak kafe numvuy, tohuk lakal ilmoytah yani kinni"
  68,14,"Usuk a weelot kah weeloysimem, maali gaddaa kee xalay mangintah sabbata"
  68,15,"Ni-aayoota (Qhuraan kinnuk) kaal tankirriyime waqdi, ah naharsi marih hayyayyoona iyya anqasah"
  68,16,Xayi uddurul (waktil) kate waa bedu kaak heenno sanal
  68,17,"Diggah nanu makki mara qulul kee qabaarat niqiyyire bustaan mara kah niqiyyire innah, usun subci wakti kay caxammixu tumaleelak qellut yargiqoonu waanamah xiibiten waqdi"
  68,18,Yalli faxek maxaccinnon
  68,19,Tokkel ku Rabbih kabuk usun xiinit anuk mire (giráy kaa carrisse kinnuk) kaa mireh
  68,20,Tokkel usuk data gommod ceelak maacise
  68,21,Tokke sittah kayam kaayeenih maacisen waqdi
  68,22,Sinni buqree kee sinni caxammixuh waqlal kuula kaa yargaqu waah orbisa mara tekkeenik ittak iyyen
  68,23,"Tokkel gexeenih, usun tutuc axcuk"
  68,24,Ta saaku tumaleela bustaan siinil cule waytaama ittak axcuk
  68,25,Kuuleenih loowiteenimil dudda le mara sinni akka luk
  68,26,"Tokkel usun sinni bustaan carareeh gombod yekkem yublen waqdi, diggaluk nanu baditneeh gitak hoxneh nan iyyen"
  68,27,"Usun Bustaan sinni bustaan kinnim yismiten waqdi: Wonna hinnay nanu kay kayrik baxaysite mara nekke, tumaleela cakkik kak waasneemih sabbatah iyyen"
  68,28,"Keenik kas kee kayrih yayse num: siinik maxaccinniyoo, Yalla ma saytunnossaanaa, Yalli saytunih itteenih, hinnay Yalli faxek itteenih"
  68,29,"Nanu ni Rabbi kaah yaguude saytunnoysiyyah kaa saytunnosna, diggah nanu ninni nafsi yudlume marah sugne tumaleela cakkik waasneemil"
  68,30,Tokkel gari garut keenik yufkune sitta assacakkuk
  68,31,"Booley nee gee finqgaaw! Diggah nanu caddok tatre marah sugne, Yallih amri cinneeh tumaleela cakkik waasne waqdi"
  68,32,"Ni Rabbi nanu abneh nan umaanek kaal gacneemih sabbatah, tama bustaanak taysem nee ciggiilisele, diggaak nanu ninni Rabbik qafuu kee muxxo qaagitna"
  68,33,"Addunyâ digaalá Tonna. Diggah akeerâ digaalá wohuuk naba, usun woh yaaxige mara akkinnoonuy waasimak yenen"
  68,34,"Diggah Yallak meesita mari, sinni Rabbih xaqul waara niqmat elle yan jannoota lon"
  68,35,Tokkel muslimiin koros inna maay abna galtol? (mabna)
  68,36,Maca litoonuu Mannal mekeltaanaa? muslimiin kee koros galtol missoowaanah ittaanamal
  68,37,Hinnak qaraanak oobe kitaabay elle barittaana litoonuu
  68,38,Diggah isin faxinnaanim addak kak doorittoonuh
  68,39,"Hinnak xagnittey xiibal siinih diggosneh iyya nellih litoonuu Qhiyaamah ayrô fanah, diggaluk isin sinnih faxxaanam mekeltaanamal"
  68,40,"Nabiyow! ken (koros kinnuk) esserey :woo meklay abiteeni geyoonu waanamah waas keenik yekke num miyyaay"
  68,41,"Hinnak Yallat agleytiitih yan maray usun iyyaanamah waas keenih yakkey faxaanamah ken cata maay lon, toysa usun iyyaanamat numma yacee mara yekkeenik sinni agleytit baahoonay"
  68,42,"Qhiyaamah ayróy Yallî sarbay ni sarba ceele wayta tamballayu waytaah, sinam sujuud fanah edde seecimtay, koros sujuud edde abtam duude wayta"
  68,43,"Intiita keenik sabruuruttaah taqunxeeh iroh fayya tet haanam maduudaanaay xixxibaané kee qunxaané ken buulta Yallih digaalah gibdah, Nummah usun addunyal sugen waqdi sujuuduh seecimak sugen qaafiyatah nagay anuk, tokkel usun kaxxamariinoh sujuud abak ma suginnon"
  68,44,"Toysa Nabiyow ta Qhuraan dirabboysa maraa kee yoo sittah cab, usun kak aaxige waan gambik ken lagsennooh ken digaalennok"
  68,45,"Kaadu dago wakti (xokobbiseyyo), keenih abenno dambitte ossitaanamkeh diggaluk yi digaalá gibdih korosul"
  68,46,"Hinnak Nabiyow atu a farmoh gudduusiyyal galtó ken essertaah, usun woo galtoh magoyta elle tiqilsee mara yekkeenii kah aamine waanam"
  68,47,"Hinnak usun qellittem elle tan luucal macfuuzuy, qellittaamih ixxigay usun faxaanam kak yaktubeeni maay lon"
  68,48,"Toysa Nabiyow atu isi Rabbih meklal isbiraay, kullumti kataysah (Nabii Yuunus kinnuk) inna makkin naqabuu kee sabri sinnah, usuk isi Rabbih qoxxitit (kaxxa faxewaynaan kinnuk) kullumti bagih addat anuk seece waqdi"
  68,49,"Kay Rabbih kabuk Racmat kaa eleele wannay, qambisimak yen kullumti baguk baaxok booxal usuk ilqime numuh anuk"
  68,50,"Tokkel kay Rabbi isi farmoh kaa dooreeh, meqe marih num kaa abe. (ambiyaa kee farmoytit kinnuk)"
  68,51,"Nummah Nabiyow koroosite mari Qhuraan yaabbe waqdi, usun sinni intiitat Koo qawlusaanaah koo yankiseenim xayyossu haan koh lon naqabuh, kaadu usuk diggah cabuli kok iyyan kuuxe waynaanah"
  68,52,Usuk (Qhuraan kinnuk) ginoh (woh seehadaa kee jinni kinnuk) kassis akke waytek kalah tu hinna
  69,1,Alcaaqha is Qhiyaamâ migaqwak migaaqak teynay is nummah takku waytam yascasse kinni
  69,2,Qhiyaamay cakkil takku wayta macaay
  69,3,Maca koo tiysixxigeeh Nabiyow Qhiyaamay cakkil takku wayta
  69,4,Samuud deqsitta kedoó (woh Nabii Saalic mara) kee Qaad deqsitta kedó (woh Nabii Huud mara) Qhiyaamay meesî gibdah lubbî taatuki deqsitta dirabbosseh
  69,5,"Tokkel samuuduh tu gactek, Yalli caddok taturte xongolot ken finqise"
  69,6,"Kaadu Qaad deqsita marah tu gactek, Yalli kaxxa xongoloo kee xabca le caacayay caddok tatret ken finqise"
  69,7,"Yalli malcina baraay bacra ayroy sitta katattay aggirriqqe sinni caacay keenit ruube, tokkel woo baritteé kee woo ayroorah addat sinaamay rabtey qangalaltay tamiirâ laqiibay gorrittey inaaqah tani ceelah ken table"
  69,8,Tokkel woo marak numwy finqite kalah raaqe keenik maay table
  69,9,"Kaadu firqawnaay, kaak naharat korosuh suge maraá kee magaalol elle korsen mari (Nabii Luut mara kinnuk) kaxxa dambi luk yemeeten"
  69,10,"Tokkel usun sinni Rabbih farmoyta cineenih, wonnaluk Yalli gibdi mabbuxuh ken yibbixe (digaalá kinnuk)"
  69,11,"Diggah nanu lee caddok taturteeh kulliimik amo ciggilte waqdi, doynikit Nabii Nuucùû luk sin nukkuqeeh sin raaqisne"
  69,12,"Woo abto kassis siinih abne, kaadu raaqissa ayti tet raaqissamkeh"
  69,13,Tokkel baantat inki adda fuuxa fuuxumta waqdi
  69,14,"Kaadu baaxoo kee qaleelá le aroocak tamukkuqeeh, inki atkah sittat tamuttukeeh bulá takke"
  69,15,Toysa too waqdi Qhiyaama soltah
  69,16,"Kaadu qaran qanxixaah, usuk woo ayró boolaataah Qande luk maraaqa"
  69,17,"Kaadu malayka kay deraafel gactaah, woo ayró ku Rabbih qarshi malaykak bacra malaykatti isi amol yakkuqe"
  69,18,"Too ayró sinaamey cisab kee galtoh Yallî fooca sin maksan, isin qellissaanamak tu kaak maqellitta"
  69,19,Le kitab migdi gabah kah yontocowwime numuh tugactek wallê gibdah yi kitab ibbixa ikriya iyya
  69,20,"Diggah anu asmatuk suge, inni cisaabat (galtot) garayuwaam"
  69,21,Toysa usuk akeeral ruffu kaa hayta mano le
  69,22,Jannatay fayya leh addal yan
  69,23,Jannatti mexexi kaa daggaasita marah xayih
  69,24,"Keenik iyyaanah:akumaay, aquba ruffû xica tatrusutten meqe taamáh sabbatah, taturte ayroorah addat"
  69,25,"Kaadu Le kitab guri gabah kah yontocowwime numuh tu gactek, maganey yi kitab yoh antacawwime wannay iyya"
  69,26,Kaadu inkinnah maa xaginniyo yicisab kinnim
  69,27,Maganey addunyal abe rabi yi manoh ellecabo akkinnay
  69,28,Yi maali yoh xiqem mali Yallih digaalák
  69,29,Yi duddaa kee reedá yok gexxeh
  69,30,"Iyyan jahannam malaykak:kaa abbixaay wonnaluk kay namma gaba fillat kaak axuwa silsilatat"
  69,31,Tohuk lakal jaciim deqsitta girá kaa culusa tet niqna tammoysamkeh
  69,32,Tohuk lakal silsilatay xexxaarah malcina tabanih cusul yakket kaa culusa iyyan
  69,33,Diggah usuk addunyal Yallay nabah inkittinaanel aamanuk masuginna
  69,34,Kaadu tu dagoyta yaskameenimih sinam ilsiisak masuginna addunyal
  69,35,Toysa ta saaku usuk takkķel isil xayi numuy digaalá isik waasa mali
  69,36,Kaadu hebeltô maaqo mali girâ marak caxta qasaalayi akke waytek
  69,37,Ama qasaalayi takmem matan dambileelay koroosannuk kate wayte akke waytek
  69,38,Xiibitah an isin tableenimil
  69,39,Kaadu able waytaanamal xiibita
  69,40,Diggah ta Qhuraan Yallih maxcoy massakaxxa le farmoyti yakriye kinni
  69,41,"Kaadu usuk (Qhuraan kinnuk) gadabê maxco hinna, kaa nummassaanam siinik dagoh"
  69,42,"Kaadu usuk qellittem aaxigeh iyya ginnilih maxco hinna, isin kassittaanaah elle kaskassowtaanam siinik dagoh"
  69,43,Usuk ginó gineh yan Rabbih kabuk oobe kitaaba
  69,44,Kaadu Nabii Mucammad Asale nanu axce wayneemik tu nel diraabah ginnaasitinnay
  69,45,Nanu diggah qanxaffe luk migdi gabah kaa abbaxuk neneeh kaa digaalak nen
  69,46,Tohuk lakal canti ramad kaak argaquk nen
  69,47,Tokkel siinik ni digaalák kaa reebisaamih dudda num mali
  69,48,"Kaadu diggah, Qhuraan kassiisi Yallak meesita marah"
  69,49,"Kaadu diggah nanu naaxigeh, siinik diggah ama Qhuraan dirabboysa mara"
  69,50,"Kaadu diggah ama Qhuraan dirabboysaanam, Qhiyaamah ayró koroosite maral kaxxa nadaama akke le"
  69,51,"Kaadu diggah, usuk (Qhuraan kinnuk) nummay asmat le kinni"
  69,52,Toysa saytunnos! ku Rabbih migaaqay naba
  70,1,Korosuk num raq sinni digaaláy keenil obtu wayta essereeh kallace
  70,2,"Usuk korosuh tet essereeh keenik tet waasa num mayan, yalli tet oobisam faxek"
  70,3,Yallay fayya leeh nabna leh kabuk taniih keenik cattam matan
  70,4,Malaykaa kee jibriil Yallâ fanah tawqe ixxi kak kontom alfih sanat yakke ayróh addat
  70,5,Toysa isbir Nabiyow qaxmeqe sabrih
  70,6,"Diggah, usun (koros kinnuk) digaalá xer iimiy akke waytah yablen"
  70,7,Kaadu nanu xayiimiy takku waytah tet nable
  70,8,Amah takkem Qaran diyaayisen lakqoo kee nacaasih innah gaca ayró
  70,9,Kaadu qaleelá bisu le suufuy fikiikiseeniy caacayat gexah inna takke ayró
  70,10,"Elle xayi elle xayi essere waah, kacnoyti kacnoyta essere waa ayro"
  70,11,"Yalli woo ayro sitta ken yaybulleeh, sitta yaaxigeeniih sittah xiqaanam malon. tokkel umeyni (korosta kinnuk) isi nafsik isi xaylo fidah yaceem faxaah sangeela Qhiyaamah ayroh digaalak"
  70,12,Kaadu isi barraa kee isi toobokoyta fidah yaceem faxa
  70,13,Kaadu kay kedoy (gulub kinnuk) kaa orbissaah kaa reebissah tani fidah yaceem faxa
  70,14,"Baaxô bagul inkih enni ittaamat waddiimaamih sangel le, tohuk lakal Yallih digaalák naggoowam faxa woo fidat"
  70,15,"Caagid usuk elle faxa inna hinna, diggah is ladá deqsitta giráy hadiidigtaah habuubugta kinni"
  70,16,Is arab siibtá gira niqnâ gibdah
  70,17,"Isî fanah secta iimaanat derre cabeeh, Yallaa kee Yallih farmoytih amri cine mara"
  70,18,"Kaadu sectah maalu kobxiseeh, Yallih cakki kak aceewee mara"
  70,19,"Diggah seehadayti baakerliiy, qaraarakolih (qambaxxaglih) anuk ginniime"
  70,20,usuk umaane kaa xagte tet tekkek qaraarako li kinni (qaxbaxxaagite)
  70,21,Kaadu maqaané kaa xagteeh gaddalitek kaxxa gabâ gibda li kinni
  70,22,Salat abá koh raqtuh immay
  70,23,Woh umman sinni salaatih baguk kate waa mara kinni
  70,24,Kaadu usun yimixxige cakki (maglab kinnuk) maalut kak yan mara kinni
  70,25,Kallaca tu malii kee kallace waa tu malih
  70,26,Kaadu usun cisab kee galtoh ayró (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) nummaysa mara
  70,27,Kaadu usun sinni Rabbih digaalák meesita mara
  70,28,"Tama meesih kah meesitaanam, diggaluk ken Rabbih digaalá yaamineenim mali (baggibda mali)"
  70,29,Kaadu usun sinni sammooma (sambooba) dalwak dacrisa mara
  70,30,"Sinni gennaaqoh agabuu kee sinni say naqoosay ken gabá timlike akke waytek, toysa diggah usun qeemu maloonuuy, yassacakken mara hinnon"
  70,31,"Tokkel tamahak kalihim faxeeh, gurrise mari, woo mari usun caddok taturleela kinni"
  70,32,Kaadu usun sinni amaanootaa kee sinni xagna dacrisa mara kinni
  70,33,"Kaadu usun sinni sumaaqittel soolaah, wohul diggi iyya mara kinni"
  70,34,Kaadu usun sinni salat le waktil dacrisa mara kinni
  70,35,"Woo mari jannootah addal massakaxxa leeh, ruffu iyya"
  70,36,Nabiyow koroosite mari fillitte kadeedisak koo fanah edde yardem maca lee
  70,37,Kok migdaa kee gura le kabul horta hortah gaca mara akkuk
  70,38,"Kulli seehadayti keenik, Yalli waara niqmat le jannat ise culsaamah sangeelaa"
  70,39,"Aleey caagid usun elle yakkalen inna hinna, diggah nanu usun yaaxigeenimik ken ginne. (woh daacoyta kinnuk)"
  70,40,Ayrô mawqooqii kee ayrô kormaami Rabbil (Yalli isi nafsi edde faxak) xiibita diggah nanu dudda linoomul
  70,41,"Keenik yayse mara ciggiilisnaamal, kaadu hebeltô seehadayti keenik nek mayassaqqa, ken bayisnam fannek abe nee kaltam matan"
  70,42,"Toysa usun Sinni baatilit giirisoonay ken ixxic, kaadu sinni addunyal digritoonay ken ixxic ken ayróy (woh Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) kah xagnisimeenit ongoorowwu iyyaanam fanah"
  70,43,"Magooqak sissikuk yawqen ayró, addunyal sinni yallittey xeet kee cooxuk tanî fanah tet yaqbudoonuh asassakuk kah gexak sugen innah"
  70,44,"Intiita keenik meesih rammitak buraa kee qunxaané ken buulta, woh addunyal kah xagnisimak sugen ayró (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) kinni"
  71,1,"Diggah, nanu Nabii Nuuc kay marâ fanah kaa rubneh, qansarissa digaalá keenih tamaatek naharal, ku mara meesis iyyaanamal"
  71,2,"Nabii Nuuc iyyeh: yi maraw! Diggah anu siinih meesisso kak baxxaqqa le farmoyta kinniyo"
  71,3,"Yalla uqbudaay qibaada kaah caglisa, kaadu kaak meesitaay, yamri oggola"
  71,4,"Tohul sin dambitte siinih cabeleeh, qumri siinih wadirroyse le yimixxige waktî fanah, Diggah Yalli mekle wakti (Raba kinnuk) yamaate waqdi, mawadirroysima, isin woh yaaxige mará akkinnitoonuy iimaanâ fanah asissikuk tenen"
  71,5,"Nabii Nuuc iyyeh:yi Rabbow diggah, anu inni mara kol yaamanoonuh baraay laqó ken seeceh"
  71,6,Tokkel Yi seeco tu keenih mossinna kudimik sá
  71,7,"Kaadu diggah, anu keenih seecinnaanih waqdi dambi keenih cabtuh sinni feeraari sinni aytiitat heeniih (axcem yaabbeenimik) sinni sarat yumbududeeniih, (yoo yableenimik) koroosannul yeedeeniih, kaxxa mariinoh kaxxa mariiniten iimaan oggolaanamak"
  71,8,"Tohih lakal diggah, anu xongolo fayya haak keenih seece"
  71,9,"Tohih lakal diggah, anu xongolo fayya keenih heeh, tutuccah tutuccu keenit exce"
  71,10,"Tokkel sinni Rabbil dambi cabti essirita keenik exce, diggah usuk maggom dambi cabti li kinnik"
  71,11,"Yallal tuduureeniih, dambi cabti kaal esseritteenik, sittallakleh rob siinih ruube le"
  71,12,"Kaadu maaluvy xalay farakka siinih heele, kaadu wahoobah yan basaatin siinih heele, kaadu weeqaytitte siinih heele"
  71,13,Maca liton Yallih nabnak kah meesite waytaanam
  71,14,Nummah Yalli ranko rankoh sin ginek
  71,15,Yalli malcina qaran sittak amol massoowak elle gine inna matablaanaa
  71,16,"Kaadu alsá ken (Qaranwa kinnuk) addal diifu abeeh, ayró ifa faanus abe"
  71,17,Kaadu Yalli baaxok sin gineeh aysubukiyyah sin yuysubuke
  71,18,"Tohuk lakal teetit sin gacsaah, Qhiyaamah ayro teetik sin yayyaaqe ayyaaqiyyah"
  71,19,Kaadu Yalli baaxó fidó siinih abe
  71,20,Farakka le gitittel tet bagul gexxoonuh
  71,21,"Nabii Nuuc: yi Rabbow diggah usun (boola le mara kinnuk) yamri cineeniih, le maaluu kee le xalay finqak sa tu kah osse wayta abbottii kee gaddaloola katyen iyye"
  71,22,Kaadu usun kaxxa uma maláh malsen
  71,23,"Kaadu sinni yallitteh qibaadá macabina sittak iyyen, kaadu Waddiiy, Suwaaqaay, Yaqhusuvy, Yaquuqh kee Nasri deqsitta numtinwellitteh qibaadá macabina sittak iyyen"
  71,24,Kaadu nummah maggo mara finqiseenihik ta daalimiinih finqak sah tu mossin iyye Nabii Nuuc isi Rabbik
  71,25,"Usun aben dambitteh sabbatah leet yunxuqsumeeniih, girá culsumen, tokkel usun Yallak kalah cateynit magennon"
  71,26,"Kaadu Nabii Nuuc: yi Rabbow baaxô bagul koroosite marak inkittuy mutuccu iyya macabin iyye"
  71,27,"Diggah atu ken cabtek ku naqoosa makkoyse loonuuh, maxalan umeynay kaxxa koroosannu le akke waytek"
  71,28,"Nabii Nuuc: yi Rabbow yoo kee yi xaleynaay, yi buxá moominiinih anuk cule maraa kee, lab moominiin kee say moominiinih inkih dambi cabaay, daalimiinih baatik sa tu mossin iyye"
  72,1,"Nabiyow! ixxic: Yallak wacyi yol obsimeech diggah jinnik horta yakke mari qhuraan yok ankaciseeh, yoo nummayseh, tokkel usun sinni marâ fanah gacen waqdi: nanu diggah qajiibik (cakkumuk) yan qhuraan noobbeeh ankacisne keenik iyyen"
  72,2,"Tama Qhuraan cakkii kee maqaanê fanah seecaah, meqe gita sinaamah yascasse, tokkel nanu kaa nummasneeh, ninni Rabbit agleh hebeltohim mahaynaay kaah abna qibaadat tu ma nasgalla"
  72,3,"Kaadu diggah ni Rabbih nabna fayya itteeh, usuk barra ma haysitinnaay, xalay ma haysitinna iyyen"
  72,4,"Kaadu ni toogimayti (ibliis kinnuk) Yallak cakki gitak xeeruk raqta maxco axcuk suge, yalli barraa kee baxa le iyye waqdi"
  72,5,"Kaadu diggah, nanu seehadaa kee jinni Yallal dirab heewaytam nekkele"
  72,6,"Kaadu diggah seehadak labha jinnik labha magansitak teneeh, jinni conxóo kee caddoktatur keenih osisak yen"
  72,7,"Diggah, seehadâ koros tekkeleh isin kah tekkelen innah jinnow Yalli rabteemik num ugse weelem"
  72,8,"Kaadu jinni: diggah nanu qaran gufnam fanneeh, gibdi malaykay kaa dacrissaa kee dabiitittek kibbiimeh neh suge iyye"
  72,9,"Kaadu diggah, nanu ahak duma qaraanak elle daffeyna arooca luk sugne kay xaagu ankacisnuh, tokkel taway too xaagu ankacisam faxa num dabiitay kaa qambaala geele"
  72,10,"Diggah, nanu (jinni butta kinnuk) Yalli baaxol yan marah faxem umaané kinnim kee hinnay ken Rabbi keenih faxem maqaané kinnim manaaxiga"
  72,11,"Kaadu diggah meqe maray Yallak meesita net yaniih, wohuk kalah yan mari net yanih butta buttay sissinih anuk"
  72,12,Kaadu jinni iyyeh; diggah nanu Yalla baaxô bagul taanise waynaah kudimil kaak assaqqee waynam nismiteh nee digaalam faxek
  72,13,"Kaadu diggah, nanu qhuraanay massa le gitâ fanah tirri sinam haa noobbe waqdi kaa nummasneh tokkel isi Rabbi nummayse num abite maqaaneh daggoysiyyak ma meesitaay dulmih abe umaanek fulah tu kaat osisaanamak mameesita"
  72,14,"Kaadu diggah;nanu garab muslimiinih kak yaniih, garab korosuh kak yan mara kinnino, Tokkel yuslume marah tu gactek, too mari meqe gita doorite mara"
  72,15,"Kaadu koroosite marah tu gactek, jahannam giráh bocó yakken"
  72,16,"Kaadu Yalli: insii kee jinni islaamaninnô gita yibbixeenih diggi elle axcinnoonuy maggo leek ken afaquk nen iyye"
  72,17,"Wohul ken naqiyyirê gidah, isi Rabbih kassitit (Qhuraan kinnuk) derre cabe num, Yalli gibdi digaalá kaa culsa"
  72,18,"Kaadu diggah, masaagid Yallih iimik kay addal kaak kalihim maqbudinaay qibaad kaah caglisa"
  72,19,"Kaadu diggah, Yallih naqsi Nabii Mucammad fraseo isi Rabbi yaqbuduh soole waqdi jinni kay amol sittak bagul sitta qoxxisam akke raarra hee Qhuraan kaak ankacisuh"
  72,20,"Nabiyow korosuk:cagalah anu inni Rabbi aqbudeeh agleh inkittu kaat mahaa qibaadál keenik ixxic"
  72,21,"Nabiyow tama korosuk: diggah anu umaane siinik kalam maduudaay maqaane siinih baaham maduuda keenik ixxic"
  72,22,"Nabiyow diggah, Yallih digaalak num yoo macataay, kaak kalah eleelita mara mageya keenik ixxic"
  72,23,"Kinnih immay anu Yalli yoo edde amriseemih gudduysiyyaa kee yoo edde ruube farmooma sin gudduysam duuda, kaadu yallaa kee kay farmoytih amri cine num diggaluk jahannam girá le, umman tet addal waarak"
  72,24,"Koros edde tan umaanek ma katta digaalák elle xagnisimeenim ubullu haytam fanah, tokkel usun too digaalá ken xagta waqdi aaxige lon cateynak boola leeh, ixxuk dagna lem kinni mara"
  72,25,Nabiyow ama korosuk isin digaalak elle xagnisimteenim xayim kinnim kee hinnay yi Rabbi xer wakti kah abem kinnim anu maaxiga keenik ixxic
  72,26,"Yalli qellittam yaaxigiiy, isih qellisem num mayaybulla"
  72,27,"Usuk farmoytiitik isi farmoh dooreeh edde leedeeh yikcine farmoyta akke waytek, tokkel Yalli isi farmoytah fooca le gambii kee derre le gambik jinnik kaa dacrissa malayka kaah ruuba"
  72,28,"Yallih farmoyti yaaxigê gidah, Yallih farmoytittey kaak duma rubsumte sinni Rabbih farmooma diggal gudduyseenimkeh, kaadu ken garil enni ittam Yalli marot yabbixe isi ixxigat, kaadu kullim looweeh ixxu kak gacseh woo hiimik tu kaak maqellitta"
  73,1,Kee isi sarot yambududow! (Nabii kinnuk)
  73,2,Bar inkih salaatah sol barak dagom akke waytek
  73,3,"Barak garab sol, hinnay garabak dagom cab"
  73,4,"Hinnay garabat osisaay, Qhuraan caatih cubbusak akriy"
  73,5,Nabiyow Diggah Nanu qilsi maxco (Qhuraan kinnuk) kol oobisenno
  73,6,Diggah barak gimo aban salat kee qibaada sorkocobbaxa kaxxam raatissaah maxcô baxxaqqaa kee diggah aysuk raqta
  73,7,Diggah laqo maggo agxe lito
  73,8,"Nabiyow ku Rabbih migaq cusaay, isi qibaadah kaâ fanah aggiriqiyyah iggiriqqiy"
  73,9,"Usuk ayrô mawqaa kee ayrô kormâ Rabbi, kaak sa cakkil yaqbuden Yalli mayanak, toysa keltiyyah kaal kelit"
  73,10,Kaadu koros koo kee ku diinik ittaamal isbiraay qaxmeqe cabtih ken cab
  73,11,Kaadu Nabiyow yoo kee tama yaayoota dirabboysa maray niqmatat yani ittah cabaay! Dago wakti keenih ab
  73,12,Diggah usun ni garil axoowaa kee jaciim deqgsitta girá lon
  73,13,Kaadu uma maaqoy serko ley katlak oobe waytaa kee ken qansarissa digaalá lon
  73,14,"Baaxoó kee qaleelá tangayye ayróy, qaleelá caxitta burta takke"
  73,15,"Diggah nanu makki korosey farmoytay (Nabii Mucammad csati kinnuk) sin taamoomil sumaaqita siinî fanah rubne, firqawnâ fanah farmoyta (Nabii Muusa kinnuk) kah rubne innaah"
  73,16,"Tokkel firqawni too farmoyta cineeh, gibdi digaaláh kaa digaalle"
  73,17,"Toysa sinni nafsi too digaalak mannal catetton, meesi gibdah urru amqadoytit abta ayró, (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) tengeddeenik"
  73,18,"Woo ayro meesî gibdah qaran qanxixah, Yalli is tamaatu waytaamah hee xagni yamaatuwaam raq mali"
  73,19,"Diggah ta aayoota sinaamah kassiisik, toysa qakkaloowaah, isi nafsih maqaané faxe num isi Rabbî fanah gita yabbaxay Yallak meesii kee taaqatal"
  73,20,"Nabiyow! diggah ku Rabbi atu barti salaatah waqdik teyna barak sidiica afak namma afak daguk raqtam kaak soltaah, aka adda garab kaak soltaah, aka adda kaadu sidocaytoh afa kaak soltam yaaxigeh, ku kataysiisik hortay kolluk tanî luk, yalli usuk bar kee laqo takkeh gide yaaxigeeh usuk ken waadoysa, yalli isin bar inkih salaatah soolak xintaanam duude waytaanam yeexegeeh, qafu siinih kak abeeh siinil xabbacoyseh, toysa barti salaatal qhuraanak siinih xabbacowtem akriya, yalli siinik biyaakita maray barti salaatah soolam duude waa siinit aneelem yeexegeh, kaadu aka maray yallih muxxo (rizqhi kinnuk) gurrusay baaxô bagul kabxah (tellemmo kinnuk) yangayyee kee aka maray yallih gital gaaduh yangicille siinik aneelem yeexegeh, toysa barti salaatal qhuraanak siinih xabbacowtem akriya, kaadu fardi salat elle faxxiima'nnal abaay, zakay waajibik siinil tani acuwa, kaadu yallih fooca edde faxak sadqhat ottocowwa, kaadu simaamey sinni nafsih maqaanek tatrussu hayteenem is yallih xaqul isin addunyal tatrusseenimik kayrih aysuk raqtaah galtoh nabuk raaqak tet geetton, kaadu yallak dambi cabti esserita, diggah yalli dambi cabtili xuwawli kinnik"
  74,1,Kee bududet yan Nabiyow
  74,2,Ugutaay sinam Yallih digaalák meesis
  74,3,Kaadu isi Rabbi eyneb
  74,4,Kaadu isi sara najaasak saytunnos
  74,5,Kaadu Yallat agleyta haanam kee raqqate umaaneenak exxer
  74,6,Kaadu tu edde tassamgguh acwa maabin
  74,7,Kaadu ku Rabbih kacanu edde geytu waytaamal isbir
  74,8,Tokkel ugut Baantá fooximtu wayta waqdi
  74,9,Too ayró gibdi ayró
  74,10,Too ayró korosul xabcá mali
  74,11,Nabiyow! Yoo kee inâ bagut dibuk anuk gineh an num (waliid ibnul mughiira kinnuk) sittah cab
  74,12,Kaadu maggo maalu kah ecee num
  74,13,Kaadu kaallih geytimta xaylo kah ecee num
  74,14,Addunyal mano xabbacoysiyyah kah xabbacoyseeh farakka kah hee num
  74,15,Tohuk lakal xalay kee maalu kaah ossam qaagitaah sangeela
  74,16,"Caagid usuk elle yakkale inna hinna, diggah usuk naayoota cirdih angadduk suge"
  74,17,Saytutticin qaley girák tani yawqeemih kaa dirkiseyyo
  74,18,"Diggah usuk isi nafsil cubbuseeh, massoyseh Nabii kee Qhuraan xagitik iyyuwaam"
  74,19,Tokkel usuk abbarsimehik mannal massoysee ta uma xagit
  74,20,Tohuk lakal abbarsimehik mannal massoyseeh ta uma xagit
  74,21,Tohuk lakal usuk cubbii kee malat qagteh
  74,22,Tohuk lakal ceereeh fooca kaxxa ribiyyah ribe
  74,23,"Tohuk lakal cakkit derre cabeeh, kaxxamariiniteh"
  74,24,"Tokkel Qhuraanak: ah tu hinna Mucammad naharsi marak baahe baab akke waytek iyye"
  74,25,Ah tu hinna seehadâ maxcó akke waytek iyye
  74,26,"Saqhar deqsitta girá kaa culseyyo, teetit cararaah tet digaalá tammoysuh"
  74,27,Saqhar kinni girá maca koo tiysixxigeeh
  74,28,"Is xagaral cado macabtaay, lafa macabta carrissa tet akke waytek"
  74,29,"Is xagar carissaah, dattossah"
  74,30,Taban kee sagaal tet amol yan malaykak
  74,31,"Kaadu girá dacrisa mara malayka akke waytek maabinnino, Kaadu maabinnino ken ixxu koroosite marah aqayyaareey, kitab kah yontocowwime mari yasmitê gideh iyyaanam akke waytek, kaadu yeemene mari iimaan elle ossituuy, kitab kah yontocowwime maraa kee moominiin elle agaywaagite waytu, kaadu sorkocobbaxittet biyak le maraa kee koros Yalli tahat ceelalloh maca faxee ittuh, Tonnaah Yalli isih faxe mara makkoysaah isih faxe mara tirri haa, ku Rabbih qandé takkeh gide taaxigê matan kaa akke waytek, girá tu hinna is seehadah kassis takkemkeh iyyaanam akke waytek"
  74,32,"Koros elle takkale inna hinna, Yalli alsál xiibite"
  74,33,Kaadu Bari derre caba waqdil xiibite
  74,34,Maaci ifá waqdil xiibite
  74,35,"Diggah, is (girá kinnuk) nabaamak tiyak teyná"
  74,36,Is seehadah meesissoh tan
  74,37,Siinik faxe mari maqaanél taturay hinnay umaanél wadirrooway
  74,38,Ummaan nafsi abiteemit axawah yan
  74,39,Migdi maray moominiinih yani akke waytek
  74,40,Jannat addal sitta esseraanah
  74,41,Umeyniitiy gira cultê caalat
  74,42,Saqhar deqsitta girá maca sin culussee keenik iyyan
  74,43,Addunyal salat aba marâ lih salat abak masuginnino iyyan
  74,44,Kaadu tu mali askamuk masuginnino
  74,45,Kaadu umaanet giirisa marâ lih giirisak sugne
  74,46,Kaadu galtóh ayró (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) dirabboysak sugne
  74,47,Asmat (Raba kinnuk) net xikki iyyam fanah
  74,48,Tokkel shafaaqat abá marih shafaaqatta tu keenih maxiqta
  74,49,A koros kassitit (Qhuraan kinnuk) derre kah cabtam maca lee
  74,50,Gilsime dibookolih innah
  74,51,Lubaakak kude waqdi
  74,52,Wonna hinnay keenik kulli seehadayti fakut tan kitooba iseh tantacawwimeeh geyam faxa
  74,53,"Tonna hinnay diggah, usun ellecaboh ayrók ma meesitan"
  74,54,Nummah ta Qhuraan usuk kassiisi elle kaskassoowa marah
  74,55,Tokkel kassitam faxa mari kaal kaskassoowah
  74,56,"Kaal (Qhuraan kinnuk) kaskassowtam matan Yalli kah faxe num akke waytek, usuk (Yalla kinnuk) kak meesitoonu meesi caglitaah, dambi cabti caglita Rabbi kinni"
  75,1,Diggah Yalli Qhiyaamah ayról xiibite
  75,2,Kaadu diggah moominti nafsiy isi yassacakkel xiibite
  75,3,Seehadayti (korosta kinnuk) kay lafoofi gaaboyse weennom yakka lee
  75,4,"Yeey, nanu tet gaaboysenno, kay feeraarih exaaxi massosnam duudak"
  75,5,"Tonna hinnay, seehadayti isi foocal tanim dirabboysam faxa"
  75,6,Qhiyaamah ayró maa waqdii iyyeh esseraamal? (kah esseram anqasa)
  75,7,Tokkel Mablá baditta waqdi
  75,8,Kaadu alsá diifi duugumta waqdi
  75,9,Kaadu ayroó kee alsá gaaboysimtaah inki arac yawqen waqdi
  75,10,"Seehadayti: woo ayró (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) anke kudnaa anke eleelitnaa iyya"
  75,11,Tonna hinnay eleelitan rike matan
  75,12,Woo ayró idyaa kee madab ku Rabbih xaqu cagalah
  75,13,Seehadaytuh woo ayró taamak yuysukumem kee wadirroysem warsintah
  75,14,"Tonna hinnay, seehadayti isi nafsil isih sumaaqita"
  75,15,Kaadu Abeh yan uma taamak faxem malkitaamah woo malkit kaah xiqam mali
  75,16,"Nabiyow wacyi kol ooba waqdi qhuraanat isi arraba masgayyin, raqsat kaak tasissikeemih fayxih"
  75,17,"Diggah nel tan kaa liilil kaa gaabosnam, kee kay kiraati"
  75,18,"Kaadu Nabiyow ni farmoyti jibriil gitak qhuraan kol nakriye waqdi, kaa ankacisaay tibbi ixxic, tohuk lakal usuk koo elle barse innal ikriy"
  75,19,Tohuk lakal diggah kay baxxaqisiyyi nel yan
  75,20,"Korosey caagid Isin elle takkalen inna hinna, ugut kee galtok tu matana ittaanamal, nummah isin addunyaa kee tet bilhada kicinton"
  75,21,"Kaadu isin akeera cabtaanaah, teetih mataamittan"
  75,22,Woo ayró meqe marih Foocitte (qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) iftah
  75,23,Isi Rabbî fanah wagitta.(woh meqe mara kinnuk)
  75,24,Kaadu woo ayró uma marih foocitte ribbimtah
  75,25,Kaxxa umaanéy xiiron lafoofi teetik edde taddigillee teetit akke lem tasmiteh
  75,26,Nummah rooci (coxxo) kaxkaxxo gufa waqdi
  75,27,Iyyi kaa daylisaa iyyan
  75,28,Kaadu diggah usuk (raba num) addunyak baxsimam yasmiteh. (raba kinnuk)
  75,29,Kaadu sarba sarbat makitta
  75,30,Woo ayro (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) seehadak beyto ku Rabbî fanah takke
  75,31,"Tokkel korosti Yallih farmoytaa kee qhuraan manummaysinnaay, salat maabinna"
  75,32,"Takkay immay qhuraan dirabboyseeh, iimaanat derre cabe"
  75,33,Tohuk lakat isi marâ fanah kaxxamariinitak gexe
  75,34,"Finqi koh yan, kaadu finqi koh yan"
  75,35,Tohuk lakal finqi koh yan kaadu finqi koh yan
  75,36,Seehadayti foyyah annaak calayah yanitay kaa iyyoonuwaanam yakkalee
  75,37,Seehadayti daacoyti tiffoytay maxaxat caxaanak yekkeh manannaa
  75,38,"Tohuk lakal dabloytak yekkeeh, Yalli kaa gineeh, kaa masssoyseeh, weelo kaa yeymeegqe"
  75,39,Tokkel namma qaynat kaa abé lab num kee say numuh anuk
  75,40,Yallay toh abe rabtem yaynuwweemih qamal geytoli hinnaa? (yeey kinnih)
  76,1,"Nummah seehadaytut rooci haanak duma dabaanak xer (der) daban kaal tatre, usuk cusaanamay xagar kak xagaanah tuh suge kalah"
  76,2,"Diggah nanu seehadaytu lab num kee say numuk yengele daacoytih tiffak kaa ginne kaa naqayyaruh, (mokkorruh) tokkel yaabbeeh yable seehadaytu kaa abne"
  76,3,Diggah nanı tirtô gitaa kee makô gita kaah baxxaqisneh moomintuy faatita akkee kee korostay yangadde akke yakke immay
  76,4,"Diggah nanu korosuh, silsilootay ibitte keenik edde debraanaa kee, ogoogay fillittee kee gaboobi ittat keenik edde yaxeenii kee, saqiir deqsitta giráy ken carrisa keenih massosne"
  76,5,Diggah meqe mari galoosay gocoyuk (kamri) kibuk taniy agleh kaafuur lek yaaquben
  76,6,"Ama gocoyuy yaaqubeeniy kaafuur agleh edde yani, is daray Yallih naqoosa kak taaqube, usun ayfuxxukiyyah tet yayfuxxukeeniih, faxxa heen kabul tet beyan"
  76,7,"Ama mari axbuux (nadri) duudusaah, Qhiyaamah ayróy umaané kak fixiixih tani Yallih digaalák meesitan"
  76,8,Kaadu usun tumaliiy qayxixxuu kee seewaytu maaqó yaskamen tet kacanu luk
  76,9,"Cagalah nanu sin kah naskamem Yallih foocih taaga, galtoo kee faatit siinik elle mafanna iyyan"
  76,10,"Diggah nanu ninni Rabbik meesitna, gibdah fooci edde ribbiima (kamadima) ayrók (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk)"
  76,11,"Tokkel Yalli woo ayróh umaanék ken reebiseeh, fooci ifuu kee wallé (farcat) keenih yecee"
  76,12,Kaadu yisbireenimih sabbatah jannat kee cariiril ken galte
  76,13,"Kay addal qaraakiyil kelitak, ayró mayablaanaay, kaxxa xabca mayablan"
  76,14,"Kaadu Kay cooxih silaaló keenit xayyowtah ken silaalisak, kaadu ama cooxih mexexih mafaala xabbacoowiyyah keenih xabbacowta"
  76,15,"Kaadu jannatti urruy ken yakdume keenit meekisah, mingiilay lakqok tanii kee kobboyyaayiy bililleelak (karaarit kinnuk) tani"
  76,16,Bililleelay lakqok taniy usun elle faxaanah gidel kiyaasiyyah kiyaaseeni
  76,17,Kaadu kay addal galoosay gocoyuk kibuk taniy agleh zanjabiil lek ken yafqen
  76,18,"Kay addal tan daray, salsabiil deqsittak yaaquben"
  76,19,"Kaadu jannatti urruy elle yanin caalatal elle waara keenit meekita, ken table waqdi luuluy fixiixiseeni ken takka le"
  76,20,"Kaadu jannatak faxe ikkeey wagittay, tokkel niqmatay weeloysoonu duude waanaa kee kaxxa Reeda table"
  76,21,"Anxaxin saray xabcin cariirik yanii kee gibdi cariirik yan sari ken xagaral yaniih, qado lakqok tan gabâ biriitat (cagooluk) billiiman, kaadu ken Rabbi yaaqubeenimiy saytuniy taahirik tanik ken yafqe"
  76,22,"Diggah ta galtó sin meqe taamoomih galto kinniih, sin taamoomi addunyal yalli raabiteeh yikcineh yan taamak sugte keenik iyyan"
  76,23,Diggah Nabiyow Qhuraan oobisiyyah nanu ninnih kol oobisne
  76,24,"Nabiyow Ku Rabbih meklal isbiraay, korosuk dambit kaxaxah yan marih yab moggolinaay hinnay koroosannuu kee maxqawitit caddok tatreh yan marih yab moggolin"
  76,25,"Kaadu ku Rabbih migaq Carraay, saaku xag"
  76,26,"Kaadu barak tut kaah kummaataay, barak xer waktit salat kaah ab"
  76,27,"Diggah tama mari (koros kinnuk) sissik tiya (addunya kinnuk) kicnoonuuh, qilsi ayroy ellecabol ken qambalta cabaanah (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk)"
  76,28,"Nanu ken ginneeh gino keenik karriqqi hayne, kaadu nanu bayisnam fannek, bayissi ken hayneh ken innah yan maray kayrih keenik yayse ciggiilisiyyah ciggiilisenno"
  76,29,"Diggah tama suurá seehadah kassiisi, toysa isi nafsih maqaané faxe num, isi Rabbih gita yabbixe, iimaan kee meqe taamál"
  76,30,"Isin caagiidak hebeltô caagidiy faxxaana manton, Yalli faxeh akķke waytek, diggah Yalli isi ginô caaloota yaaxigi, abba haamal naggaar kinni"
  76,31,"Yalli isi naqoosak isih faxe mara isi Racmat (jannat kinnuk) culsa, kaadu daalimiinih (koros kinnuk) akeeral qansarissa digaalá massoyse"
  77,1,Yalli ittâ lakleh itta kataata caacayal xiibite
  77,2,Edde luk gibdi caacayay hawwug iyyal xiibite
  77,3,Kaadu yalli malaykay qubulta usuk faxa ikke beytay fixiixisiyyah kaa fixiixissal xiibite
  77,4,"Edde luk yalli malaykay cakkii kee deedalaay, calaalii kee caraamu ittak baxissam kay xaquk luk obtal xiibite"
  77,5,Edde luk malaykay wacyi Yallih ambiyaa kee farmoytiitil oobissal xiibite
  77,6,Seehada Yallal malkit geewaytuh hinnay meesisso keenih yakkuh Yallih digaalák
  77,7,Cagalah Qhiyaamâ caagidik isin elle xagnisinteenim akkelem Raqmali
  77,8,Tokkel Cutuk duugumaah diifi kak gexa waqdi
  77,9,"Kaadu qaran qanxixaah, fakkiima waqdi"
  77,10,Kaadu qaleelá riira (bula) takke waqdi
  77,11,Kaadu Yallih farmoytit kee ken ummattâ fanat mekla edde aban wakti muggaqsime waqdi
  77,12,Farmoytit edde waddiroysimtem Maa ayroóy
  77,13,"Ginô fan edde meklaanaah edde Baxsan ayró, kah xagnisimeenim (woh Qhiyaamah ayró)"
  77,14,Kaadu seehadaytow maca koo tiysixxigeeh Baxsi ayroó kee tet gibdaabini kinnim
  77,15,Qhiyaamah ayro dirabboyse marah woo ayro fingi yan
  77,16,Naharsi marak Yallih farmoytit dirabboyse mara mafinqisinninoo
  77,17,Tohuk lakal wadirsi mara ken kataysenno
  77,18,Tonnah abba heenno umeyniitik (koros kinnuk)
  77,19,Yallih inkittinaanee dirabboyse marah woo ayro (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) finqi yan
  77,20,Seehaday boola le leek (daacoyta kinnuk) Sin ma gininninoo
  77,21,Edde luk sabhalal leeh dacayri le aracay (saynumih maxax kinnuk) bica let kaa ma hanninoo
  77,22,Yallih xaqul Yimixxige waktî fanah
  77,23,"tokkel kaa ginnam dudneeh, yayse dudda lem nee"
  77,24,Ni dudda dirabboysa marah woo ayro Finqi yan
  77,25,Baaxó aracay inkih sin yasgalleeh yabbixe maabinninoo
  77,26,"Siinik nuwwaamaay, rabteemih inkih"
  77,27,"Kaadu fayyale qaleelá teetil mahanninoo diggi tet haytuh, kaadu coboy leey salfa lek sin mafqinninoo"
  77,28,Ni niqmat yangaddee marah woo ayro Finqi yan
  77,29,"Korosuk qhiyaamah ayró: jahannam giráh digaaláy dirabboysak sugteenî fanah gexa keenik iyyan"
  77,30,Gexaay iraawita jahannam giráh qiiriy sidiica luddalê fanah
  77,31,"Usuk Ma silaalisaay, giráh huurik xiqam malik"
  77,32,Diggah is kaxxa qarih gide yakke xinkilliq qambissa
  77,33,Usuk (xinkilliq kinnuk) Dat caawin gaala ceela
  77,34,Yallih meesisso dirabboyse marah woo ayro Finqi yan
  77,35,Ta ayró dirableelá yabtaamih dudda mali. (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk)
  77,36,Yaabaanamih idni keenih mayantacawwima edde yawqoonuh
  77,37,Tama ayro dirabboysa marah woo ayro Finqi yan
  77,38,"Qhiyaamah ayró korosuk iyyaanah: tah ginô fan edde meklaanaah baxsan ayró, sin kee naharsi mara edde gaabosneh"
  77,39,"Toysa Isin malá teelleenik, yi digaalak edde cattimtoonuh yoh malsita"
  77,40,Ellecaboh ayro dirabboysa marah woo ayro Finqi yan
  77,41,Diggah Yallak meesite mari jannatal silalwaa kee daroorih addal yan
  77,42,Kaadu caxâ mixuk faxxa haanamih addal yanin
  77,43,"Keenik iyyaanah: akumaay aquba rufto luk, addunyal abbaasitten meqe taamah sabbatah"
  77,44,Diggah nanu tonnal galatna meqem abite mara.(moominiin kinnuk)
  77,45,Jannatti niqmat dirabboyse marah woo ayro Finqi yan
  77,46,"Yalli korosuk iyyah: addunyal meqem akumaay dago wakti teetit hataka diggah isin umeyniitik, Yallat agleyta hayteenimih sabbatah"
  77,47,Cisab kee galtoh ayro dirabboyse marah woo ayro Finqi yan
  77,48,"Kaadu Yallah salat abaay kaah rammita keenik iyyeenik, salat kaah maabaanaay, kaah marammitan"
  77,49,Yallih aayoota dirabboyse marah woo ayro Finqi yan
  77,50,"Toysa ta qhuraanay Yallih yab kinnih iyyal aamine weenik, maakitaabaay, maayaabaay kaak wadir elle yaaminoonu waanam"
  78,1,Qhurayshi koros itta essertam maatiyaay
  78,2,Itta essertam naba xaagu. (woh qhuraan kee sooloh ayró)
  78,3,Woh usun itta elle waan xaagu
  78,4,Wonna hinnay aaxigelon
  78,5,"Tohuk lakal digga luk, aaxigelon"
  78,6,Baaxó fidó siinih maabinninoo
  78,7,Kaadu qaleelá kadeeditte (xiikol) maabinninoo baaxoh
  78,8,Kaadu namma qaynatah sin ma gininnoo? (labim kee sayiimih anuk)
  78,9,Kaadu sin xin sin xagarih raacat (rofto) maabinninoo
  78,10,Kaadu bar sartan ma abinninoo? (kay ditet)
  78,11,Kaadu laqó quusi edde gurrussan wakti siinih maabinninoo
  78,12,Kaadu digga le malciin sin amol maxisinninoo? (malcina qaran kinnuk)
  78,13,Kaadu ayro ifoytay hadiidigay cuumi le maabinninoo
  78,14,Kaadu qamburrek taraaracinta lee moobisinninoo
  78,15,Amboo kee baaxók ubukku ittam teetit nayyaaquh
  78,16,Kaadu garoobuy gaabuh yani. (bustanwa kinnuk)
  78,17,"Diggah, baxsi ayroy ginô fan edde baxsaana yimixxige wakti yekke. (qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk)"
  78,18,Baanta fuxsinta ayró butta buttah anuk tamaaten. (woh Qhiyaamah ayró)
  78,19,"Kaadu qaran fakkiimaah, afoofi yakke ayró malaykah obtih"
  78,20,Kaadu qaleelá gexsimtaah edde bakarbakar takke
  78,21,Digga luk jahannam girá woo saaku koroosite mara aracal qambalta gira tekke
  78,22,Is caddok taturleelah elle gaceyná tekke.( koros kinnuk)
  78,23,Usun Tet addal amurruqe wayta liggiditte daffeya maráh anuk
  78,24,"Tet addal xabcaay, aqubbu haanam matammoysan"
  78,25,Nabam niqni lee kee girâ marih qasaalayi akke waytek
  78,26,Tamah keenih taguude galtó kinni. (ken uma taamák gexaak)
  78,27,"Diggah, usun fokkaaqok (cisaabak) meesitak suge weenimih sabbatah"
  78,28,Kaadu ni aayoota dirabboysiyyah dirabboyseenimih sabbatah
  78,29,Ummaanim nesketteh (gaabosneh) kutbeh lawcal macfuuzul
  78,30,Toysa Tammoysa! Siinih osisnam mannu digaalák sa keenik iyyan
  78,31,Diggah Yallak meesita mari asallam le.(limayeenih)
  78,32,Basaatin (masno) kee qinab lon
  78,33,Kaadu kaqoona ley fooduh tani lon.(inki qumri le lon)
  78,34,Kaadu galoosay gocoyuk kibuk tani lon
  78,35,Kay addal deedal maxcoo kee dirabboysiyyak tu mayaabban
  78,36,Tamah ku Rabbik galtoo kee acway dudda le kinni
  78,37,"Qaranwaa kee baaxooy, ken nammayih fanal enni ittaamih Rabbiy fulte Racmatta le.Kaâ luk yaabaanamih dudda lem matana"
  78,38,"Jibriil kee malayka saffih gacca ittah solta ayro, num keenik mayaaba racmaan kinni Rabbi idini kah yeceeh cakkit yaabá num akke waytek"
  78,39,"Toh nummah ayróy raq sinni, toysa Ellecabô maqaane isi nafsih faxe num isi Rabbî fanah madaara yaallay iimaan kee meqe taamáh abittol"
  78,40,"Diggah nanu xayi digaalál sin meesisneh, seehadayti kay namma gaba tuysukumem yable ayróy, korosti maganey burtá akkinniyoy edde iyyak"
  79,1,Yalli koros roocitte gibdi siibiyyah siibta malaykal xiibite
  79,2,Kaadu moominiin roocitte caalih tayyaaqe malaykal xiibite
  79,3,Kaadu yalli giiruh giirissa malaykay Yallih amrih wacyi oobissaah tayyaaqel xiibite
  79,4,Kaadu yalli qalaylih qalalta malaykay Yallih amri tagdabuh qalaltal xiibite
  79,5,Kaadu Yalli isi amri bicissaah tagdube malaykal xiibite
  79,6,Tangayyi (Baaxo kinnuk) tangayyeh tan ayróy gino inkih edde rabta (toh naharsi baantá fuxsunta ayró kinnuk)
  79,7,Nammey haytô baantá teetil katayta (toh ummaanim edde tanuwweeh edde ugutta baantá)
  79,8,Woo ayró koros sorkocobbaxitte meesittah
  79,9,Ken intiita xixxibittaah taqunxeeh
  79,10,diggah nee innaa gacsimelem Rabneek lakal nuwwuk addunyâ manoh iyyan
  79,11,Rumutte lafoofi tikki inneek lakalaa addunyah gacsinnam
  79,12,"Is toysa baxaysitteeh, kasaaritte madaara iyyen"
  79,13,Cagalah is ugut baanatah inki xongoló kinni
  79,14,Tokkel usun inkih saahira deqsitta baaxol nuwwwuk gaabowan (woh Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk)
  79,15,Nabiyow Nabii Muusâ xaagi kol yemeetee
  79,16,Kay Rabbi saytunnoowe daqaaray Tuwa degqsital kaah seece waqdi
  79,17,"Firqawnâ fanah gex, diggah usuk caddok tatrehik kaak axcuk"
  79,18,"Kaadu kaak ixxic: dambik saytunnowtaamih sangel maay litoo"
  79,19,Kaadu ku Rabbih inkittinaanee kee kay taaqat edde yanim koh ascassoo kaak meesita num takkemkeh
  79,20,Edde luk Nabii Muusa kaxxa astá kaa yuybulle
  79,21,Edde luk firqawni kaa dirabboyseeh cineh
  79,22,Tohuk lakal iimaanat derre cabeeh sissikuk gexe
  79,23,tokkel sinam kobxiseeh seeceh
  79,24,Anu sin Rabbiy inkih daga Raaqa kinniyo iyye
  79,25,Edde luk Yalli kaa digaaleh ellecaboh iyye maxcoo kee naharsi maxcol
  79,26,"Diggah, firqawnaa kee digaalak kaa geyteemil Yallak meesita marah elle kaskassoowaanam edde tan"
  79,27,Sinaamey ginoh gibduk raqtam siini innaa? hinnak qaranaay?xisoh kaa xisek
  79,28,Kay amo fayya heeh kaa massoyseh
  79,29,"Kaadu kay bar dattoyseeh, kay laqó ayrô diifut yeyyeeqe"
  79,30,Kaadu baaxó tohih lakal tet fidseh
  79,31,Teetik lee kee num kee lac akummu haytam teetik yeyyeeqe
  79,32,Kaadu qaleelá xiikooluh baaxot daabiseh
  79,33,Sin kee sin lacih tuxxiqih
  79,34,Tokkel qhiyaamaa kee Kaxxa gibda tamaate waqdi. (woh nammay haytó baanta kinnuk)
  79,35,Toh Num abba heem edde kassita ayró
  79,36,Kaadu jaciim deqsitta girá yaybulleen saaku yable marah
  79,37,Tokkel yallih amrih cinat caddok tatre numuh tugactek
  79,38,Kaadu akeerak addunyâ mano muxxuse num
  79,39,Toysa diggah Jaciim deqsitta girá is kay orbeyná
  79,40,"Kaadu Isi Rabbih foocih soolok meesiteeh, isi nafsi umaanê fayxik waase numuh tugactek"
  79,41,Toysa diggah jannat usuk kay orbeyná
  79,42,Nabiyow Koros qhiyaamak soltima ma waqdiiy axcuk koo esserta
  79,43,Atu tet ixxigak litom mantu tet keenih warissuh
  79,44,Tet ixxigá cagalah ku Rabbit taade
  79,45,Cagalah atu teetik meesita mara meesiise (kade) kinnito
  79,46,"Diggah usun tet yablen ayró, addunya manol carraa kee hinnay saakuk sa tu suge wee marih innah gacca iyyan"
  80,1,Nabii Fooca ribbi heeh derre cabe
  80,2,Inti mali kaal yemeeteemih
  80,3,Nabiyow maca koo tiysixxigeeh usuk kok bartah yaniimit dambik saytunnoowa way
  80,4,"Hinnay kassitaah, woo kassit kaa yanfiqe way"
  80,5,Yallal yaamineemik Gaddalita numuh tugactek
  80,6,"Tokkel Atu kaat tafkuneeh, kaat agxitta"
  80,7,Kol tanim matan usuk aaminewaah saytunnoowe waamah
  80,8,Sissikuk kol yemeete numuh tugactek
  80,9,Usuk Yallak meesitak. (woh inti mali kinnuk)
  80,10,Tokkel Atu kaak kalih marat agxitta
  80,11,"Nabiyow atu kah abtenna hinna, diggah is kassiisi"
  80,12,Tokkel faxa num kaa kasah. (Qhuraan kinnuk)
  80,13,Yalli yeynebe kitoobah addal yan. (woh Qhuraanay lowcal macfuuzul yani kinni)
  80,14,Is fayya le arac leeh saytunnowteh
  80,15,Is Taktube malaykah gabat tan
  80,16,Massakaxxa le meqe malayka
  80,17,Seehadayti abbarsıimuk maxxu koroosinnu leeh
  80,18,Yalli macak kaa ginee naharsi adda
  80,19,Tiffoytak (daacoytak) kaa gineeh ranko rankoh kaa caddoddoyseh
  80,20,Tohuk lakal gita kaah xabbacoyseh. (woh inâ bagih mawqa kinnik)
  80,21,Tohuk lakal kaa qidaah edde kaa yaaguqen magaq kaah abé.(woh kabri)
  80,22,Tohuk lakal Yalli isih faxa waqdi kaa ugsa qhiyaamah ayró
  80,23,Tonna hinnay nummah (guddunuh) Yalli kaak abá iyyeemiy kaa kah amrise maabinna
  80,24,Tokkel Seehadayti isi maaqô fanah cubbi luk wagitay
  80,25,Diggah nanu lee cayxih caxne qamburrek
  80,26,Tohuk lakal baaxó qanxisiyyah qanxisne
  80,27,Edde ambó teetit nuysubuke
  80,28,"Kaadu qinabaay, anxeexa.(saqi qayso)"
  80,29,"Kaadu zaytuunuvy, tamiira (nakila kinnuk)"
  80,30,Kaadu masnoonay (bustaanway) kiboh tani
  80,31,Kaadu caxâ mixuu kee caxuwa. (qayso)
  80,32,Sin kee sin lacah tuxxiq takkê gideh
  80,33,Tokkel Qaddik tan xongoloy ayti waysissa tamaate waqdi. (qhħiyaamâ xongolo kinnuk)
  80,34,Too ayró num isi toobokoytak kuda
  80,35,Kaadu isi inaa kee isi abbak kuda
  80,36,Kaadu isi barra kee isi xaylok kuda
  80,37,Woo saaku ummaan num keenik ise duddu haa caagidiy edde agxita le
  80,38,Too ayró meqe marih foocitte iftah
  80,39,Tasuuleeh wallittah
  80,40,Kaadu woo saaku uma marih foocittel obol yan
  80,41,Ditii kee dité tet buulta
  80,42,"Woo mari usun gibdi korosuvy, gibdi umeyniiti"
  81,1,Ayró xambaqsintaah diifi teetik kata waqdi
  81,2,Kaadu cutuk luuqa waqdi
  81,3,Kaadu qaleelá baaxô baguk gexsimtaah foyya takke waqdi
  81,4,Kaadu tabuni gaali loynamalita waqdi. (idqa gaalá kinnuk)
  81,5,Kaadu dubaali wariggâ gibdah gaaboysima waqdi
  81,6,Kaadu badwa giráh innah ursumta wagqdi
  81,7,"Kaadu nafsitte ise celtaamat xibbansinta waqdi. (woh meqe mara meqe marâ luk, uma mara uma marâ luk massoysan waqdi)"
  81,8,Kaadu nuwwih yoogoqen awká esserinta waqdi
  81,9,Maa dambih qiddinteeh (tiggifimeeh) teetik axcuk
  81,10,"Kaadu aben taamá elle tan kitooba xayyoysintaah, fakkimta waqdi"
  81,11,Kaadu qaran laaracak siibima waqdi
  81,12,"Kaadu jaciim deqsitta girá ursuntaah, hadiidigsinta waqdi"
  81,13,Kaadu jannat Yallak meesita marah xayyoysima waqdi
  81,14,"Too waqdi, nafsi maqaanek hinnay umaanek xayoysitem yaaxigeh"
  81,15,Yalli laqó ifi kak qellita cutuukal xiibite
  81,16,Gexxa cutuukay isi aroocat qellittal xiibite
  81,17,Kaadu bari dité baaha waqdil xiibite
  81,18,Kaadu maaci diifu baaha waqdil xiibite
  81,19,Diggah qhuraan massâ kaxxa le farmoytih (jibriil kinnuk) maxca
  81,20,"Usuk (Jibriil kinnuk) caylaleeh fayya le arac le, qarshi le rabbih xaqul"
  81,21,"Wokkel malayka kaa oggoltaah, wacyil amaanat le"
  81,22,Kaadu sin kataysa (Nabii kinnuk) cabuli akke waamal xiibite
  81,23,"Nummah Nabii jibriil, Yalli kaa edde gine weelot ayro mawqa le gambik baxxaqqa le ikkel kaa yuble"
  81,24,Usuk (Nabii kinnuk) wacyi gudduysiyyal cillaaleli hinna. (cinnaane li/gabâ gibda li)
  81,25,Kaadu ta Qhuraan Yallih Racmatak xiiriyime sheetaanih maxca hinna
  81,26,Toysa anke gexxaanaah qhuraan dirabbosseenik
  81,27,"Usuk (Qhuraan kinnuk) gersim hinna, Yallak kassiisih insii kee jinnih oobe kitab akke waytek"
  81,28,Siinik cakkii kee iimaanal soolam faxah yan numuh kassiisi
  81,29,Isin faxxaanam matakka Yallay ginô Rabbih yani faxah akke waytek
  82,1,Qaran qanxixa waqdi
  82,2,Kaadu cutuk luuqa waqdi
  82,3,"Kaadu badwa sittal tanfuxxukumeeh, sittat tangale wagqdi"
  82,4,Magooqa fokkaqsimtaah addat sugtem iró ciggilsinta waqdi
  82,5,Woo waqdi ummaan nafsi yaaxigeh yuysukumem kee udurrusem taamak
  82,6,Kee seehadaytow maca koo duquurussaah ku Rabbiy cinda lek
  82,7,"Kaay koo gineeh, koo massoyseeh soolo koo yeymeeqe"
  82,8,Isih faxxa hee weelol koo bicseeh gine
  82,9,"Tonna hinnay, a korosey isin nummah gital matanin galtoh ayró dirabbossaana ikkalah"
  82,10,"Diggah, sin dacrissa malayka dacayrih siinit tan"
  82,11,Yallih garil massakaxxa le kutbe abta malayka sin taama dacrissam
  82,12,Isin abba haytaanam taaxigeh
  82,13,Diggah meqe mari jannatal yalli keenih yeceeh yan niqmatat yan
  82,14,Kaadu diggah umam aba mari (koros kinnuk) Jaciim deqsitta girah addal yan
  82,15,Usun galtoh ayró (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) tet culan
  82,16,Kaadu usun teetik cerrita mara hinnon (inkinnah teetik mayawqan)
  82,17,Kaadu maca koo tiysixxigeeh galtoh ayró kinnim
  82,18,"Tohuk lakal maca koo tiysixxigeeh, galtoh ayró kinnim"
  82,19,"Woh ayroy nafsi nafsih tu edde xiqe waah, woo saaku amri Yalli le"
  83,1,Keexoo kee midaan daggoysa marah finqaa kee digaala tan
  83,2,Usun Sinaamak keexitan waqdi dudsuta mara keexoo kee midaan
  83,3,Kaadu usun sinaamah keexeenik hinnay sinaamah miidaanise yakken waqdi daggoysaanah
  83,4,Woo mari diggah sinni magooqak ugtoonu waanam Mayasmitaanaa
  83,5,Nabah tan ayrot
  83,6,Woh sinam ginô Rabbih foocal soltu wayta ayró cisab kee galtoh
  83,7,Nummah asmatah! umá marih kitab baaxok gubal sijjiin deqsita aracay ceya lel yan
  83,8,Sijjiin kinnim maca koo tiysixxigeeh
  83,9,Kitaabay yunkuttubey gaba kak kaleeni kinni
  83,10,Woo ayró finqi yan dirabboysa marah
  83,11,Woh galtoh ayró (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) dirabboysa mara
  83,12,"Kaadu tet dirabbossam matan, ummaan caddok taturliy maggo dambilih yani akke waytek"
  83,13,Ni Qhuraanih aayoota kaal yakriyen waqdi naharsi marih hayyayoonay tunkuttube iyye
  83,14,"Tonna hinnay usuk Yallih kitaabâ ikkal, usun abak sugen uma taamoomi (dambi kinnuk) ken sorkocobaxitte buulteh Qhuraan nummaysaanamak"
  83,15,"Wonna hinnay diggah, usun (koros kinnuk) woo ayro (Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk) sinni Rabbik rebsimaanaah kaa mayablan"
  83,16,"Tohuk lakal diggah, usun jaciim deqsitta girá cula mara kinnon"
  83,17,"Tohuk lakal: tah woo girah digaalay isin dirabboysak sugteeni keenik iyyan"
  83,18,Nummah digga luk meqe marih (moominiin kinnuk) kitab jannatak fayya le aracay Qilliyyiin deqsital yan
  83,19,Maca koo tiysixxigeeh Qilliyyuun kinnim
  83,20,"Woh kitaabay yunkuttubeeh, gaba kak kaleeni kinni"
  83,21,Yalli xayyoyseh yan malayka kaah sumaaqitta
  83,22,Diggah meqe mari jannatal yalli keenih yeceeh yan niqmatat yan
  83,23,Sinni Rabbii kee usuk keenih massoyseemî fan Qaraakiy amok wagtan
  83,24,Niqmatat yaniinim keenik ken foocitteh wir kee nooril taaxige
  83,25,Liyyuk yan gocoyuy alifut yanik Ken yafqen
  83,26,"Ellecabo kak miski suruylek, woo Niqmatih geytoh qalala mari qalalay"
  83,27,Kaadu tasniim deqsitta darak tu kaat yasgalleen (daragu kinnuk)
  83,28,Is (tasniim kinnuk) jannatti daray Yalli xayyoyseh yan mari kak yaaqube kinni
  83,29,"Diggah, isi taama yoysomme mari (koros kinnuk), yeemene maral asaaluk sugen addunyal anqasah"
  83,30,"Kaadu keenil dardaran (xaqxaqan) waqdi, intiitaa kee miniina sittah casak sugen keenit aban anqasah"
  83,31,"Kaadu sinni marâ fanah yandabben waqdi, sattaluk andabbuk sugen moominiinit aben xagaa kee anqasah"
  83,32,"Kaadu moominiin yablen waqdi, diggah a mari makkoote mara axcuk sugen"
  83,33,Kaadu ama koros moominiin dacrisa marah anuk ma rubsuminnon
  83,34,"Edde luk Qhiyaamah ayro, yeemene mari korosul yasuuleeh, anqasah"
  83,35,Sinni Rabbii kee usuk keenih massoyseemî fan Qaraakiy amok wagtan jannatal
  83,36,"Koros addunyal abak sugte umaaneenaa kee dambittel galtimtee? Yeey, dudda le galtoh galtimte"
  84,1,"Qaran qanxixa waqdi, (woh Qhiyaamah ayró)"
  84,2,"Kaadu isi Rabbih ayti yaceeh, kay amri oggolam cakkik kaal tan"
  84,3,"Kaadu baaxó fidsimtaah, farakka itta waqdi"
  84,4,"Kaadu tet addat tanim qambissaah, foyyah kak raqta"
  84,5,"Kaadu isi Rabbih ayti taceeh, kay amri oggoltam cakkik teetil tan"
  84,6,"Kee ta seehadaytow diggah, atu isi Rabbî fanah gexxaah , meqe taama abtek hinnay uma taama abtek, tokkel atu qhiyaamah ayró kaat angoorewettooh abteemil koo galte le"
  84,7,"Tokkel Le kitab migdak kah yontocowwime numuh tu gactek, (moomintu kinnuk)"
  84,8,Toysa Sahalik tan fokkaaqoh (cisab kinnuk fokkaaqime le sarriinoh)
  84,9,Kaadu isi marâ fanah wallitak yandabbe.(jannatal)
  84,10,"Kaadu Le kitab kay xiiroonih derrek kah yontocowwime numuh tu gactek,(korosta kinnuk)"
  84,11,Toysa Sarriinoh finqaa kee baatih deerise le (seece le)
  84,12,Urta girá culele tet niqna tammoysuh
  84,13,Diggah usuk addunyal isi marih addal wallitak suge
  84,14,Diggah usuk isi Rabbî fanah inkinnah aduure wayu waam yekkele
  84,15,"Yeey, Yalli kaa gacsele! diggah kay Rabbi kaa yabalih sugeeh kay caalat yaaxigeh"
  84,16,Yalli korta ayról ciggiila qasa caawil xiibite
  84,17,Kaadu bar kee usuk gaaboyseemil (yaskatteemil) xiibite
  84,18,"Kaadu alsal xiibite, noori teetik duuda waqdi"
  84,19,Diggah gurraak gurral (caalataak caalatal) koretton sinaamey
  84,20,Toysa kah aamine waanam maca loonuv? (koros kinnuk)
  84,21,"Kaadu Qhuraan keenil yankirriyime waqdi, Yallah kah kummaate waanaah kah rammite waanam macalon"
  84,22,"Tonna hinnay, koroosite mari rabak lakal ugut yanim dirabboysah"
  84,23,Yalli yaaxigeh usun sinni sorkocobbaxittet qellissi haanam. (qinaadi kee koroosannuk)
  84,24,Toysa nabiyow ken aytikumus qansarissa digaalál
  84,25,"Kinnih immay yeemeneeh meqe taamoomi abbaasite mari, aggiriqqe sinni galto le akeeral"
  85,1,Yalli mafdagoogi le qaraanal xiibite
  85,2,Kaadu Yalli isi naqoosa gaaboysu waamah xagana keenih edde hee ayrol xiibite (woh Qhiyaamah ayró)
  85,3,"Kaadu sumaaqitée kee, elle sumaaqiteynal xiibite"
  85,4,Moominiin elle digaaluh Baaxó dageeh qanxise mari abbarsimeh
  85,5,Bocot urta gibdi girá elle ursan. (yeemene mara edde carrisoonuh)
  85,6,Usun woo waqdi tet amol daffeyak yenen
  85,7,Usun yeemene maral baahaanamal gaabowwu iyyeenih assalaalaquk sugen
  85,8,"Ken kah digaaleenim matan, Yallay mayso leeh fayla lel yeemeneenim akke waytek"
  85,9,"Kaay qaranwaa kee baaxô mulki le (kobor le), kaadu Yalli ummaanim yabali kinniih kaak qellittam matan"
  85,10,"Diggah moominiinih tan labhaa kee moominiinih tan sayyó girat carrise mari, tohuk lakat atoobee weenik, usun jahaannam digaalá lon. Kaadu ken carrissa digaalá lon"
  85,11,"Diggah, yeemeneeh meqe taamoomi abbaasite mari, jannatittey guba weeqaytitte kak gexxa lon, toh kaxxa maffaafa kinni.(asallama)"
  85,12,"Diggah, ku Rabbik xibix kaxxam gibdi digaalah yabbixe wagqdi"
  85,13,"Diggah usuk ginó suge waytik qimbisaah, ken bayseek geeral ken gacisah"
  85,14,"Kaadu usuk dambi cabtiliiy, kacanu le Rabbi moominiinih"
  85,15,Qarshi le Rabbiy nabna le kinni
  85,16,Isih faxxa haam abe kinni
  85,17,Nabiyow isi ambiya dirabbosse Qandeh xaagi koo gufee
  85,18,Firqawnaa kee samuud deqsita mara kinni
  85,19,Wonna hinnay koroosite mari ku dirabboysiyyat yan
  85,20,Yalli keenik derrek marot ken yabbixe
  85,21,"Koros kaa elle weelossa inna hinnay, usuk Qhuraanay nabna le kinni"
  85,22,Usuk daccarsime luucih addal yan. (lowcal macfuuz kinnuk)
  86,1,Yalli qaran kee bar mira cutuktal xiibite
  86,2,Kaadu maca koo tiysixxigee bar mira cutukti kinnim
  86,3,"Usuk bolok iyya cutuktay, diifut dite boohaysa kinni"
  86,4,Hebeltô nafsi mayan malaykatti dacayrih amol kaak yanih akke waytek
  86,5,Toysa Seehadayti wagitay cubbusay kak ginniimem
  86,6,Usuk leey (woh daacoyta kinnuk) sissikuk kaqittak ginniime
  86,7,Numtin xiiron kee barrah aliilik fanak tawqe
  86,8,Diggah tohuk kaa gine Rabbi kaa gacsaamah duddali kinni. rabeek lakal
  86,9,Kassit! Niyaayik lubbittet qellittem fokkaqsimtaah tamballu wayta ayro (woh Qhiyaamah ayró)
  86,10,"Toysa Usuk cayla maliiy, cateyna mali"
  86,11,Yalli qaraanay qagaa-qagita roblel xiibite
  86,12,Kaadu baaxoy teetik tawqeemit baqittal xiibite
  86,13,Diggah Qhuraan yani deedalak baxissa maxcó kinni
  86,14,Kaadu usuk digir hinna
  86,15,Diggah usun Nabiih uma malah malsan.(koros kinnuk)
  86,16,Kaadu wohuk gibdi malah anu keenih malsa cakki yambulleemkeh
  86,17,"Tokkel Nabiyow Ķoros qambaalis, digaalah obtit keenih maqataatakinaay dagoh gide ken qambaalis"
  87,1,Ku Rabbiy kaxxa fayya leh migaq saytunnos
  87,2,Yallay ginoona gineeh massoyséh migaqa
  87,3,Kaadu Kaay tu isih elle faxxa hee innal caggudusey gino tirri hee tet celtaah teetik faxximtaamah
  87,4,Kaadu Kaay anxax qayso baaxok yeyyeeqeh
  87,5,Tohuk wadir kafteeh data ruma tet abe
  87,6,"Nabiyow ama qhuraan koo akriyisennooh, inkinnah kaa mahawwenta"
  87,7,"Yalli faxem akke waytek, diggah usuk tambulleem kee qellittam yaaxigeh.(maxcoo kee taamak)"
  87,8,Kaadu maqaanê gita koh xabbacoysenno
  87,9,Tokkel Nabiyow isi mara ĶKassis! kassis tu-xiqek
  87,10,Yallak meesitah yan num kassite lek.(moomintu kinnuk)
  87,11,Kaadu gibdi umeyni kassitik axxeere-lek.(korosta kinnuk)
  87,12,Kaay kaxxa girá cula
  87,13,"Tohuk lakal usuk tet addal marabaay, mayanuwwa"
  87,14,Nummah isi nafsi dambik saytunnoyse num naggooweh
  87,15,"Kaadu isi Rabbih migaq cuseeh kaa inkittoyseeh, wonnaluk salaate num"
  87,16,Wonna hinnay isin addunyâ mano muxxussan akeerak
  87,17,"Akeera mano tayseeh, raqtaah waartah"
  87,18,Diggah tama sin kassisnem naharsi kitoobal tan
  87,19,Toh Nabii Ibraahim kee Nabii Muusal obte kitooba
  88,1,Nabiyow Qhiyaamah ayroy Ghaashiya deqsittah xaagi koo gufeh innaa
  88,2,Woo ayro Koros foocitte taqunxeeh digaalat
  88,3,"Is addunyal umaaneenâ taamittaah, akeeral girah addal digaalâ taqabta"
  88,4,Niqnah solak tan girá culta
  88,5,Niqnâ gibdah facta darah leek tet yafqen
  88,6,Usun maaqó malon uma caxay dariiq deqsitta akke waytek
  88,7,"Is magablussaay, qululuk xiqtam mali"
  88,8,Moominiin foocitte woo ayro saytuniih wir itta
  88,9,Addunyal abitte isi meqe taama takcineeh ruffu itta akeeral
  88,10,Fayya iyya jannatih addal
  88,11,Uma yab kay addal ma taabba
  88,12,Kay addal gexxa dara tan
  88,13,Fayya iyya qaraakiy kay addal yan
  88,14,Kaadu kobboyaayiy maaqabah massoysimteeh daroorî qaxal heeni kay addal tan edde yaaquboonuh
  88,15,Kaadu Rooruh tan barkumaami (makaddid) kay addal tan
  88,16,Kaadu fidut tan fidooda kay addal tan
  88,17,Ta koros gaali elle ginniime inna ma wagittaay ma cubbussaa
  88,18,Kaadu qaran fayya elle heen inna
  88,19,"Kaadu qaleela elle dabsimteeh, karersimte inna"
  88,20,Kaadu baaxó elle fidsimte inna
  88,21,Toysa kassis! Nabiyow atu cagalah kassiisé kinnitok
  88,22,Atu iimaanah ken dirkisa num hinnito
  88,23,"Kinnih immay iimaanat derre cabeeh, koroosite num"
  88,24,Toysa Yalli kaxxa digaalah kaa digaale le
  88,25,Diggah ken madaara nee fan akkele rabeeniik lakal
  88,26,Tohuk lakal diggah ken cisab (fokkaaqo) kee galtó nel tan
  89,1,Yalli maacal xiibite
  89,2,Kaadu qarafah alsak naharsi tabna baral xiibite
  89,3,Kaadu ummaan iimik nammay takkem (xibbaan) kee alluudah taniimil xiibite
  89,4,Kaadu bari yamaate waqdii kee bari dardara waqdil xiibite
  89,5,"Tama hiimiy yalli elle xiibitet kas le numuh kaa xiqtah tan xiiba tanii? yeey, tanih"
  89,6,Ma tablannaa! Nabiyow ku Rabbi Qaad deqsita marak kah abenna
  89,7,Usun Iram deqsittâ kedoy kaxxa caylaay fayya le xisne luk tene
  89,8,Is tet celtam Baaxô bagul kak ginniime wayte kedó kinni
  89,9,"Kaadu Nabiyow ku Rabbi Samuud deqsita maray, qaleela ureeh, qarwah haysitek abem ma tablannaa Waad deqsita daqaaral"
  89,10,Kaadu Firqawnay xiikooluy (kadeeday) sinam edde digaala lek kah abe inna
  89,11,Usun caddok tatre mara baaxol
  89,12,Edde luk usun tet addal umaane yeymeggee mara
  89,13,"Tokkel Ku Rabbi lafit le digaala keenil caxeeh, oobise"
  89,14,"Nabiyow diggah, ku Rabbi kulli seehadaytih taama dacrisaah ken elle galte le"
  89,15,"Seehadaytuh tu gactek kay Rabbi kaa yiqiyyireeh (mokkoreeh), kaah yemqeeh kaa hatkise kaa tekkek, yi Rabbi yoh yemqeh iyya"
  89,16,"Kaadu kaa yiqiyyireeh, Isi quusi (rizqhi) kaal ceyse kaa tekkek, yi Rabbi yoo yuyqunxeh iyya"
  89,17,"Tu elle tanim tonna hinna a seehadaytow, isin qayxixxuh matamqaanaay kaa matassakaxxan"
  89,18,Kaadu tu dagoyti askamiyyah sitta milsissan (ma lallabtan)
  89,19,Kaadu nagrâ maalu cakki maliinoh gibdi makmoh takmen
  89,20,Kaadu maalu kaxxa kacanuh kicinton
  89,21,"Tonna hinnay, baaxó kaxxa angoyyih tangayyeeh, bululsimiyyah bululsimta waqdi"
  89,22,"Kaadu Nabiyow ku Rabbi yamaateeh, malayka massa massah (saffi saffih) gacta"
  89,23,"Kaadu woo ayró (Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk) jahannam bahsimah, too ayró seehadayti iimaan kee meqe taamay addunyal cinak suge kassitah, woo kassit kee nadaama mannal tu kaah xiqtaa"
  89,24,Maganey! inni manol maqaané uysukumeh suginniyoy iyya
  89,25,"Woo saaku Yallih digaalah innah tan digaalah, num ma digaala"
  89,26,Kaadu Yallih axawih innah yan axawah num ma yaxaa
  89,27,Kee satta iyye nafsow. (yallih cusiyyaa kee iimaanat)
  89,28,"Isi Rabbî fanah uduur usuk koh yeceem oggolak akcanuk, usuk ku meqe taama kok oggoleeh, Raabitehik"
  89,29,Toysa Yi naqoosay meqey moominiinih tanih loowot cul
  89,30,Kaadu keenî luk Yi jannat cul
  90,1,Ta baaxól xiibita. (makka kinnuk)
  90,2,Nabiyow atu ta baaxol dabqih yan num kinnito
  90,3,Kaadu xaltanii kee xaleenimil xiibita
  90,4,Nummah seehadaytu taqabih ginne addunyal rabba iyyam fan
  90,5,Usuk (korosta kinnuk) num ise duude waam yakkalee
  90,6,"Hiddootak: maggo maalu Mucammad qadaawatah bayse iyya"
  90,7,Usuk num isi ablewaam yakkalee? yalli kaa yablehik
  90,8,Namma inti kaah mahanninoo edde yabaluh
  90,9,Kaadu arrabaa kee namma sokto (arrobta kinnuk) kaah mahanninoo
  90,10,Kaadu namma gita kaah mabaxxaqisinninoo? (umaanee kee maqaanê gita kinnuk)
  90,11,Toysa Isi maalu meqe gital yaceemit dook (woh akeerâ gibdaabina kinnuk) macah tatre wee
  90,12,doô tatur kinnim maca koo tiysixxigeeh
  90,13,Woh naqoosannuk moomintoh tan naqso currusaanama
  90,14,Hinnay qulul edde gibdih yan ayróh addat maaqo yaskameenimi
  90,15,Xayi qayxixxuy ramad le yaskameenimi
  90,16,Hinnay tumaliy tussinnah burtat kafe yaskameenimi
  90,17,"Wohuk lakal yeemeneeh, sabril titta farriimeeh, xuwaawal titta farriime marih num yakkeemi"
  90,18,Woh migdi maray moominiinih yani kinni
  90,19,"Kaadu ni aayootal (Qhuraan kinnuk) koroosite mari, usun guri mara"
  90,20,Usun keenil alfimte girah addat yanin
  91,1,Yalli ayróo kee tet wallaqental xiibite
  91,2,"Kaadu alsál xiibite, teetil katayta waqdi"
  91,3,"Kaadu laqól xiibite, is dite kalta waqdi"
  91,4,"Kaadu baral xiibite, usuk ditet baaxó buula waqdi"
  91,5,Kaadu qaran kee qaran xise Rabbil xiibite
  91,6,Kaadu baaxóo kee baaxó fidse Rabbil xiibite
  91,7,Kaadu nafsii kee nafsi massoyse Rabbil xiibite
  91,8,Tokkel umaanê gitaa kee maqaane teetik edde tan gita teetih baxxaqiseh
  91,9,Nummah dambik tet saytunnoyse num naggooweh
  91,10,Kaadu nummah umaanet tet yubkune num baxaysiteh
  91,11,"Samuud deqgsita mari Yallih farmoyta Nabii Saalic dirabboyseh, usun umaanet caddok tatreenimih sabbatah"
  91,12,Woo marak umaaneh gibdi num kaqteeh alá yusguude waqdi
  91,13,"Tokkel Yallih farmoyti Nabii saalic keenik iyyeh: Yallih alá umaaneh maxaginaay, tet arakih ayró teetih caba"
  91,14,"Tokkel kaa dirabboyseeniih, tet yusguudeeniih, ken Rabbi digaalá ken duuduseh aliffi keenil hee ken dambih, Woo digaalá keenil massoyseh.(num keenik ma- raaqinna woo digaalák)"
  91,15,Yalli keenil baaheemik ciggiiliyyah kak meesitâ mali
  92,1,"Yalli baral xiibite, bari ditet baaxó buula waqdi"
  92,2,"Kaadu laqól xiibite, is diifut baaxó ifissi hayta waqdi"
  92,3,Kaadu labtii kee saytiyá gine Rabbi isil xiibite
  92,4,"Diggah sin taama sissinih, isin addunyah taamita maraa kee akeerah taamita marah anuk"
  92,5,"Tokkel Yalli acuya iyyem yeceeh, Yallak meesite numuh tu-gactek"
  92,6,Kaadu maqaaney (jannat kinnuk) yalli meqe marah massoyse nummaysek
  92,7,Toysa maqaanê gita kaah xabbacoysenno
  92,8,"Kaadu cillaaliteeh, Yallak gaddalime numuh tu-gactek"
  92,9,Kaadu maqaaney (jannat kinnuk) yalli meqe marah massoyse dirabboysek
  92,10,Toysa umaanê gita kaal xabbacoysenno
  92,11,"Usuk girat rada waqdi, kay maali tu kaah maxiqa"
  92,12,Diggah tirtô gitay massa le baxxaqisnam nel tan
  92,13,Kaadu diggah ellecabô dabqii (akeera) kee naharsi dabqil (addunyal) enni ittam inkih nanu lino
  92,14,"Toysa, urtah hadiidigta giral sin meesiisa"
  92,15,Tet cultam matan gibdi umeyna akke waytek
  92,16,"Usuk Nabii dirabboyseeh, iimaanat derre cabe numu"
  92,17,Teetik axxersimele Yallak kaxxam meesita num
  92,18,"Usuk isi maalu yacee numu, ise saytunnoysâ gideh"
  92,19,Kaadu hebltô numuy kay xaqul elle galtima niqmat ley kaah yemqe mayan
  92,20,"Kinnih immay, usuk tamah kah abem fayya iyya Rabbih foocih fayxi kinni"
  92,21,Kaadu usuk sarrah galtot ruffu axceleeh teetit leedele jannat culuwaa saaku
  93,1,Yalli wallaqental xiibite
  93,2,Kaadu bari diteh mudugi yakke waqdil xiibite
  93,3,"Nabiyow ku Rabbi koo cabe weeh, koo anqibe weemil"
  93,4,"Kaadu diggah, wadirsitto (akeera) naharsittok (addunyak) koh tayseemil"
  93,5,"Kaadu ku Rabbi sarroh (akeeral) kulli niqmat koh aceeleeh, kaat leedettooh ruffu kaat axcetto"
  93,6,"Nabiyow ku Rabbi qayxixxuh koo geeh, aracay elle orobta koh maabinnaa? abeh"
  93,7,"Kaadu kitab kee iimaan kinnim aaxige waa numuy garcit yanih koo geeh, tirri koo mahannaa"
  93,8,"Kaadu tu malih koo geeh, koo magaddalisinnaa"
  93,9,"Toysa atu toh teexegek, qayxixxu le cakkik ma gutqin"
  93,10,"Kaadu kallaci aba numuh tu gactek, kaa ma xiiriyinay meqe qangara kaal gacis"
  93,11,"Ku Rabbih niqmatah tugactek, kaat walalaay kaa elle faatit"
  94,1,Nabiyow Alil koh farakka ma hanninoo islaamaninnoo kee nubuwwannul
  94,2,Kaadu qilsi quuka kok moobisinninoo
  94,3,Qilsi quukay xiiron kok yiyqilseek
  94,4,Kaadu fayya koh mahanninoo ku xagar (galab) xago
  94,5,Toysa diggah gibdaabinâ luk xabca tan
  94,6,Diggah gibdaabinâ luk xabca tan
  94,7,"Toysa Nabiyow isi caagiidak tamurruqe waqdi, qibaadat taqabaay teetil ingicilliy"
  94,8,Kaadu Ku Rabbih xaqul taniimih sangeelaay kaa kallacit (jannat kinnuk)
  95,1,Yalli xiibiteh Tiin kee Zaytuun deqsitta namma caxal
  95,2,Kaadu qaley Tuuri siina deqsittal xiibite
  95,3,Kaadu a baaxoy saay lel xiibite. (Makka kinnuk)
  95,4,Nummah seehadaytu tayse weelol ginne
  95,5,"Wohuk lakal usuk yallih amri oggole weeh, kay farmoytit kataate week girak gubi gubah kaa gacsenno"
  95,6,"Takkay ikkal, yeemeneeh meqe taamoomi abbaasite mari, aggiriqqe wayta galtó le akeeral"
  95,7,Tokkel tahak wadir seehadaytow galtóh ayróh (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk ) dirabboysiyyat maca koo bahtaah
  95,8,"Yalli mekla abba haytaamak meklah yaysi hinnaa? Yeey, kinnih"
  96,1,Nabiyow ku Rabbiy gino gineh yanih migaaqal ikriy
  96,2,Seehadaytu dabloytak gine Rabbi kinni
  96,3,Nabiyow! ku Rabbiy kaxxa cinda leh migaaqal ikriy
  96,4,Usuk kalamat elle yaktuben gurra barse Rabbi kinni
  96,5,"Usuk seehadaytu, aaxaguk suge weem barse Rabbi kinni"
  96,6,"Nummah, diggah seehadayti umaanet caddok tatrah"
  96,7,Gaddalitem isik yable waqdi
  96,8,Diggah madaara ku Rabbî fanah takke Nabiyow
  96,9,Nabiyow tableh innaa a numuy waasa? (abu jahal kinnuk)
  96,10,Yallih naqsi (Nabii Mucammad Aasaeiiķo kinnuk) salat aba waqdi
  96,11,"Yoh warisey ta salaatak waasâ num, usuk tirtô bagul yene kaa tekkek"
  96,12,Hinnay Yallak meesil amrisa num yekkek. (wohuk anninnal kaa waasaah)
  96,13,"Nabiyow! Yoh warisey ta sinam waasa num Qhuraan dirabboyseeh, iimaanat derre cabe kaa tekkek"
  96,14,Usuk maaxiginnaa? Diggah Yalli usuk abba haam yable Rabbi kinnim
  96,15,"Caagid usuk (abu jahal kinnuk) elle yakkale inna hinna, usuk tamahak kate wee kaa tekkek gombo kaak gibdi xibixih abbixenno, jahannam girat kaa gasiyak"
  96,16,"Kay gombo, dirabley, hoxa leh tani kinni"
  96,17,Tokkel usuk kaa qokla marah deerisay
  96,18,Nanu girá dacrissa malaykay giral sinam digaaltah seecennok
  96,19,"Caagid usuk (abu jahal kinnuk) elle yakkale inna hinna, Nabiyow kay yab moggolinaay, salaatah kummaataay isi Rabbit xayyow"
  97,1,Diggah Nanu muxxó le baray leylatul Qhadri deqsitat kaa (Qhuraan kinnuk ) oobisne Ramdaanak
  97,2,Nabiyow leylatul Qhadri bar kinnim maca koo tiysixxigeeh
  97,3,"Leylatul Qhadri usuk baray muxxó ley, alfi alsak kayrih aysuk raaqa kinni"
  97,4,"Tama barat malaykaa kee Jibriiliy ruuc deqsita qaraanak edde obta, sinni Rabbih idnih, ummaan caagidiy Yalli woo liggidih addat mekle luk"
  97,5,"Woo bari saayaay nagaaya, maaci maacissi iyyam fanah"
  98,1,"Kitab elle oobe marak yahuud kee nasaarak koroosite maraa kee Yallat agleyta haa mari, baxxaqqa geyyi haanam fanah edde sugen koroosannuk kata mara makkinnon"
  98,2,Woh Yallih farmoyta Mucammaday saytun kitooba (Qhuraan kinnuk) yakriye
  98,3,Woo kitoobah addal nuimmâ xaagittee kee qadaalatal tan amrittey massal tani tan
  98,4,"Mabaxsiminna kitab akah yontocowwime mari (yahuud kee nasaarak), baxxaqqa (Nabii kee Qhuraan kinnuk) keenih temeeteek wadir akke waytek"
  98,5,"Kaadu usun kalah kah amrisimeenim malon yallah qibaada caglisak, kaa yaqbudeeniih baatil diinittek inkih islaam diinî fanah keltaanaah salat soolisaanaah zaka yaceenim akke waytek, woh massa le diini kinni"
  98,6,"Diggah kitab elle oobe marak koroosittem kee Yallat agleyta haa mari, jahannam girah addal yan, teetil waarak, woo mari usun ginok umaaneh gacta ginó kinnon"
  98,7,"Diggah yeemeneeh meqe taamoomi abe mari, woo mari usun ginok tayse ginó kinnon"
  98,8,"Ken galto ken Rabbih xaqul Qhiyaamah ayro qadni deqsitta jannootay guba weeqaytitte kak gexxa, umman kay addal waarak. Yalli meqe taamoomi keenik raabiteh, kaadu usun kaak raabiteenih keenih abe konnaba, woh isi Rabbik meesite marih galto"
  99,1,Baaxó isi angoyyih tasgayyime wagqdi
  99,2,Kaadu baaxó isi addal taniimiy qilsi tayyaaqe waqdi (rabtem tekkek wohuk kalah tanim tekkek)
  99,3,Kaadu seehadayti is lem macaay iyya wariggah
  99,4,Woo ayró (qhiyaamah ayró) is isi bagul umaanee kee maqaanek abeenimih xaagu inkih warissah
  99,5,Diggah ku Rabbi tet amriseemih sabbatah
  99,6,"Woo ayró sinam soolô ballaaqak taduureh fixiixih anuk, ken taamoomi ken yaybulloonuh ken elle galtoonuh"
  99,7,"Tokkel maqaanek qunxa xuuneyti qilsah gide abe num, wohih galto able le"
  99,8,"Kaadu umaanek qunxa xuuneyti qilsah gide abe num, wohih galto able le"
  100,1,Yalli qaduwwî fanah sissikuk yarde faarisiy fuftoh fuf iyyal xiibite
  100,2,Edde luk xukuuqunut ardi gibdah xinkilliq yayyaaqe faarisil xiibite
  100,3,Edde luk qaduwwi maaca warara faarisil xiibite usuk garcit (karcit) anuk
  100,4,Tokkel is abtah tan ardih gibdah sawar (fulle) fuluk hayta
  100,5,Kaadu woo ardat isi macaxu qaduwwi macaxih addal macsissal xiibite
  100,6,"Diggah, seehadayti isi Rabbih niqmat yangaddi kinni"
  100,7,Kaadu diggah usuk wohul isi nafsil sumaaqita num kinni
  100,8,"Kaadu diggah, usuk maaluh gibdi kacanu le num kinni"
  100,9,Tokkel mayaaxiga innaa! seehadayti kaa qambaltam magooqat enni ittam Yalli yayyaaqu waa waqdi cisab kee galtoh
  100,10,Kaadu umaanee kee maqaanek alilwat qellisimak sugtem geytimtu waytam mayaaxiga innaa
  100,11,Diggah ken Rabbi ken kee ken taamoomik woo ayro adda yaaxigi kinni
  101,1,"Al-Qhaariqa: is Qhiyaamah ayroy sinam lubbitte meesissot taagureh migaq kinni"
  101,2,Al-Qhaariqa is macaay
  101,3,Maca koo tiysixxigee Nabiyow Al- Qhaariqa kinnim
  101,4,Seehadá fixix kee magga gibdah laahintih (ufuy mali kinnuk) innah edde gacta ayró
  101,5,Kaadu qaleelá fakfaken suufih (woh illi xagooru) innah edde gacta ayró
  101,6,Tokkel maqaanê miidaan kak yiqilseeh yan numuh tugactek
  101,7,Toysa usuk rufto le mano le jannatal
  101,8,Kaadu miidaan haliffi akak iyye numuh tu gactek
  101,9,Toysa kay orbeyna haawiya deqsitta girá
  101,10,Maca koo tiysixxigeeh Nabiyow is kinnim
  101,11,Is giray gibdi niqna le kinni
  102,1,Maaluu kee xaylô maggal sittal hiddottaanaah (tirtirissan) Yallih taaqatak sin agxisseh
  102,2,Rabi sin elelliiy magooqa guffu haytaanam fan
  102,3,Tonna hinnay sarrah aaxigetton! (rabi lakal)
  102,4,Kaadu nuimmah sarrah aaxigetton!ellecaboh ayroh digaala siinil obta waqdi
  102,5,Tonna hinnay isin sin qambaltam asmatah aaxiginnitoonuy edde taniinimik waasimak tenen
  102,6,"Yalli xiibiteh diggah, jaciim deqsitta girá ablettoonumul"
  102,7,Kaadu diggah asmat le mablah tet abletton
  102,8,Tohuk lakal diggah woo ayró (Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk) isin addunyal edde agxitak sugten niqmatak esserimetton
  103,1,Yalli waktil xiibite
  103,2,"Diggah, seehadayti finqat yaniimil"
  103,3,"Yeemene maray meqe taamoomi abeeh, cakkil sitta farriimeeh, sabril sitta farriime koh raaquh"
  104,1,Ummaan camiliy sinam qaybisaah ilqah Fingaa kee baati tan
  104,2,Maalu gaaboyseeh lowalloowe num
  104,3,Diggah usuk isi maali isi waarisu waam yakkale addunyal
  104,4,Caagid usuk elle yakkale inna hinna! Diggah usuk cutama degqsitta giray edde qambisinnaanihim bokookissát gasyime le
  104,5,nabiyow Maca koo tiysixxigeeh cutamá kinnim
  104,6,Is Yallih giray ursumteeh hadiidigsinte kinni
  104,7,Is leh tan niqnah gibdah xagarak sorkocobbaxittel bukku itta
  104,8,Diggah is keenil alfimteh kaluqqu itte
  104,9,Usun makaadooday ruubumut tanih addat axawat anuk. (teetik awqe waanâ gidah)
  105,1,Nabiyow! Ku Rabbi dakanu leh yan marak kah abenna Matablannaa
  105,2,Yalli Ken uma mala finqa maabinnaa
  105,3,Kaadu haadá butta buttah keenit ruube itta kataatak
  105,4,Xeetiy cararte kallak yani keenil qambissa
  105,5,tokkel ruma yekke caffaa kee cafulay yonkommeh inna ken abe
  106,1,Qhureyshi deqsittah tan kedo luk sugte qaadáa kee edde sugen saay ma qajjibsittaanaa
  106,2,Ken qaada gilal yamanâ fanah arhoh aban safar kee cagay shaamâ fanah aban safar kinni meesite kalah.(Yalli keenih yecee amaan kee niqmata)
  106,3,Toysa a Qarih Rabbi (kaqbá kinnuk) yaqbudoonay qibaadá kaah caglisak
  106,4,"Woh Yallay qululuk ken yoskomeeh, conxok amaan (saay) keenih yecee kinni"
  107,1,Galtoh ayró dirabboysa numih caalat yoh warisey
  107,2,Woh qayxixxu le cakkik gibdi gutqoh gutqa num kinni
  107,3,Kaadu usuk tu dagoyta adoobisaanamah sinam milsiisaay isih maaba
  107,4,Salat abah yan maray (munaafiqhiin kinnuk) yallak galto edde garrise waah gibdi digaalá tan
  107,5,Usun sinni salat waala maray le waktil kaa abewa
  107,6,Usun yoobulah sinam sinni tablenkeh meqe taama aba mara kinnon
  107,7,"Kaadu cine waanam, cina mara gacsah, mingiilaay yakmeenih yaaqubeenim kee wohuk kalah taniimik"
  108,1,Diggah Nabiyow nanu kawthar deqsita doray jannatti addal yani koh necee
  108,2,"Tokkel Nabiyow salat kee masgaadá, isi Rabbih caglisak ab"
  108,3,"Nabiyow diggah koo kee atu tirtok luk temeetem niqbi num, usuk samad maliiy kulli kayrik yiggiriqqeh"
  109,1,"Nabiyow koroosite marak ixxic: kee ta koroseey"
  109,2,Isin taqbuden Numtinwellittee kee sin yallitte maqbuda
  109,3,Kaadu isin anu aqbudeh an inki yalla yaqbude mara hinniton
  109,4,Kaadu anu isin taqbudeenim (yallak kalah tanim kinnuk). yaqbude num hinniyo
  109,5,Kaadu isin anu aqbudeh an inki yalla yaqbude mara hinniton
  109,6,"Isin sinni diini Litoonuuh, anu inni diini liyo"
  110,1,Nabiyow Yallih qokol (cató) kee makki fakim koh Yamaate waqdi
  110,2,Kaadu seehadá Yallih diinit butta buttah culah table waqdi
  110,3,"Toysa Ku-Rabbi saytunnos kaa faylisak, kaadu dambi cabti kaal esser,, diggah usuk isil gaca marak gacim (toobat kinnuk) oggolaah qafu aba Rabbi kinnik"
  111,1,"Abii lahab namma gaba finqiteh, kaadu usuk finqiteh"
  111,2,Kay maaluy yedderee kee kay xaylo Kaah xiqtem maliiy yallih digaalak tu kaak ma catta
  111,3,Usuk Ķaxxa ura-le giray hadiidigta Culele
  111,4,"Kaadu kay barray bocó takkuqih tani, girá kaâ luk culele"
  111,5,Tet fillat cambok yan akatay is jahannam giráh addal edde diggalsimta yan
  112,1,"Ixxic nabiyow:usuk Yalla inkittu kinniih, agleyta mali"
  112,2,Yalli cagalah caagiidaa kee faxaanamih magdabah eleelitan Rabbi kinni
  112,3,"Yalli maxalinnaay, Kaa xaltem matan"
  112,4,"Kaadu makkinnaay masuginnaay mayan, inkittuy kaa ceelaah kaa qeedaala"
  113,1,"Ixxic Nabiyow: maaca gine Rabbi maggansitaah kaa eleelita"
  113,2,Usuk ginni heemih umaanek
  113,3,"Kaadu gibdi dite leh yan barih umaanek kaa maggansita, usuk (bar kinnuk) culah yan waqdi"
  113,4,Ķaadu kuntuubaabil baabah tuf- tufó abtah tan sayyóh umaanek koo maggansita
  113,5,Kaadu kuuxe waynanli kuuxe waynan aba waqdih umaanek koo maggansita
  114,1,"Ixxic Nabiyow: seehada gine Rabbi maggansita"
  114,2,Seehadah amoytay ken yamlike maggansita.(Yalla kinnuk)
  114,3,"Seehada kah rammittaah, taqbude Yalla maggansita"
  114,4,"Waswaseynah yan sheytanay, Yallih cusiyyak garcitan waqdi sinam waswasaah, Yalla cusan waqdi qellitah umaanek koo maggansita"
  114,5,Kaay(sheytan kinnuk)seehadâ sorkocobbaxittet waswasaa kee umaane culsa
  114,6,Jinni sheytoonaa kee seehadâ sheytoonak tan waswasak